\par\pard\plain \s0\ql\fi0\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 GEN - - Si waitogh Ufroghm\u233?n; Nama Translation
\par\pard\plain \s52\ql\fi0\lin0\rin0\sb160\sa80\b\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs33 1
\par\pard\plain \s106\qc\fi0\lin0\rin0\sb160\sa80\b\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 R\u233?ny\u233?gh
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 1\~}
Ufroghan Ng\u225?nj\u225?nam yafrotam njafar a mband, {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 2\~}
mband t\u233?morw\u233?n s\u225?fofnar a m\u233? sotro. Nder\u233? arakafam yafary\u233?ng m\u233?inyotio rokar t\u233?morw\u233?n wareng\u233?gh k\u233?nj\u250?n m\u233?inyotio kw\u233?fkw\u233?fan, Ng\u225?nj\u225?nene Mb\u233?rmb\u233?r t\u233?morw\u233?n em\u225?ng\u233?ghan nu tukm\u233?.
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 3\~}
F\u233?yo Ng\u225?nj\u225?n norayai, "K\u233?t\u225?n yumyotan kwayagh\u233? so y\u233?m, " a kwayagh\u233? nufary\u233?ng. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 4\~}
Ng\u225?nj\u225?n t\u233?morw\u233?n \u225?uw\u233?ghan m\u233?nam\u233?n n\u233?m\u233? y\u233?mon yinjoi. F\u233?yo y\u233?mon y\u233?faloi kwayagh\u233? k\u233?t\u225?ndm\u233? kw\u233?fkw\u233?fta. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 5\~}
Y\u233?mon y\u233?tkw\u233?n yaramai kwayaghai "efogh, " a kw\u233?fkw\u233?foe "S\u233?mb\u225?r." F\u233?r\u233?gh nawaindai a akw nufary\u233?ng. Y\u233?n\u233? t\u233?morw\u233?n fronde efogh.
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 6\~}
F\u233?yo Ng\u225?nj\u225?n norayai, "K\u233?t\u225?n yumyotan saur\u233?gh so y\u233?m nu falogh\u233?t m\u233?n\u225?t s\u225?i efalow\u233? nu s\u243?mbio." A y\u233?n\u233? nufrotam. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 7\~}
F\u233?yo Ng\u225?nj\u225?n yafrotam saur\u233?ghkaf s\u225?f a efaleyai nu mbandot k\u233?t\u225?ndm\u233? nu tukta. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 8\~}
Y\u233?mon y\u233?tkw\u233?n yaramai saur\u233?ghkaf sifayai, "Njafar." F\u233?r\u233?gh nawaindai a akw nufary\u233?ng t\u233?morw\u233?n s\u243?mbio efogh.
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 9\~}
F\u233?yo Ng\u225?nj\u225?n norayau, "K\u233?t\u225?n yumyotau nu njafar mbanmbandot m\u233?n\u225?t so tafgh\u233?n \u225?mbiro sifayat, m\u233?n\u225?t nden\u233? mband so y\u233?fandat." A t\u233? nufaram. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 10\~}
Y\u233?mon y\u233?tkw\u233?n yaramai yu "mband, " a nu \u225?rk\u233? t\u233? n\u233?naflai af\u233?gh\u233?t y\u233?m y\u233?tkw\u233?n yaramai "arakaf." A Ng\u225?nj\u225?n y\u233?morm\u233?n a asnetam m\u233?n\u225?yan n\u233?m\u233? y\u233?mon yinjoi.
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 11\~}
F\u233?yo y\u233?mon norayai, "Yumyotau mband m\u233?inyotio walasafot njamke t\u233?f\u233?n funagh\u233?t, nden\u233? emofem efunat njamke a emofem efunat mbwe." A t\u233? y\u233?morm\u233?n ufroghan. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 12\~}
Mbandam efunam walasafot njamke t\u233?f\u233?n a Ng\u225?nj\u225?n nasnetam m\u233?n\u225?yan n\u233?m\u233? y\u233?mon ewinjoi. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 13\~}
F\u233?r\u233?gh nawandai a akw nufar. Y\u233?n\u233? t\u233?morw\u233?n nambiom\u233?n efogh.
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 14\~}
F\u233?yo Ng\u225?nj\u225?nam norayai, "K\u233?t\u225?n eumyotau kwayagh\u233? ufargh\u233?t y\u233?n\u233? njafar k\u233?nj\u250?t m\u233?n\u225?t efogh falogh\u233?t k\u233?t\u225?ndm\u233? s\u233?mb\u225?rta m\u233?n\u225?t tufarotang\u233? efoghf\u233?ne njam efogh so em njam yunj\u233?f so em a w\u225?wefnogh t\u233?m\u233?nd so n\u233?reindat, {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 15\~}
f\u225? so natremngotat njafar k\u233?nj\u250?n m\u233?n\u225?t kwayagh\u233? so yaramete k\u233?t\u225?n mbandot." A y\u233?morm\u233?n ufroghan. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 16\~}
F\u233?yo Ng\u225?nj\u225?nam ewafrom\u233?ng y\u233?n\u233? s\u243?mbio ndimbal kwayagh\u233?-efogh menat efogh lim\u225?n\u233?gh\u233?t a gh\u233?rare s\u233?mb\u225?r lim\u225?n\u233?gh\u233?t. Y\u233?mon nden\u225?yo ewafrotam k\u233?nd. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 17\~}
Y\u233?mon ekmetam kwayagh\u233? njafar k\u233?nj\u250?n m\u233?n\u225?t mband tuk\u233?n atremngogh\u233?t, {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 18\~}
m\u233?n\u225?t efogh a s\u233?mb\u225?r falogh\u233?t. A Ng\u225?nj\u225?m n\u233?snetam m\u233?n\u225?yan n\u233?m\u233? y\u233?mon ewinjoi. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 19\~}
F\u233?r\u233?gh naweindai a akw nufar-y\u233?n\u233? t\u233?morw\u233?n s\u243?mbios\u243?mbiom\u233?n efogh.
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 20\~}
F\u233?yo Ng\u225?nj\u225?n norayai, Eumyotau nu so y\u233?m afoghare gh\u233?rs\u233? rokaraf\u233?, a yumyotau y\u233?n\u233? ambone yam ewafoi men." {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 21\~}
F\u233?yo Ng\u225?nj\u225?n ewafrotam ndimba arakafm\u233?n f\u233?rf\u233?raf\u233? artotam m\u233?inyotio w\u233?la s\u225?fot nu k\u233?m\u233?ghm\u233?n rokar \u225?rk\u233? ek\u233?m nu k\u233?nj\u250?n a m\u233?inyotio w\u233?la s\u225?fotm\u233?n. A Ng\u225?njan n\u233?snetam m\u233?n\u225?yan n\u233?m\u233? ewinjoi. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 22\~}
Y\u233?mon efrendai f\u225? m\u233?inyotio a emndai nden\u233? t\u225?f emor nu k\u233?nj\u250?n m\u233?n\u225?t funagh\u233?t a m\u233?n\u225?t tafongi arakaf, a y\u233?mon emndeyai men m\u233?n\u225?t f\u225?rof\u225?ro afayogh\u233?t nambayan{\super a{\footnote \pard\plain \s212\ql\fi0\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22  {\super a}{{\cs214\b\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 1.22 }
