. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 23\~}
F\u233?r\u233?gh nawaindai a akw nufar- y\u233?n\u233? t\u233?morw\u233?n 5m\u233?n efogh.
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 24\~}
F\u233?yo Ng\u225?nj\u225?n norayai, "Yumyotau mband m\u233?inyotio w\u233?la s\u225?fot gh\u233?rs\u233? w\u233?r\u225?r: m\u233?njar\u233?ghm\u233?n w\u233?r\u225?r a munjan w\u233?r\u225?r, ndimbal a n\u233?mbnar. A t\u233? nufrotam. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 25\~}
Ng\u225?nj\u225?nam ewafrotam f\u233? m\u233?inyotio a f\u225? nasnetam m\u233?n\u225?yam n\u233?m\u233? y\u233?mon ewinjoi.
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 26\~}
F\u233?yo Ng\u225?nj\u225?n norayai, "S\u233?nonjo y\u233?ndfem so ewafrotam \u225?r; f\u225? so em nden\u233? y\u233?nd k\u233?s y\u233?n\u233?m t\u233?fene s\u225?f. F\u225? waftaf\u233? so em wagiffaf a menafefaf a m\u233?inyotio w\u233?r\u225?r, manjar\u233?gh w\u233?r\u225?rfaf a munjan w\u233?r\u225?rfaf, ndimbal a n\u233?mbnar." {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 27\~}
F\u233?yo Ng\u225?nj\u225?nam ewafrotam \u225?r, ewafrom\u233?ng f\u225? nden\u233? s\u225?fot f\u225?yo. Y\u233?mon ewafrom\u233?ng ghak\u233?r a m\u233?r\u233?s, {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 28\~}
efrendangeyai f\u225? a norayai, "So eware t\u225?rf\u225?r ambumt\u233?rt\u233?r, m\u233?n\u225?t nden\u233? f\u233?fene \u225?kiambum so emor m\u233?inyotio y\u233?nam\u233? mband maratan, a so t\u233?nmanangi y\u233?fene lim\u225?n\u233?gh mbanmbanot. Y\u233?ndon n\u233?kmetan f\u233?m wanjeng\u233?t wagiffaf, menfaf a m\u233?inyotio k\u233?ghat w\u233?r\u225?rfaf.
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 29\~}
Y\u233?nd t\u233? n\u233?usenam\u233?n m\u233?inyotio w\u233?ka s\u225?fot njamke a m\u233?inyotio w\u233?n mbwe m\u233?n\u225?t feyot n\u233?net. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 30\~}
W\u233?nde m\u233?inyotio k\u233?ghat w\u233?r\u225?rafet a m\u233?inyotio menafet y\u233?nd t\u233? n\u233?isenam\u233?n yus a arauaf\u233? w\u233?n y\u233?feyot n\u233?net. A t\u233? t\u233?morw\u233?n ufroghan.
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 31\~}
Ng\u225?nj\u225?n n\u233?retai y\u233?n\u233? rokarfaf y\u233?mon \u225?rk\u233? ewafrotam, a f\u225? mindefifi nasnetam. F\u233?r\u233?gh naweindai a akw nufar. Y\u233?n\u233? t\u233?morw\u233?n 6m\u233?n efogh.
