F\u233?yo njafar a mband emorm\u233?gn wafroghe yifoi.
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 2\~}
Sefenm\u233?n efghon Ng\u225?nj\u225?nam yifoi n\u233?m\u233? y\u233?mon t\u233? tawafrotau a n\u233?kmboi \u225?s\u225?foghta. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 3\~}
Y\u233?mon y\u233?frendai sefenm\u233?n efogh a f\u233?nataye y\u233?kmai nden\u233? f\u233?t\u233? efogh m\u233?nam\u233?n nden\u233? y\u233?n\u233? efghon y\u233?mon t\u233? yifoi y\u225?ne wafroghyam a n\u233?kmboi \u225?s\u225?foghta.
