A nden\u233? y\u233?morm\u233?ng ndern\u225?ye njafar a mband t\u233?morw\u233?n wafroghan.
\par\pard\plain \s105\qc\fi0\lin0\rin0\sb160\sa80\b\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 Eden ndau
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 Njam Yur\u233? Ng\u225?nj\u225?nam yafrotam njafar a mband. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 5\~}
k\u233?t\u233? yau tamorw\u233?n \u225?mb gh\u233?rs\u233? w\u233?n y\u233?n\u233? mband tuk\u233?n \u225?rk\u233? t\u233? w\u233?n mbwe nafnyam\u233?nd m\u233?nam\u233?n y\u233?mo \u225?mb yau yafretam nu afam\u233?gh\u233?t, a k\u233?t\u233? yau \u225?mb \u225?r t\u233?morw\u233?n m\u233?n\u225?t wanogh\u233?t yu tun\u233? {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 6\~}
w\u233?nde nu y\u233?nmorm\u233?n k\u233?t\u225?ndm\u233? mband k\u233?nj\u250?ta farut a nuam yafrory\u233?ng mband.
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 7\~}
F\u233?yo Yur\u233? Ng\u225?nj\u225?nam ewerai \u225?mb ngw\u233?rm\u233?ng k\u233?t\u225?ndm\u233? mbandta a yafrotam \u225?r y\u233?nata; y\u233?mon yaramai gh\u233?rs\u233? ramgh\u233?t ambone y\u225?ne minf\u233?neta a y\u233?n\u233? \u225?r n\u233?namndai im\u225?ng\u233?ghaf\u233?.
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 8\~}
F\u233?yo Yur\u233? Ng\u225?nj\u225?nam yiyai ndau Eden k\u233?nj\u250?n, werta a k\u233?t\u233? y\u233?mon y\u233?kmai \u225?r efe y\u233?mon t\u233? yafarnjam\u233?ng. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 9\~}
Y\u233?mon ewafrotam\u233?ng m\u233?inyotio w\u233?lo s\u225?fot wayamneghaf\u233? w\u233?n k\u233?t\u233? kanotaw\u233? a kafunaw\u233?t mer w\u233?n mbwe. Y\u233?n\u233? ndau n\u233?ndk\u233?fan k\u233?t\u233? tiyang\u233?rw\u233?n w\u233?n \u225?rk\u233? m\u233?nayen yaramete gh\u233?rs\u233? a w\u233?n \u225?rk\u233?m\u233?nayam y\u233?ramete mat m\u233?nam\u233?n n\u233?m\u233? y\u233?m mer a n\u233?m\u233? y\u233?m m\u225?m\u225?fi.
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 10\~}
Wanje y\u233?raye Eden ndau k\u233?nj\u250?ta a y\u233?frone y\u233?n\u233? ndau; a y\u233?ngwarfne Eden ndauta nde w\u233?ng\u233?m, a k\u233?t\u225?ndm\u233? k\u233?t\u233? a nafaloy\u233?nd a namndai 4 wanje. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 11\~}
Y\u233?n\u233? fronde wanjeyoene y\u233?tkw\u233?n y\u233?m Fison, y\u233?nam\u233? nu y\u233?raye Afila yuwom\u233? yarende k\u233?t\u233? \u225?nde em gol. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 12\~}
F\u233?w\u233?nf\u233?w\u233?nofnar gol k\u233?t\u233?f ewinjotat a nden\u225?yo y\u233?n\u233? mband mer w\u233?m. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 13\~}
S\u243?mbiom\u233?n wanje siy\u233?m Gion; y\u233?nam\u233? yanraye a nuam yarende ndimbal yu Kus. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 14\~}
Nambiom\u233?n wanje siy\u233?m Tigris, \u225?rk\u233?m\u233?n\u233? yaraye Asiria w\u233?rta, a fom\u233?n wanje siy\u233?m Ufrates.
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 15\~}
F\u233?yo Yur\u233? Ng\u225?nj\u225?nam y\u233?kmai \u225?r Eden ndau k\u233?nj\u250?n m\u233?n\u225?t mband makw\u233?lot a werwergh\u233?t. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 16\~}
Y\u233?mon y\u233?mndai f\u225?, "F\u233?mon fia y\u233?nata w\u233?n mbwe \u225?rk\u233? w\u233?n t\u233?u yeneta ndau k\u233?nj\u250?, {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 17\~}
w\u233?nde w\u233?nm\u233?n yau \u225?rk\u233? w\u233?nam y\u233?ramete matyam m\u233?nam\u233?n n\u233?m\u233? meryam a m\u225?m\u225?fi. F\u233?mon yau so yenete y\u233?n\u233? w\u233?nm\u233?n mbwe, njam f\u233?mon yenete, f\u233?m t\u225?f so k\u233?r n\u233?m.
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 18\~}
F\u233?yo Yur\u233? Ng\u225?nj\u225?n norayai, Yau mer y\u233?m m\u233?n\u225?t \u225?roe yambia amnogh\u233?t, y\u233?ndon so yafrotan y\u225? w\u225?ut\u225?r\u233?gh \u225?r \u225?rk\u233? y\u225?yot mbark\u225?nd y\u225? w\u225?utargh\u233?t."
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 19\~}
