Yafrote s\u233?msot wafarogh ndimbal boutoe, a koro 18 insis tukta saw\u233?rghkaf tuk\u233?n. T\u233?kam s\u233?safne ndimbal bout t\u233?ndota a ram\u233?gh tafngo ndimbal bout yuwan, n\u233?ndk\u233?fan tuk\u233?n mbrandeyaf\u233?. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 17\~}
