S\u243?mbioe m\u233?inyotio f\u233?nat\u233? men, m\u233?inyotio f\u233?nat\u233? manjar\u233?gh w\u233?r\u225?r, a m\u233?inyotio f\u233?nat\u233? gh\u233?rs\u233? rokar \u225?rk\u233? n\u233?roghat mband tuk\u233?n so k\u233?naflangi fefaf m\u233?n\u225?t wamang\u233?t. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 21\~}
