\u193?mb akwan Abimelek\u233?m emotay\u233?ng y\u225?ne faiofnar \u225?s\u225?fogh \u225?r a y\u233?fe ewaufroy\u233?ng n\u233?m\u233? yam kufrotaw\u233?ng a f\u225? minde f\u233?rf\u233?r tamorw\u233?n. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 9\~}
