F\u233?yo njam Ng\u225?nj\u225?nam w\u233?m\u225?f\u225?retay\u233?ng y\u233?nd tane afane m\u233?ngota k\u233?t\u225?n d\u225?bi yuwot. Y\u233?ndon norayay\u233?n Sarafaf, 'F\u233?m so fenjo uw\u233?gh yuyafote tafaf \u225?rkam\u233? njam y\u233?nyow\u233?, so noraye tanem\u233?n nden\u233? f\u225? siy\u233?m tane ghak\u233?rfifi.'"
