F\u233?yo Abimelekam yaramay\u233?ng Sara Ebraame, sif, kau a faiofnar \u225?s\u225?fogh \u225?rf\u233?. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 15\~}
F\u225? norayay\u233?ng Ebraamefaf, "Senmon m\u233?inyotio tane mband; n\u233?kmang\u233? t\u233?u \u225?rkam\u233? y\u233?nam\u233? fenjo m\u233?ndeye." {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 16\~}
