Yur\u233? tamorw\u233?n ng\u225?r\u225?mro Sarafaf nden\u233? f\u233?t\u233? f\u225? k\u233?s norayay\u233?ng, a Yur\u233? yafrotam Sara n\u233?m\u233? f\u225? uny\u233?ghofnar si norayay\u233?ng, {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 2\~}
Sara namnday\u233?ng suaf\u233? a y\u225?r\u225?ftai ghak\u233?r ambum. Ebraam olmanan y\u233?n\u233? efghonfifi Ng\u225?nj\u225?n uny\u233?ghofnar so y\u233?mndai f\u225?. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 3\~}
Ebraamam y\u233?tkw\u233?n yaramay\u233?ng Aisek, {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 4\~}
a njam y\u225?ne ambum tamorw\u233?n 8 efogh namnday\u233?ng, Ebraamam gh\u233?ngan y\u233?nfay\u233?ng, nden\u233? f\u233?t\u233? Ng\u225?nj\u225?nam y\u233?mnday\u233?ng f\u225?. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 5\~}
Ebraam t\u233?morw\u233?n 100 yunj\u233?f Aisek n\u225?r\u225?ftam y\u225?yot. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 6\~}
Sara norayay\u233?ng, "Ng\u225?nj\u225?n kw\u233?nmarse ta f\u233?n, a m\u233?inyotio \u225?mbiro\u225?mbiro efe n\u225?y\u225?retat y\u233?n\u233?mam\u233?n so nurtam y\u233?ndf\u233?." {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 7\~}
F\u233?yo y\u233?mon yasamngoy\u233?ng, "Efe njam norayat Ebraamefaf nde Saram y\u225?njo ambum so yamanjne? Y\u233?ndon y\u225?r\u225?ftan ambum y\u225?yot aus\u233?yan."
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 8\~}
Ambum nanotay\u233?ng a y\u233?n\u233? efghon f\u225? t\u233?morw\u233?n njamke t\u225?ik\u233?r, Ebraamam yafrotam ndimbal t\u233?m\u233?nd.
\par\pard\plain \s105\qc\fi0\lin0\rin0\sb160\sa80\b\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 Agar a Ismail engw\u225?f\u225?retangeyay\u233?nd
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 9\~}
\u193?mb efghon Ismail, efe Ijifm\u233?n amaf Agaram y\u225?r\u225?ftai Ebraame, k\u233?mbnaw\u233?t y\u233?maf\u233? Sarane ambum Aisek. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 10\~}
Saram ewinjeyai f\u225? a norayai Ebraamefaf, "Titr\u233?m y\u233?n\u233? \u225?s\u225?fogh m\u233?r\u233?s a y\u225?ne ambum. Y\u233?n\u233? amafoene ambumom yau so tawanang\u233? \u225?mb rokar fenem\u233?n, \u225?rk\u233? tane ambumomro so tawanang\u233?." {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 11\~}
Y\u233?n\u233? yam taw\u233?rsotau Ebraam ndimbal k\u233?r\u225?ye, m\u233?nam\u233?n Ismail nden\u225?yo t\u233?morw\u233?n y\u225?ne ambum. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 12\~}
W\u233?nde Ng\u225?nj\u225?n norayai Ebraamefaf, "Yau m\u225?m\u233? mwigh\u233? n\u233?m m\u233?nam\u233?n ambum a fene \u225?s\u225?fogh amaf Agar. Ewafrota n\u233?mat Saram njam namndeta m\u233?nam\u233?n Aisek k\u233?nj\u250?m\u233? f\u233?m so em \u225?ki ambumaf\u233? \u225?rk\u233? t\u233? norayay\u233?n uny\u233?ghofnar si. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 13\~}
Y\u233?ndon so nden\u225?yo k\u233?maraman t\u225?rf\u225?r ambum fene \u225?s\u225?fogh amafone ambumoefaf, m\u233?n\u225?t f\u225? so kamndang \u225?mbiro yu. F\u225? siy\u233?m fene ambum f\u233?t\u233? y\u233?m."
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 14\~}
\u193?mb akwan Ebraamam yaramai \u225?mb njamke a bai nu afoghare Agarefaf. Y\u233?mon ambum y\u233?finjoi faderan y\u225?faf a engwatembayay\u233?ng. F\u225? nuwanoy\u233?ng a kawersow\u233?t y\u233?nam\u233? Beyersiba fanfneyam\u233?. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 15\~}
Njam m\u233?inyotio nu nefoy\u233?ng, y\u233?mon ambum y\u233?frangoy\u233?ng k\u233?ghatan {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 16\~}
a n\u225?mnjoy\u233?ng \u225?mb 100 mit\u233?. F\u233?yo norayay\u233?ng, "Y\u233?ndon yau so tinjon ambum k\u233?ran." Njamandio f\u225? t\u233?morang\u233?rw\u233?n k\u233?t\u233?, f\u225? ye nufngoy\u233?nd.
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 17\~}
Ng\u225?nj\u225?n t\u233? n\u225?y\u225?reng ghakroene ye, njafar si r\u233?sagh \u225?r norayay\u233?ng Agar njafarta, "N\u233?m\u233? t\u233?f\u233?n y\u233?m Agar? Yau f\u233?rf\u233?r n\u233?m. Ng\u225?nj\u225?n t\u233? n\u225?y\u225?reng ghakroene ye. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 18\~}
Kokai, kuwano a t\u233?kaf f\u225? a t\u225?ut\u225?na y\u225?. Y\u233?ndon so tiy\u225?ton ndimbal yu y\u225?ne \u225?ki ambum k\u233?nj\u250?m\u233?." {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 19\~}
F\u233?yo Ng\u225?nj\u225?nam yasaw\u233?ry\u233?ng y\u225?ne gh\u233?k\u233?f, a y\u233?mon yinjoy\u233?ng y\u233?kw. F\u225? nuwanoi yararotam nu baik nue \u225?mb y\u225? ghak\u233?r ambumoe yaramay\u233?ng. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 20\~}
Ng\u225?nj\u225?n t\u233?morw\u233?n ghak\u233?roefaf njam f\u225? kanotaw\u233?ng; f\u225? t\u233?kmang\u233?rw\u233?n Faran fanfneyan a namnday\u233?ng far\u233? n\u233?ghn\u233?gh. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 21\~}
Yatmam y\u233?ronjam Ijifm\u233?n amaf y\u225?yot.
\par\pard\plain \s105\qc\fi0\lin0\rin0\sb160\sa80\b\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 Mwigh\u233? r\u233?ny\u233?gh Ebraam a Abimelek
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 22\~}
Y\u233?n\u233? efghon Abimelek n\u233?waneyay\u233?nd Fikolf\u233?, fiyarafene s\u233?nko \u225?r a norayay\u233?ng Ebraam, "Ng\u225?nj\u225?naf\u233? f\u233?m ere m\u233?inyotio rokar wafroghan. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 23\~}
F\u233?yo uny\u233?ghofnar si koraya y\u233?na Ng\u225?nj\u225?nene s\u225?fr\u233?re m\u233?n\u225?t nden\u233? f\u233?m yau so nuinde tafaf, tane ambumt\u233?rt\u233?r, o tane \u225?ki ambumafefaf. Y\u233?nd merro t\u233? kw\u233?n\u233?m fefaf, f\u233?yo f\u233?m uny\u233?ghofnar si koraya m\u233?n\u225?t nden\u233? f\u233?m so merro n\u233?m tafaf a y\u233?nan y\u233?n\u233? yuwon \u225?nde f\u233?m n\u233?morangre."
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 24\~}
Ebraam norayay\u233?ng, "Y\u233?nd uny\u233?ghofnar si norayan."
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 25\~}
Ebraam kawatarnaw\u233?ng Abimelekefaf nu y\u233?kwm\u233?n \u225?rk\u233? Abimelekene faiofnar \u225?s\u225?fogh \u225?r\u233?m narenjam\u233?nd. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 26\~}
Abimelek\u233?m norayay\u233?ng, "Y\u233?nd mafina w\u233?m emon y\u233?n\u233? tafrote. F\u233?mon yau waufroi ta y\u233?n\u233?mam\u233?n. Y\u233?nd m\u233? n\u225?y\u225?ren m\u233?n s\u233?nonjo y\u233?n\u233?mam\u233?n.
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 27\~}
F\u233?yo Ebraamam yaramai \u225?mb sif a kau Abimeleke, a y\u233?n\u233? s\u243?mbioyam mwigh\u233? yarenjaghm\u233?nd. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 28\~}
Ebraamam efaloy\u233?ng sif tos\u233?tos\u233? y\u225?njo sifta, {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 29\~}
a Abimelek\u233?m yamotay\u233?ng f\u225?, "N\u233?mam\u233?n f\u233?mon y\u233?n\u233? tafrote?"
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 30\~}
Ebraamam yawangoy\u233?ng, "T\u233?myo y\u233?n\u233? sefen sif tos\u233?tos\u233?. Y\u233?n\u233? yam wafroghe, f\u233?mon y\u233?fande nde y\u233?nd fw\u233?m emo nu y\u233?kw y\u233?tatem. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 31\~}
F\u233?yo y\u233?n\u233? yu y\u233?tkw\u233?n t\u233?nmotaw\u233?t Beyersiba, s\u243?mbio \u225?r\u233?m uny\u233?ghofnar mwigh\u233? yar\u233?ny\u233?ghm\u233?nd.
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 32\~}
Soram\u233? y\u233?mofem yafrom\u233?nd y\u233?n\u233? mwigh\u233? r\u233?ny\u233?gh Beyersiban, Abimelek a Fikol nangoy\u233?nd Filistia. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 33\~}
F\u233?yo Ebraamam eitam tamarisk w\u233?n Beyersiban t\u225?wefnotau Yur\u233? Akegh Ng\u225?nj\u225?n. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 34\~}
Ebraam y\u233?kmang\u233?rm\u233?n Filistain yuwon tekefifi.
\par\pard\plain \s52\ql\fi0\lin0\rin0\sb160\sa80\b\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs33 22
\par\pard\plain \s105\qc\fi0\lin0\rin0\sb160\sa80\b\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 Ng\u225?nj\u225?nam yufotam\u233?ng Ebraam
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 1\~}
1 \u193?mb efghon soram\u233? Ng\u225?nj\u225?n yufotam Ebraam; y\u233?mon y\u233?moy\u233?ng f\u225?, "Ebraam!" A Ebraamam yawangoy\u233?ng, "Y\u233?nd sw\u233?m y\u233?na!"
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 2\~}
Ng\u225?nj\u225?n norayay\u233?ng, "T\u233?ngwan fenjo ambum, fenjo ambumfifi Aisek, efe f\u233?mon eghete mindefifi, a kuwano Moreya mbandot. K\u233?t\u233? mband tunak\u233?f tuk\u233?n y\u233?ndon so k\u233?mauyafon f\u225?, t\u233?fai f\u225? nden\u233? f\u233?t\u233? tayot gh\u233?ng\u233?not."
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 3\~}
T\u225?nd\u225?i \u225?mb akwan Ebraam enfete f\u233?s gh\u233?ng\u233?not yawasote y\u225?njo ndonki, a yanay\u233?ng Aisek a y\u225?njo s\u243?mbio faiofnar \u225?s\u225?fogh \u225?r y\u233?maf\u233?. F\u225? nuwanoy\u233?nd y\u233?n\u233? yuwot Ng\u225?nj\u225?nam \u225?rk\u233?mam\u233?n f\u225? t\u233? emnday\u233?ng. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 4\~}
Nambiom\u233?n efghon Ebraamam y\u233?ngwinjoy\u233?ng y\u225?ne yu nayuta. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 5\~}
F\u233?yo f\u225? norayay\u233?ng s\u243?mbio faiofnar \u225?s\u225?fogh \u225?rfefaf, "Kamnjend y\u233?na ndonkif\u233?. Ghak\u233?r ambum a y\u233?nd so k\u233?nyowa k\u233?t\u225?n w\u225?wefnogh\u233?t a so y\u233?nd k\u233?nang\u233?m f\u233?fefaf."
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 6\~}
Ebraamam y\u233?mndai Aisek w\u233?n t\u233?nj r\u233?sagh\u233?t gh\u233?ng\u233?not, a y\u225? y\u233?monyo giri a f\u233?s. Njam f\u225? tayow\u233?ng merne, {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 7\~}
Aisek norayai, "Af\u233?!"
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 Y\u233?mon yawangoy\u233?ng, "Wai tane ambum?"
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 Aisek namotay\u233?ng, "Y\u233?ndon efandwan f\u233? a w\u233?n t\u233?nj, w\u233?nde \u225?nde y\u233?m sif tos\u233? gh\u233?ng\u233?not?"
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 8\~}
Ebraamam yawangoy\u233?ng, "Ng\u225?nj\u225?n f\u225?yo \u225?mbiro so n\u233?usena." A s\u243?mbio f\u225? n\u233?ngwaneyay\u233?nd merne.
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 9\~}
Njam f\u225? nufareyay\u233?nd y\u233?n\u233? yuwot \u225?rk\u233?m\u233?n\u233? Ng\u225?nj\u225?nam ewamnday\u233?ng, Ebraamam y\u233?rametam gh\u233?ng\u233?n w\u225?rogh kitar\u233? a efayotam w\u233?n t\u233?nj tuk\u233?n. Y\u233?mon yumbetam y\u225?njo ambum a y\u233?fayoi f\u225? gh\u233?ng\u233?n w\u225?rogh kitarayan w\u233?n t\u233?nj tuk\u233?n. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 10\~}
F\u233?yo y\u233?mon y\u233?kafay\u233?ng giri yuyoy\u233?ng y\u225? ngiot. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 11\~}
W\u233?nde Yurane njafar r\u233?sagh \u225?r n\u233?nutnay\u233?ng k\u233?t\u225?ndm\u233? njafarfa, "Ebraam, Ebraam!"
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 Y\u233?mo y\u233?ngwawangoi, "Wai sw\u233?m y\u233?nd y\u233?na."
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 12\~}
F\u225? norayay\u233?ng, "Yau taghna ghak\u233?r ambum o n\u233?mndafi yam yafrota y\u225?faf. S\u233?nonjo y\u233?nd mat nden\u233? w\u233?m f\u233?mon ut\u233?mnd\u233? a n\u225?myote wafrogh\u233?t Ng\u225?nj\u225?nefaf, m\u233?nam\u233?n f\u225? yau fenjo f\u233?f\u233?t ambum y\u233?re y\u225? tamb\u233?n."
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 13\~}
Ebraam nawarenday\u233?ng ereghan a yinjoy\u233?ng ghak\u233?r sif nawas\u233?nai k\u233?ghatan y\u225?njo t\u233?krayan. F\u225? nafley\u233?ng a y\u233?nmarai y\u233?ramay\u233?ng gh\u233?ng\u233?not ghak\u233?r ambumoe wasogh. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 14\~}
Ebraamam y\u233?n\u233? yu y\u233?tkw\u233?n y\u233?ramai, "Yur\u233? n\u233?us\u233?nam." A s\u233?nonjo taw\u233?tio \u225?r\u233?m norayai nden\u233?, "Yuane mband tunak\u233?f tuk\u233?n f\u225? n\u233?us\u233?ne."
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 15\~}
Yurane njafar si r\u233?sagh \u225?rom yanmoi Ebraam k\u233?t\u225?ndm\u233? njafarta. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 16\~}
Y\u233?ndon yafrotan uny\u233?ghofnar si m\u233?naye tanjo y\u233?tkw\u233?ne- nde Yur\u233? noraye- nden\u233? y\u233?ndon so f\u233?m k\u233?nfrendang\u233?n wem\u225?rot. M\u233?nam\u233?n f\u233?mon y\u233?n\u233? tafrote a yau y\u233?re fenjo f\u233?f\u233?t ghak\u233?r ambum ta tamb\u233?n, {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 17\~}
y\u233?nd uny\u233?ghofnar si norayan y\u233?ndon so k\u233?maraman \u225?ki ambum nden\u233? t\u225?rf\u225?r k\u233?nd k\u233?s emo njafaran o miri k\u233?s emo arakaf t\u233?ndom\u233?. Fenjo \u225?ki ambumam so esmetat y\u233?fenjo m\u233?k t\u233?fn\u225?r. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 18\~}
