Njam amaf yau m\u233?nde y\u233?m angogh\u233?t f\u233?mof\u233?, f\u233?yo f\u233?m so n\u233?m mer k\u233?t\u225?ndm\u233? uny\u233?ghofnar sita \u225?rk\u233? f\u233?m t\u233? noraya tafaf. W\u233?nde yau tane ambum t\u233?ngwango k\u233?t\u225?notio. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 9\~}
F\u233?yo faiofnar \u225?s\u225?fogh \u225?rom yafrotam nden\u233? f\u233?t\u233? yur\u233? Ebraamam y\u233?mnday\u233?ng a sotaf\u233? si norayai y\u225?faf y\u233?n\u233?mam\u233?n.
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 10\~}
F\u233?yo y\u233?n\u233? faiofnar \u225?s\u225?fogh \u225?rom ewanay\u233?ng 10 y\u225?ne yurane kamel a nafrangoy\u233?ng, y\u233?mon ewanai m\u233?inyotio y\u225?ne yurane mer rokar. F\u225? yiyotam Aram Naaraim, Naorene ndimbal tesen. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 11\~}
\u193?s\u225?fogh \u225?rom tamorw\u233?n kamel a nar\u225?mnjoy\u233?nd ndimbal tesen t\u233?ndota nu y\u233?kwfaf. A t\u233?morw\u233?n f\u233?r\u233?ghan, t\u225?f amaf n\u233?nwanoy\u233?ng nu wuk\u233?gh\u233?t. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 12\~}
F\u233?yo f\u225? oray\u233?gh kufngong\u233?, "Yur\u233?, Ng\u225?nj\u225?n tane ndimbaloene Ebraamene, kwiy\u225?to y\u233?nd fifiyaf\u233? s\u233?nonjo, tuyafo fenjo uw\u233?gh Ebraame. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 13\~}
Y\u233?na y\u233?nd wakayong nufaf, a m\u233?r\u233?sm\u233?r\u233?s ndimbal tese en\u233?m nu wuk\u233?gh\u233?t. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 14\~}
Y\u233?ndon so tamotang\u233?m y\u233?n\u233? m\u233?r\u233?s. So y\u233?ndon \u225?uw\u233?ghaf\u233? nu tanetang\u233?n fene ndaramta? Njam y\u233?mon kwangong\u233? siy\u233?m nu n\u233?net, a y\u233?ndon nden\u225?yo nu so tawaraman kamelafet, m\u233?t\u233? f\u225? y\u233?m f\u233?mon t\u233? yafer fene faiofnar \u225?s\u225?fogh \u225?roene Aiseke. Y\u233?n\u233? ende y\u233?nd mat namndan nden\u233? f\u233?mon t\u233? yuyafo fenjo uw\u233?gh tane ndimbaloe."
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 15\~}
Frondeyo y\u233?mon t\u233? tiyoy\u233?ng oray\u233?gh, Rebeka n\u233?nwanoy\u233?ng y\u225?njo nd\u233?rambaf\u233? t\u233?nmafayong\u233?rw\u233?n y\u225?ne faderan. F\u225? t\u233?morw\u233?n m\u233?r\u233?s Betuelene, Milkane ambum, efe t\u233?morw\u233?n amaf Ebraame y\u225?nng\u233?n Naor. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 16\~}
Y\u233?n\u233? m\u233?r\u233?s t\u233?morw\u233?n minde m\u233?ndef\u233? yuwagia, yau \u225?mb \u225?rf\u233? ekmarm\u233?n y\u233?maf\u233?. F\u225? nuwanoi nu y\u233?kw\u233?t, y\u233?nmikay\u233?ng y\u225?ne nd\u233?ramb a n\u233?nangoy\u233?ng. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 17\~}
A faiofnar \u225?s\u225?fogh \u225?r n\u233?ngengoy\u233?ng a y\u233?ngwanfetai f\u225? a t\u233?mndang\u233?, "\u193?uw\u233?ghaf\u233? ta nu so kwaram n\u233?net."
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 18\~}
M\u233?rsom y\u233?mndai, "T\u233?neta, ndimbal." Y\u233?mon w\u233?keye a y\u233?fnary\u233?ng y\u225?njo nd\u233?ramb a taramang\u233? y\u225? nu. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 19\~}
Njam y\u233?mon yifoy\u233?ng ram\u233?ghe y\u225? nu n\u233?net, f\u225? norayai, "Y\u233?ndon nden\u225?yo m\u233? so t\u233?nwaukan nu fene kamelot k\u233?t\u225?notio f\u225? kor t\u233?remngong\u233?. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 20\~}
