\par\pard\plain \s105\qc\fi0\lin0\rin0\sb160\sa80\b\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 Jeikofene s\u243?mbiom\u233?n a nambiom\u233?n efreng\u233?gh
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 1\~}
Jeikof n\u225?y\u225?ray\u233?ng nden\u233? Labanene ambum norayay\u233?ng, "Jeikofam t\u233?rse m\u233?inyotio rokar \u225?rk\u233? t\u233?fene afane a kar namnd\u233? wem\u225?r y\u225? tamb\u233?n." {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 2\~}
F\u225? nden\u225?yo mat n\u225?y\u225?to nden\u233? Laban yau n\u233?nufary\u233?ng nden\u233? f\u233?t\u233? f\u250?tar y\u225?faf nden\u233? frondeyan. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 3\~}
F\u233?yo Yur\u233? norayai Jeikofefaf, "Kango fekifene mbandot a kaka f\u250?tarfefaf a y\u233?nd so w\u233?m k\u233?t\u233? f\u233?maf\u233?.
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 4\~}
F\u233?yo Jeikofam ghany yangwatembai Reisel a Leyafefaf \u225?ligh\u233?t marat ndimbal yuwot \u225?nde y\u225?ne sif m\u233?r\u233?n tamorw\u233?n. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 5\~}
F\u225? norayay\u233?ng y\u233?fefaf, "Y\u233?ndon t\u233?fandan nden\u233? f\u233?feraf\u233? yau f\u250?tar t\u233?m tafaf nden\u233? fronde k\u233?s t\u233?m. W\u233?nde tane afane Ng\u225?nj\u225?n t\u233? t\u233?m y\u233?ndf\u233? t\u233?nre. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 6\~}
F\u233?m mat em nden\u233? y\u233?nd k\u225?s\u225?fotan mindefifi f\u233?ferafai. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 7\~}
F\u233?ferafam t\u233? kwauweindaye ta, y\u233?mon t\u233? ewengote tane fai 10 mbinotm\u233?. W\u233?nde Ng\u225?nj\u225?nam yau yumyo f\u225? ta waghang\u233?t. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 8\~}
Njam f\u225? noraya, 'N\u233?mbne mboraf\u233? sof em fene faim\u233?n' m\u233?inyotio sif m\u233?r\u233?n n\u225?r\u225?ftat n\u233?mbne mboraf\u233? tot\u233?r; a njam t\u233? noraya, 'Y\u233?n\u233? wit\u233?rmbogh wafer\u233?ghkaf k\u233?s em y\u225?ne so kamndangi faim\u233?n, m\u233?inyotio sif m\u233?r\u233?n k\u233?s k\u225?r\u225?ftat wit\u233?rmbogh. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 9\~}
F\u233?yo Ng\u225?nj\u225?nam t\u233? ewanang f\u233?ferafan sif m\u233?r\u233?n a t\u233?m eramang tayot.
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 10\~}
Y\u233?n\u233? werewereyam y\u233?nd onjo w\u233?kmang\u233?rm\u233?n, y\u233?nd n\u233?ngretayan tuk\u233?t ghak\u233?r gout \u225?rk\u233? ewit\u233?rmbou, n\u233?mbne mborkaf o n\u233?mbne wareng\u233?gh mborkaf. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 11\~}
Onjo k\u233?nj\u250?n Ng\u225?nj\u225?nene njafar si r\u233?sagh \u225?r w\u233?motay\u233?ng y\u233?nd, 'Jeikof!' F\u233?yo y\u233?ndon y\u233?ngwangoy\u233?n, 'Wai sw\u233?m y\u233?nd.' {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 12\~}
Y\u233?mon y\u233?mndai, "K\u233?reta tuk\u233?t a t\u233?fanda y\u233?n\u233? m\u233?inyotio ghak\u233?r gout, \u225?rk\u233? em ekam wit\u233?rmboghkaf em, n\u233?mbne mboraf\u233?, n\u233?mbne war\u233?gh mboraf\u233?, m\u233?nam\u233?n y\u233?ndon t\u233? tafandan m\u233?inyotio n\u233?m\u233? Labanam ewafrote fefaf. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 13\~}
Y\u233?nd w\u233?m Ng\u225?nj\u225?n efe nufary\u233?n fefaf Betelan, \u225?nde f\u233?mon yasunam olif w\u233?kw\u233?r y\u233?n\u233? w\u237?m fu \u225?rk\u233? y\u233?m m\u233?n\u225?t nj\u250?nnj\u250?nofnar yamot a \u225?nde f\u233?mon yafrotam uny\u233?ghofnar si tafaf. S\u233?nonjo t\u233?frango y\u233?n\u233? mband, a kuwano fene f\u250?tarfene mbandot."
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 14\~}
Reisel a Leyafem yawangeyay\u233?nd y\u225?, "K\u233?t\u233? n\u233?mndafi \u225?mb t\u233? y\u233?m t\u233?fene afane m\u233?rnan t\u233?feyot siya tawanang\u233?m? {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 15\~}
T\u233? f\u225? nemne nden\u233? y\u233?nd dafi y\u233?n\u233?m? Yau y\u233?naro tafrote y\u233?mon y\u233?nd y\u233?nt\u233?rnai w\u233?nde y\u233?mon t\u233? t\u233?fene mani t\u233?t\u233?rne \u225?rk\u233? emorm\u233?n t\u233?f\u233?n faim\u233?n. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 16\~}
Efalo m\u233?inyotio y\u233?n\u233? rokar \u225?rk\u233? Ng\u225?nj\u225?nam ewanay\u233?ng t\u233?fene afata t\u233?fene em a t\u233?fene ambumt\u233?rt\u233?rafene. S\u233?nonjo tafrota n\u233?m\u233? Ng\u225?nj\u225?n t\u233? n\u233?mnda f\u233?m.
\par\pard\plain \s105\qc\fi0\lin0\rin0\sb160\sa80\b\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 Laban a Jeikof yafrot krufr\u225?t
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 17\~}
F\u233?yo Jeikof efayoy\u233?ng y\u225?ne ambumt\u233?rt\u233?r a y\u225?t\u233?nof kamel tuk\u233?n, {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 18\~}
Y\u233?mon t\u233?limndau y\u233?n\u233? w\u233?r\u225?r y\u225?ne frondeta a t\u233?rsau m\u233?inyotio rokar \u225?rk\u233? m\u233?n\u225?t f\u225? kamnendaw\u233?ng Fadan Araman a nangoy\u233?ng y\u225?ref\u233? Aisekefaf Kanan\u233?n. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 19\~}
Njam Laban naflay\u233?ng m\u233?n\u225?t sif s\u233?f t\u233?rgh\u233?t, Reiselam oroe y\u225?refane mewang ewanay\u233?ng. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 20\~}
Jeikofam nden\u225?yo y\u225? uny\u233?ghe Labane Aram \u225?r m\u233?naye yau yafrotay\u233?ng nden\u233? f\u225? nuwanote. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 21\~}
F\u233?yo f\u225? nuwanoy\u233?ng w\u233?keye m\u233?inyotio y\u225?ne rokaraf\u233? y\u225?ne n\u233?m\u233? tamorw\u233?n. F\u225? n\u233?ngurtoy\u233?ng Eufrates wanje n\u233?ngwanoy\u233?ng nden\u233? mband tunak\u233?f Giliad.
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 22\~}
s\u243?mbio efogh soram\u233? Labane yaufroy\u233?nd nden\u233? Jeikof t\u233? nuwano w\u233?keye. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 23\~}
F\u225? a y\u225?ne kaka f\u250?taram y\u233?ta y\u233?fnam\u233?nd Jeikof 7 efogh ersam\u233?ng, Labanam y\u233?rsa f\u225? mband tunak\u233?f Giliadan. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 24\~}
Ng\u225?nj\u225?n y\u233?morm\u233?n Laban Aram \u225?r onjoe s\u233?mb\u225?ran a t\u233?mndang\u233? f\u225?, "Aya kor nawarawena yau noraya n\u233?mndafi si Jeikofefaf." {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 25\~}
Njam Labanaf kerkeran nawerayay\u233?nd Jeikofe, Jeikofam efayoy\u233?ng y\u225?ne farai mband tunakfan. F\u233?yo Laban a y\u225?ne f\u250?tarfem efayoy\u233?ng y\u233?fene farai mband tunak\u233?f Giliadan.
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 26\~}
F\u233?yo njam Labanam yamotay\u233?ng Jeikof, "N\u233?m\u233? f\u233?m t\u233?nmafrote m\u233?naye uny\u233?ghe tafaf? F\u233?mon enwasro tane m\u233?r\u233?s nden\u233? m\u233?kene kw\u233?fkw\u233?f m\u233?ngo \u225?r. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 27\~}
N\u233?mam\u233?n f\u233?m n\u233?nwano kwankwane a wenmaweny? F\u233?mon w\u233?i kor yau w\u233?mnde nden\u233? y\u233?nd nuwanotan, y\u233?ndon so k\u233?nmatembangay\u233?n f\u233?m \u225?uw\u233?ghaf\u233? waghaf\u233? temberin a af. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 28\~}
F\u233?mon yau nden\u225?yo mat y\u233?nd w\u225?y\u225?to m\u233?n\u225?t s\u233?nagh\u233?t tane \u225?kiambum a tane m\u233?r\u233?sof. F\u233?mon tafrote onon yam. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 29\~}
Y\u233?nd waftaf\u233? w\u233?m fe waghagh\u233?t, w\u233?nde kerker s\u233?mb\u225?ran fene afane Ng\u225?nj\u225?nam y\u233?nd w\u233?mnde nden\u233?, 'Aya kor nawarawena yau n\u233?mndafi si koraya Jeikofefaf.' {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 30\~}
S\u233?nonjo f\u233?mon t\u233? y\u233?frango ferafane m\u233?ngo m\u233?nam\u233?n f\u233?m k\u233?n\u233?m m\u233?ngofaf. W\u233?nde n\u233?mam\u233?n f\u233?mon oroe enwan tane ng\u225?nj\u225?n?
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 31\~}
Jeikof\u233?m yawangoy\u233?ng, "Y\u233?nd n\u233?nafrangoy\u233?n m\u233?nam\u233?n y\u233?nd f\u233?rf\u233?r kw\u233?morw\u233?n. Y\u233?nd kemnaw\u233?n nden\u233? f\u233?mon kar so t\u233?ngwasreyai fem\u233?rsof tafafta m\u233?naye waferghe. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 32\~}
Njam f\u233?mon tawinjo fenjo ng\u225?nj\u225?n endefaf njam em yau so tumyong\u233?m gh\u233?rsat. T\u233?f\u233?n kaka f\u250?tarfene s\u225?fr\u233?re, eronja ndimbal k\u233?r\u225?ye f\u233?m m\u233?nde k\u233?s n\u233?m y\u233?nam\u233? n\u233?m\u233? tane em a tawam n\u233?m\u233? fene em, Jeikof mafina nden\u233? Reisel\u233?m t\u233? oroe enwanai y\u233?n\u233? ng\u225?nj\u225?n.
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 33\~}
f\u233?yo Laban naflay\u233?ng Jeikofene farai m\u233?ngot, a y\u233?namayo Leyane farai m\u233?ngot a w\u233?i y\u233?namayo s\u243?mbio \u225?s\u225?fogh amafane farai m\u233?ngot. W\u233?nde y\u233?mon n\u233?mndafi yau ewinjoy\u233?ng. F\u225? n\u233?ntory\u233?ng Leyane farai m\u233?ngota a n\u233?naflay\u233?ng Reiselene farai m\u233?ngot. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 34\~}
Reiselam eutory\u233?ng y\u233?n\u233? ng\u225?nj\u225?n eflay\u233?ng kamelafene yaf\u233?n a n\u225?mnjoy\u233?ng y\u233?fene tuk\u233?n Laban y\u233?ta komanjotau m\u225?m\u225?gh\u233?raye farai m\u233?ngom\u233? w\u233?nde n\u233?mndafi yau ewinjoy\u233?ng. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 35\~}
Reisel norayai y\u225?refefaf, "Yau n\u233?kw n\u233?m, af\u233?, w\u233?nde y\u233?nd yau so kokayon siya k\u233?mafotang\u233?n f\u233?m; y\u233?nd wemesm\u233?n kwam." F\u233?yo Laban t\u233? yafrotam ronjagh y\u233?mon yau ewinjoy\u233?ng ng\u225?nj\u225?n.
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 36\~}
F\u233?yo Jeikof n\u233?kwan yifoi a y\u233?motai Laban, "N\u233?m\u233? n\u225?k y\u233?ndon tarafnan? N\u233?m\u233? tane yaufi w\u233?m \u225?rk\u233?m\u233?n\u233? f\u233?m k\u233?n\u233?m y\u233?nd kw\u233?nmifne? {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 37\~}
S\u233?nonjo nden\u233? f\u233?m m\u225?m\u233?gh\u233?raye komanyote y\u233?nam\u233? m\u233?inyotio tane y\u225?fan, t\u233? f\u233?mon n\u233?mndafi fene m\u233?ngom\u233?n? T\u233?k\u233?m y\u233?na m\u233?inyotio t\u233?fene kaka f\u250?tarfene s\u225?fr\u233?re. Mato y\u233?mofem so t\u233?fandang\u233? \u225?rk\u233? \u225?r y\u233?m t\u233?fenem\u233?n mbark\u225?nd. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 38\~}
Y\u233?nd t\u233? t\u233?nre f\u233?maf\u233? 20 yunj\u233?f. Fene sif a gout t\u233?rsan a y\u233?nd yau t\u233?netan \u225?mb ghak\u233?r si fene sif m\u233?r\u233?nm\u233?n. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 39\~}
Y\u233?ndon yau y\u233?n\u233?rsam\u233?n feyot \u225?mb w\u233?r\u225?r \u225?rk\u233?m\u233?nayam o t\u233?smangai k\u233?ghat w\u233?r\u225?ram; y\u233?nd fai kufrotan oling\u233?gh w\u233?r\u225?rot y\u233?ndio. Y\u233?nd kw\u233?m\u233?inde f\u233?mon m\u233?n\u225?t faiot m\u233?inyotio \u225?ligh w\u233?r\u225?rot efghon o s\u233?mb\u225?ran. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 40\~}
Y\u233?nd k\u225?s\u225?fotan feyot kw\u225?mnjote ram\u233?ram\u233? yam efghon a s\u233?mb\u225?ran kruf\u233?ran k\u233?m\u233?gh teslan. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 41\~}
Y\u233?nd kw\u233?morw\u233?n fene m\u233?r\u233?naf\u233? 20 yunj\u233?f s\u233?nonjo y\u233?nd n\u225?s\u225?fotam\u233?n feyot 14 yunj\u233?f fene s\u243?mbio m\u233?r\u233?sfet, 6 yunj\u233?f fene w\u233?r\u225?rot, a f\u233?mon w\u233?fai tane fai 100 mbinotm\u233?. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 42\~}
Njam tane afane Ng\u225?nj\u225?n, Ebraam a Aisekene Ng\u225?nj\u225?n yau t\u233?m y\u233?ndf\u233?, f\u233?mon so kw\u233?natembangai y\u233?nd firo s\u233?nonjo, w\u233?nde Ng\u225?nj\u225?nam t\u233?fande tane ndimbal k\u233?rt\u233? t\u233?fande a minde k\u225?s\u225?fotan, a kerker s\u233?mb\u225?ran y\u233?mon mbark\u225?nd yiy\u225?to."
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 43\~}
F\u233?yo Labanam yawangoy\u233?ng Jeikofe, "Y\u233?n\u233? sere tane m\u233?r\u233?s, tane \u225?kiambum, a tane sif m\u233?r\u233?n. M\u233?inyotio rokar f\u233?mon njam efanda em tane. N\u233?m\u233?w\u233?t y\u233?ndon so yafrotan s\u233?nonjo tane m\u233?r\u233?sofet a y\u233?fene ambumt\u233?rt\u233?rat? {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 44\~}
S\u233?nonjo, mato mwigh\u233? r\u233?ny\u233?gham so y\u233?kai nden\u233? fandagh\u233?t y\u233?n\u233? n\u233?ndk\u233?fan f\u233?m a y\u233?nd.
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 45\~}
Jeikofam t\u233?nkafang\u233? w\u237?m a s\u233?nagh ewafngoy\u233?ng nden\u233? f\u233?t\u233? fu. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 46\~}
F\u233?yo Jeikof norayay\u233?ng y\u225?ne f\u250?tarfefaf, "T\u233?naum\u233?ndangi \u225?mb w\u237?m, t\u233?kmetaw\u233?t wambre, a t\u233?netaw\u233?t njamke w\u237?m wamb\u233?r \u225?nde t\u233?kang\u233?rw\u233?n. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 47\~}
Y\u225?njo sie, Labanam t\u233?nmotang\u233? y\u233?tkw\u233?n Jeghar Saaduta, w\u233?nde Jeikofam t\u233?nmotang\u233? Galeed.
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 48\~}
