Njam Josef yanafem yinjo t\u233?nmorw\u233?n, y\u233?mofem y\u225?y\u225?mngoy\u233?nd nayuta, njam kaka n\u233?namdai, y\u233?mofem mwigh\u233? y\u233?faronam\u233?nd m\u233?n\u225?t so tesmetaw\u233?t krot. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 19\~}
F\u225? korayangi, "Y\u233?nan y\u233?n\u233?m onjo t\u233?fn\u225?r. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 20\~}
K\u233?naflangi so y\u233?smetam krot f\u225? a yitam y\u233?nan \u225?mb y\u233?kw\u233?t. Y\u233?ndfem so t\u233?mndang\u233?m t\u233?fene af\u233?, k\u233?ghat w\u233?r\u225?ram t\u233? t\u233?netat f\u225?, f\u233?yo y\u233?ndfem so y\u233?fandam n\u233?m\u233? y\u233?n\u233?m y\u225?ne onjom\u233?n!"
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 21\~}
W\u233?nde njam Riuben\u233?m n\u225?y\u225?retam y\u233?fene mwigh\u233? faror\u233?gh, f\u225? n\u233?namndai Josefe wanjargh\u233?t. F\u225? korayangi, "Yau so y\u233?setam krot. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 22\~}
N\u233?mat y\u233?ndfem so \u225?mb f\u233?r\u233?k? M\u233? so yitam y\u233?n\u233? sotro y\u233?kw\u233?t y\u233?na siy\u233?m fanfne yuwon." F\u233?yo f\u225? so k\u233?r y\u233?m t\u233?fene ng\u225?ng\u233? ngiofnaye." Riuben\u233?m kwankwane mwigh\u233? t\u225?itotau m\u233?n\u225?t s\u225?i tanjarngai Josef a tangotau k\u233?t\u225?n y\u225?refefaf. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 23\~}
Njam Josef nufary\u233?ng, y\u225?ne yanafem y\u233?fit\u233?rnam\u233?nd mer s\u225?l\u225?me \u225?rk\u233? f\u225? tawong\u233?rw\u233?n. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 24\~}
f\u233?yo y\u233?mofem yeray\u233?nd a yitam\u233?nd k\u233?nj\u250?t k\u233?t\u225?n y\u233?kw\u233?t. Y\u233?kw t\u233?morw\u233?n sotro; k\u233?t\u233? yau \u225?mb nu tukang\u233?rw\u233?n.
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 25\~}
Nden\u233?, njam m\u233? f\u225? tamorang\u233?rw\u233?n n\u233?net, f\u225? k\u233?retangi tuk\u233?t a tawinjongi karafan \u225?rk\u233? tanroghaw\u233?t kamelam nayum\u233? tanmorw\u233?n y\u233?fe tamb\u233?n, Y\u233?n\u233? m\u233?r\u233?n tamorw\u233?n Ismail \u225?r maniot rokar t\u233?rar\u233?gh \u225?r tarsagh\u233?t s\u233?f afoghare fam\u233?gh w\u233?kw\u233?r, ayatoghm\u233?n w\u233?kw\u233?r a mer wimaf\u233? w\u233?kw\u233?r k\u233?tam\u233? Giliad ta k\u233?t\u225?n Ijif\u233?t. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 26\~}
Judam tamndang\u233? y\u225?ne anaf, "N\u233?m\u233? y\u233?ndfem so tanang\u233?m m\u233?n\u225?yan njam y\u233?smetam t\u233?fene n\u233?ng\u233?n? Y\u233?ndfem so tafarng\u233?m n\u225?kaf\u233? yam. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 27\~}
W\u233?nde yau so y\u233?smetam f\u225?, so maniot t\u233?t\u233?rnang\u233?m y\u233?fefaf Ismail \u225?r rokar maniot t\u233?rar\u233?gh \u225?r m\u233?inyotio soram\u233? f\u225? siy\u233?m t\u233?fene n\u233?ng\u233?n, t\u233?fenjo fifi a f\u233?r\u233?k." Y\u225?ne yanafem yiy\u225?toy\u233?nd. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 28\~}
F\u233?yo njam Ismail \u225?r, efe tamorw\u233?n Midian \u225?rm\u233?n rokar maniot t\u233?rar\u233?gh \u225?r njam enmorm\u233?n, Josef yanafem yutory\u233?nd y\u233?kwta a y\u233?ramay\u233?nd maniot 20 mani mbweyot. A rokar t\u233?rar\u233?gh \u225?r\u233?m y\u233?ngwasroy\u233?nd k\u233?t\u225?n Ijif.
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 29\~}
\u193?mb efogh soram\u233?, Riuben n\u233?ngangoi m\u233?n\u225?t Josef s\u225?i y\u233?kwta turtongai, njam f\u225? n\u233?retai Josef yuk\u233?r t\u233?morw\u233?n, y\u233?mo y\u225?njo s\u225?l\u225?me y\u233?tirary\u233?ng y\u233?fe. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 30\~}
f\u233?yo f\u225? n\u233?ngangoi y\u225?njo y\u225?nafefaf a kawatarnau, "N\u233?m\u233? ambum t\u233? y\u233?ngwanangi. Y\u233?ndon n\u233?m\u233? yafrotan s\u233?nonjo?"
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 31\~}
F\u233?yo yanafem t\u233?smangi tot\u233?r gout a yukay\u233?nd Josefene s\u225?l\u225?me f\u233?rkan. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 32\~}
Y\u233?mofem y\u233?ngwatembay\u233?nd mer s\u225?l\u225?me y\u225?refefaf y\u233?n\u233? siaf\u233?, "T\u233?fanda y\u233?n\u233? y\u233?ndfem n\u233?m\u233? yinjong\u233?m y\u233?n\u233? s\u225?l\u225?me y\u233?m fene ambumoene?"
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 33\~}
Y\u233?ferafam yayangoi tekofnar, f\u225? korayang\u233?, "N\u233?m\u233?w\u233?t, y\u233?n\u233? siy\u233?m tane ambumoene s\u225?l\u225?me! A k\u233?ghat w\u233?r\u225?ram m\u233?t\u233? t\u225?f y\u233?nata, Josef safanro t\u233? t\u233?ftarnat kar\u233?fkarfot!" {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 34\~}
F\u233?yo Jeikof\u233?m t\u233?rirang\u233? y\u225?njo s\u225?l\u225?me a numanetam kar\u233?fkarfe, f\u225? ye kendau k\u233?nj\u250? tikfe y\u225?njo ambumoenem\u233?n tekfifi y\u233?rsam. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 35\~}
Y\u225?njo m\u233?rnam y\u233?ta tamarotaw\u233?t f\u225?. W\u233?nde y\u233?mo m\u233? tangkenau f\u225? s\u225?i tamorartaw\u233?t, "Tane w\u233?i so mb\u233?w\u233? m\u233?ngo, nendan tane ambumm\u233?n." F\u225? so korayau a w\u233?i so ye kufngongai.
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 36\~}
M\u233? tekofnar, midian \u225?rm\u233?n maniot t\u233?rar\u233?gh \u225?r nufary\u233?nd Ijif\u233?t, \u225?ndan y\u233?mofem y\u233?ternay\u233?nd maniot Fotifarefaf ofis \u225?s\u225?fogh \u225?r Faraoene warsagh \u225?r Ijifm\u233?n Folifa t\u233?morw\u233?n s\u233?nko \u225?r warsagh \u225?roene lim\u225?n\u233?gh \u225?mnjogh sifay\u233? wamb\u233?ghfaf.
