\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 1\~}
Y\u233?n\u233? Efghon Judam y\u233?frangoi m\u233?ngotu a nimndai k\u233?t\u225?n Adulam, \u225?nde f\u225? tamorw\u233?n y\u233?maf\u233? \u225?r y\u233?tkw\u233?n Ira. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 2\~}
K\u233?t\u233? y\u233?mo yinjoi Kananm\u233?n amaf, Suane m\u233?r\u233?s, a y\u233?mo nawerai. Njam y\u233?maf\u233? ekmorm\u233?n, {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 3\~}
f\u225? n\u233?namndai suaf\u233? a y\u225?r\u225?ftam ambum, a y\u233?mo y\u233?tkw\u233?n yaramai ambumoe Er. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 4\~}
F\u233?yo w\u233?i amaf n\u233?namndai suaf\u233? a y\u225?raf \u225?mb ambum, a amafom y\u233?tkw\u233?n taramang\u233? Onan. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 5\~}
A njam y\u225?r\u225?ftam nambiom\u233?n ambum amafom y\u233?tkw\u233?n taramang\u233? Sela. K\u233?t\u233? Selane \u225?r\u225?f\u233?gh efghon. F\u225? k\u233?t\u233? t\u225?kmang\u233?rw\u233?n k\u233?t\u233? Kejib.
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 6\~}
Y\u233?n\u233? efogh njam karsau, Judam end efrendam y\u225?njo fronde s\u233?nko ambumoe, Er, m\u233?n\u225?t so kawerangai tot\u233?r m\u233?r\u233?s y\u233?tkw\u233?n Tamar. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 7\~}
W\u233?nde Er t\u233?morw\u233?n yaufi \u225?r Yurane s\u225?fr\u233?re, f\u233?yo Yuram y\u225?ne gh\u233?rs\u233? yangoi. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 8\~}
F\u233?yo Juda korayang\u233? Erene ghakroefaf Onan, "K\u233?ng\u233?m a kawer Tamar, nden\u233? f\u233?t\u233? t\u233?fene n\u225?k yumyote nden\u233? f\u233?t\u233? y\u225?ne y\u225?nng\u233?n efe k\u233?r t\u233?m. F\u233?mo so engweunjete ambum fene anai." {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 9\~}
W\u233?nde Onan m\u233?ndefnar t\u233?morw\u233?n m\u233?n\u225?t ambumaf\u233? s\u225?i t\u233?morw\u233?n efe so t\u233?morw\u233?n y\u225?ne sifayan, f\u233?yo njam kawanw\u233?t yanane amafof\u233?, y\u233?mo tasunau nj\u233?ng\u233?r mbandot, m\u233?n\u225?t amafom yau so tinjongai ambum efe so t\u233?morw\u233?n yanai. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 10\~}
W\u233?nde Ng\u225?nj\u225?nam t\u233?fandau yaufi Onanene m\u233?ndefnar stamorw\u233?n ambumot y\u225?ne k\u233?r anai. F\u233?yo yuram yangoi Onanene gh\u233?rs\u233? w\u233?i. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 11\~}
F\u233?yo Judam t\u233?mndang\u233? Tamar y\u225?ki amaf, "Ngangot a fene ferafafefaf m\u233?ngotuot a m\u233? n\u233?mor kwir\u233? k\u233?t\u225?n tane ambum Sela njam k\u225?y\u225?tong\u233? ndimbal so k\u233?marong\u233? f\u233?m." W\u233?nde Judam yau y\u233?n\u233? m\u233?n\u225?t tiy\u225?totau nden\u233? y\u233?n\u233? s\u225?i kufrotau m\u233?nam\u233?n f\u225? f\u233?rf\u233?r t\u233?morw\u233?n Sela w\u233?i so k\u233?r t\u233?morw\u233?n, nden\u233? y\u225?ne s\u243?mbio yanaf. F\u233?yo Tamar nangoi t\u225?kmang\u233?rw\u233?n y\u225?refaf\u233? m\u233?ngotuan.
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 12\~}
\u193?mb yunj\u233?f soram\u233? Judane amaf k\u233?r y\u233?morw\u233?n, y\u233?n\u233? ye soram\u233?,, Juda a y\u225?ne f\u250?tar Ira a Adulam \u225?r engmorm\u233?n k\u233?t\u225?n timna, m\u233?n\u225?t so talimndau sif n\u233?fghan. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 13\~}
\u193?mb \u225?rom yaufroi Tamare, "K\u233?reta, fene \u225?ki n\u233?wano k\u233?t\u225?n Timnat m\u233?n\u225?t s\u225?i enfeta y\u225?ne sif, " {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 14\~}
Tamar mataf\u233? t\u233?morw\u233?n nden\u233? Sela t\u233? nanotam, w\u233?nde yau freng\u233?gh yam y\u233?morm\u233?n y\u225?yot m\u233?n\u225?t s\u225?i kawerayay\u233?nd y\u233?maf\u233? f\u233?yo y\u233?mo efitarnam kwir\u233? s\u225?l\u225?me a nawafary\u233?ng s\u225?l\u225?meye m\u233?n\u225?t atambar\u233?ghe so t\u233?morw\u233?n f\u225?. F\u233?yo n\u225?mnjoi end s\u233?safnen t\u233?kmang\u233?rw\u233?n Enaim m\u233?ngotuot, \u225?rk\u233? y\u233?m end\u233?n k\u233?t\u225?n Timnat.
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 15\~}
Judam tayamngoi f\u225? a kemnau kar t\u233?morw\u233?n end okayogh \u225?r m\u233?r\u233?s, t\u233? w\u233?nde yafroy\u233?ng s\u225?f. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 16\~}
F\u233?yo f\u225? k\u233?kmbong\u233? a tarmenau f\u225?,, "Y\u233?ndf\u233? so naf\u233?gh wam f\u233?maf\u233?."
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 Tamar\u233?m t\u233?motang\u233?, "F\u233?m njamb so fai nufrote njam f\u233?maf\u233? y\u233?nd naf\u233?gh w\u233?m?"
