Judam uny\u233?ghofnar si w\u233?mndai, "Y\u233?ndon so k\u233?nmawatemban tot\u233?r gout k\u233?tam\u233? tane m\u233?r\u233?nta."
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 M\u233?rsom t\u233?motang\u233?,, "N\u233?m\u233? f\u233?mo so kwaram ta yatogh\u233?t nden\u233? f\u233?mo so y\u233?nmafarete gout?"
