Y\u233?mo t\u233?motang\u233?, "N\u233?m\u233? m\u233?ndefifi f\u233?m n\u233?m?"
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 M\u233?rsom tawangong\u233?, "Kauro ta fenem\u233?n ndindi a \u225?lighm\u233?n w\u233?tu f\u233?mo siy\u233?rse." F\u233?yo Judam taramang\u233? y\u225?. F\u233?yo y\u233?maf\u233? yau nufngeyay\u233?nd, a m\u233?r\u233?s n\u233?namndai suaf\u233?. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 19\~}
Soram\u233? m\u233?r\u233?s nangotam m\u233?ngotuot, y\u233?fitrary\u233?ng awamogh s\u225?l\u225?me a nawoi kor kwir\u233? s\u225?l\u225?me.
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 20\~}
Soram\u233? Judam y\u233?motai y\u225?njo f\u250?tar Iran Adulam \u225?r m\u233?n\u225?t s\u225?i t\u233?ngwanang\u233? tot\u233?r gout k\u233?t\u225?n amafoefaf a takafengai y\u233?n\u233? rokar y\u233?mo \u225?rk\u233? yaramai m\u233?rsoe nden\u233? y\u225?ne r\u233?ny\u233?gh, w\u233?nde Iran\u233?m yau yinjoi m\u233?r\u233?s. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 21\~}
F\u233?yo tamotang\u233? \u225?mb efe t\u225?kmang\u233?rw\u233?n k\u233?t\u233?, "\u193?nde so tinjon y\u233?n\u233? end areng\u233?gh \u225?r m\u233?r\u233?s efe t\u233?morang\u233?rw\u233?n ende t\u233?ndon k\u233?t\u233? Enaim end s\u233?safnefaf"
