Y\u233?nam\u233? Faraom y\u225? fitrary\u233?ng y\u225?njo ufarogh ng\u225?ng\u233? y\u225?njo ng\u225?ngata a yanyawai Josefene ng\u225?ng\u233?ng\u225?ngayan. Y\u233?mo yamanetam mer s\u225?l\u225?meye a tawamang\u233? golm\u233?n sein y\u225?ne k\u233?mam\u233?. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 43\~}
f\u233?yo yumyoi Josef s\u225?i t\u233?rsau kariotan yamndai k\u233?t\u225?n y\u225?ne y\u233?namayo yam. A \u225?rk\u233? Josef tiyotau wafarogh waft\u233? t\u233? yaramai. "Mbudme niyai!" F\u233?yo Faraom y\u233?kai Ijif yu wanjeng\u233?gh\u233?t.
