F\u233?yo Faraom yaramai tot\u233?r y\u233?tkw\u233?n Josefe Jafenat-Fanea a y\u233?mo w\u233?i taramai amaf, endene y\u233?tkw\u233?n t\u233?morw\u233?n Asenat, m\u233?r\u233?s t\u233?morw\u233?n Fotiferane, Onene gh\u233?ng\u233?n w\u225?rogh \u225?roene. Josefem yanai fandagh\u233?t m\u233?inyotio Ijif mband.
