F\u225? t\u233?morw\u233?n 30 yunj\u233?f anogh njam y\u233?mo y\u233?rnau \u225?s\u225?fogh Faraone utman\u233?gh \u225?s\u225?fogh sifayan, Ijifm\u233?n warsagh \u225?r. A njam Josefem norai Faraone sifay\u233?. Y\u233?mo t\u225?y\u225?fotau m\u233?inyotio yu Ijif\u233?n. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 47\~}
Nden\u233? k\u233?s korayau 7 yunj\u233?f f\u233?yotaro mbandan t\u233?funau s\u233?f njamke. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 48\~}
Y\u233?n\u233? yunjfan, Josefem tumendau m\u233?inyotio njamke skanotaw\u233?t k\u233?t\u233? Ijif\u233?n a t\u233?nyawetaw\u233?t flaw\u233? y\u233?nam\u233? wareng\u233?gh \u225?r ndauta ndimbal tesenam\u233?. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 49\~}
Y\u233?mo tarmbotau flaw\u233? taretare tawanong\u233?rw\u233?n ndenanit arakaf miri wifoghfaf, f\u225? n\u233?kmboi t\u233?reft\u233?ref r\u233?sagh m\u233?nam\u233?n mindefifi t\u233?morw\u233?n waf\u233?gh\u233?t.
