Y\u233?n\u233? efghon, \u225?mb kaukau yunj\u233?f s\u225?i karnyangai, s\u243?mbio ambum Josefene erafm\u233?ng y\u225?ne amafom, Asenat, Fotiferane m\u233?rsom, gh\u233?ng\u233?n w\u225?rogh \u225?r. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 51\~}
Josefem fronde s\u233?nko ambumoe y\u233?tkw\u233?n yaramai M\u233?nase, m\u233?nam\u233?n Ng\u225?nj\u225?nam t\u233? wiy\u225?tong tawitan mwighafnar m\u233?inyotio tane k\u233?rt\u233? a m\u233?inyotio \u225?r tane afane m\u233?r\u233?n k\u233?nj\u250?n." {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 52\~}
Josefem y\u233?namayo ambumoe y\u233?tkw\u233?n yaramai Ifraim, f\u225? norayai, "Ng\u225?nj\u225?nam t\u233? wiy\u225?to mbwe k\u233?r ro y\u233?n\u233? mbandan tane mwigh\u233? k\u233?rtata."
