Ambinom\u233?n 7m\u233?n yunjfan funau njamke y\u233?nam\u233? m\u233?inyotio Ijif mbandan enmorm\u233?n n\u233?nefoy\u233?nd. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 54\~}
F\u233?yo 7 yunj\u233?f f\u233?yotaro kaukau nufary\u233?ng nden\u233? f\u233?t\u233? Josef ndern\u225?ye norayam kaukau wam w\u233?i ewanai \u225?mb kaka yu, w\u233?nde Ijif k\u233?nj\u250?n k\u233?t\u233? tamorw\u233?n t\u225?rf\u225?r njamke. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 55\~}
F\u233?yo ndern\u225?ye kaukau nuyan m\u233?inyotio Ijif mbandan nden\u225?ye f\u233?t\u233? a njam \u225?r kutnaw\u233?t Faraofaf njamket, y\u233?mo tamndangai tang\u233?m Josefefaf, a ewafrotati ndern\u225?ye y\u233?mo njam emndeta f\u233?m.
