A \u225?r y\u233?nam\u233? \u225?mb t\u233?ndota tanmorw\u233?n Ijifet m\u233?n\u225?t mani so tang\u233?rsaw\u233?t flaw\u233? Josefeta m\u233?nam\u233?n kaukau t\u233?morw\u233?n awamb\u233?ghaf\u233? m\u233?inyotio mband maratan.
