Y\u233?nd t\u233? n\u225?y\u225?ran nden\u233? flaw\u233? k\u233?t\u233? y\u233?m Ijif\u233?n. Kuwanangi k\u233?t\u225?n, a tanwanangi t\u233?fe f\u233?yotaro flaw\u233? m\u233?n\u225?t so m\u233? y\u233?n\u233?m gh\u233?rs\u233? m\u233?nam\u233?n k\u233?r w\u233?m y\u233?n\u233?m."
