W\u233?nde Jeikof\u233?m yau yumyoi Josefe waitogh y\u233?feng\u233?nfifi Benjamin, y\u233?maf\u233? s\u225?i tangmorw\u233?n, f\u233?rf\u233?rm\u233?n t\u233?morw\u233?n nden\u233? \u225?mb k\u233?rt\u233? yam m\u233?t\u233? t\u225?f t\u233?rang\u233?. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 5\~}
