Josefem m\u233? ewayamngoi yanaf tekofnar, w\u233?nde f\u225? kundau nden\u233? wan t\u233?fn\u225?r kar t\u233?morw\u233?n korayang\u233? t\u233?krate y\u233?fefaf, "Naim\u233?n f\u233?m em?"
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 Y\u233?mofem tawangongi, "Y\u233?nd t\u233?n\u233?m m\u233?n\u225?t njamke s\u225?i tawanang\u233?m."
