A y\u233?mo kawafarotang\u233? onjofaf y\u233?kmang\u233?rm\u233?n y\u233?fenem\u233?n t\u225?nd\u225?i yunjfan fronde, y\u233?mo tamnda, "F\u233?m em yafogh \u225?r! F\u233?m m\u233?n\u225?t tan\u233?m fandagh\u233?t nder\u233? wayamneghaf\u233? t\u233?fene mband t\u233? n\u233?namnde."
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 10\~}
