Y\u233?nd y\u233?n\u233?m m\u233?inyotio m\u233?r\u233?n k\u233?tam\u233? \u225?mbiro m\u233?r\u233?nta. Y\u233?nd y\u233?n\u233?m efalo \u225?r, ndimbal! Y\u233?nd yau y\u233?n\u233?m yafogh \u225?r!"
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 12\~}
Josefem tawawangotau, "A, f\u233?m f\u233?t\u233? em. F\u233?m t\u233? tan\u233?m fandagh\u233?t nder\u233? wayamneghaf\u233? t\u233?fene mband t\u233? namnd\u233?."
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 13\~}
F\u225? korayangi, "Ndimbal, y\u233?na y\u233?n\u233?m 12ro y\u233?nd, fene \u225?s\u225?fogh t\u233?fn\u225?r y\u233?nd y\u233?n\u233?m y\u233?nd m\u233?r\u233?n, ambum y\u225?ne \u225?r efe y\u233?mor k\u233?t\u233? Kanan mbandan. T\u233?fene n\u233?ng\u233?n k\u233?t\u233? m\u233? fiy\u233?m y\u233?maf\u233? t\u233?fene afafe s\u233?nonjo, a \u225?mb m\u233?r\u233?n yau w\u233?i y\u233?na y\u233?ndf\u233?."
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 14\~}
W\u233?nde Josefene m\u233? tawawangotau, "Nden\u233? y\u233?nd k\u233?s norayang\u233?n f\u233?m em yafogh \u225?r! {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 15\~}
Nden\u233? so f\u233?fene afrogh y\u233?ndon yufotan. Y\u233?nd norayan Faraone gh\u233?rsaye nden\u233? f\u233?mofem yau so korongi Ijif t\u225?fandro f\u233?fene f\u233?feng\u233?n njam y\u233?n\u233?m y\u233?nan. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 16\~}
\u193?mb f\u233?m t\u225?f nguwano a t\u233?nmasro f\u233?fene n\u233?ng\u233?n. Y\u233?ndon f\u233?m m\u233?inyotio m\u233? so eweretan y\u233?na kw\u233?fkw\u233?f m\u233?ngon. F\u233?yo y\u233?ndfem kor so y\u233?ronjam f\u233?fene afrogh so y\u233?m efalo o yau, Faraone gh\u233?rsaye yau njam y\u233?m f\u233?fene n\u233?ng\u233?n, f\u233?yo y\u233?nd mat so w\u233?m f\u233?m em yufogh \u225?r." {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 17\~}
F\u233?yo Josefem enyawai kw\u233?fkw\u233?f m\u233?ngon nambio efogh.
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 18\~}
