Njam fem em efalofifi \u225?r, t\u233?kafangi \u225?mb f\u233?fene m\u233?r\u233?nm\u233?n efe so karongi kw\u233?fkw\u233?f m\u233?ngon, \u225?mb f\u233?m m\u233?inyotio t\u233?u n\u233?ngangotati m\u233?ngotuot flawaf\u233? k\u233?t\u225?n f\u233?fene m\u233?r\u233?n siogh k\u233?s em. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 20\~}
W\u233?nde t\u225?f y\u233?nmangotati k\u233?rt\u233?r f\u233?feng\u233?n tafaf. Y\u233?nayam so taufarng\u233? nden\u233? f\u233?mofem f\u233?t\u233? wauferotati efaloe, a f\u233?m yau so k\u233?r em."
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 Y\u233?n\u233? m\u233?n\u225?t f\u225? namyoy\u233?nd. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 21\~}
Korayaw\u233?t y\u233?fenjo k\u233?nj\u250?nro, nden\u233? norayay\u233?nd, "Saf\u233?nro y\u233?nd mawersote m\u233?nam\u233?n n\u233?m\u233? y\u233?ndfem yafrotam\u233?m Josefefaf t\u225?nd\u225?i y\u233?ndfem t\u233? yinjong\u233?m y\u225?ne k\u233?rt\u233? njam f\u225? y\u233?ta kametau y\u225?njo gh\u233?rsat, w\u233?nde yau k\u225?y\u225?retaw\u233?m. Y\u233?n\u233? t\u233?fnan y\u233?nd y\u233?n\u233?m y\u233?n\u233? k\u233?rtayan."
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 22\~}
Riuben\u233?m tamotang\u233?, "Y\u233?ndon yau ewaufroy\u233?n f\u233?fe yau s\u225?i yaufiyam tafrotau ambum? W\u233?nde f\u233?m yau k\u225?y\u225?retaw\u233?t! A s\u233?nonjo y\u233?ndfem so f\u233?t\u233? tawangong\u233?m y\u225?ne f\u233?r\u233?km\u233?n." {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 23\~}
W\u233?nde yau mat n\u225?y\u225?toy\u233?nd nden\u233? Josefem t\u233? mat namndai y\u233?fenem\u233?n, m\u233?nam\u233?n f\u225? korayau k\u233?nj\u250?m\u233? si wafer\u233?gh t\u233?fn\u225?rafafm\u233?.
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 24\~}
Y\u233?nam\u233? y\u233?mo sem ewawengoi y\u233?fe ye nufngoi. Njam ye nefoi, y\u233?mo korayang\u233? y\u233?fefaf w\u233?ikor, f\u233?yo y\u233?mo t\u233?kafang\u233? Simion y\u233?fene k\u233?nj\u250?n a yumbetam\u233?nd y\u233?fene gh\u233?kfan.
