Njam y\u233?mofem kaka t\u233?ngy\u225?totaw\u233?t y\u233?fene \u225?lighan Jeikof\u233?m y\u225?f\u225?retam Juda fronde Josef s\u225?i t\u233?f\u225?ngongai a tanangai mat si y\u233?n\u233? yum\u233?n Gosen. A njam k\u233?t\u233? f\u225? nufary\u233?nd. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 29\~}
Josefem y\u233?frendam y\u225?njo Karot a n\u233?nengoi y\u233?nan Gosen y\u225?ref\u233? Jeikof t\u233?nmafetau. Njam Josef n\u233?nufary\u233?ng, y\u233?mo yambnai y\u225?ref\u233? a kendau, teretau f\u225? tekfifi. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 30\~}
Ambinom\u233?n Jeikof\u233?m t\u233?mndang\u233? Josef, "S\u233?nonjo y\u233?nd afreng\u233?ghkaf w\u233?m s\u225?i k\u233?r w\u233?m. Y\u233?ndon t\u233? yinjon fene s\u225?f w\u233?ikor a s\u233?nonjo f\u233?m m\u233? n\u233?m gh\u233?rs\u233?."
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 31\~}
A Josefem tamndang\u233? y\u225?ne yanaf a y\u225?refane m\u233?r\u233?n m\u233?inyotio, "Y\u233?nd so w\u233?ng\u233?m k\u233?t\u233? Faraofaf a taufron, tane anaf a afane m\u233?inyotio m\u233?r\u233?n t\u233?fe fen\u233?m y\u233?nan tafaf k\u233?tam\u233? Kanan yuta. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 32\~}
Y\u233?n\u233? \u225?r sem sif wanjeng\u233?gh \u225?r, a y\u233?mofem emanjanat w\u233?r\u225?r. Y\u233?mofem t\u233?fe fen\u233?mnjat y\u233?fene w\u233?r\u225?r rokar a m\u233?inyotio y\u233?fene rokar n\u233?m\u233? tawam. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 33\~}
F\u233?yo f\u225? korayang\u233?, "Njam Faraom tawanmong\u233? f\u233?m a tamotang\u233? f\u233?fene sifayam\u233?n? {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 34\~}
f\u233?mofem t\u225?f t\u233?mndangi, y\u233?nd, fene \u225?s\u225?fogh t\u233?fn\u225?r, t\u233? tawanotam t\u233?fene w\u233?r\u225?r t\u233?fene gh\u233?rsayan, nden\u233? t\u233?fene \u225?kifem t\u250?m\u233?n tawafrotaw\u233?t? Njam f\u233?mofem t\u233?mndangi nden\u233? y\u233?mo so f\u233?m taumyong\u233? fem s\u225?i emo y\u233?na Gosen\u233?n, m\u233?nam\u233?n Ijif \u225?r\u233?m ekarotat sif wanjeng\u233?gh \u225?r.
\par\pard\plain \s52\ql\fi0\lin0\rin0\sb160\sa80\b\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs33 47
\par\pard\plain \s105\qc\fi0\lin0\rin0\sb160\sa80\b\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 Jeikof\u233?m y\u233?frend Farao
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 1\~}
F\u233?yo Josef kuwanong\u233? Farao fandagh\u233?t a taufrong\u233?, "Tane af\u233? a anaf t\u233? nufarngi k\u233?tam\u233? Kanan mbandta. F\u225? t\u233? tan\u233?m m\u233?inyotio manjar\u233?gh w\u233?r\u225?raf\u233? a y\u233?fene \u225?s\u225?fogh sifay\u233?, a f\u225? s\u233?nonjo em y\u233?n\u233? yuwon Gosen." {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 2\~}
Josefem engwasroi 5 yanaf a euyafoi f\u225? Faraofaf.
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 3\~}
A Faraom tamotang\u233? Josefe yanaf, "F\u233?fene sifay\u233? \u225?nde y\u233?m?"
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 Y\u233?mofem yawangoy\u233?nd, "Y\u233?nd fene \u225?s\u225?fogh t\u233?fn\u225?r, y\u233?n\u233?m sif wanjeng\u233?gh \u225?r nden\u233? f\u233?t\u233? t\u233?fene \u225?kif.
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 4\~}
Y\u233?nd t\u233? t\u233?n\u233?m y\u233?nan \u225?mnjogh\u233?t Ijif\u233?t tekofnar, k\u233?t\u233? yau kor y\u233?m yus t\u233?fene w\u233?r\u225?rot Kanan\u233?n, kaukau siy\u233?m mindefifi k\u233?t\u233?. Y\u233?ndfem y\u233?rsam mat si m\u233?n\u225?t s\u225?i y\u233?nmor Gosen\u233?n." {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 5\~}
F\u233?yo Faraom t\u233?mndang\u233? Josef, "S\u233?nonjo fene af\u233? a m\u233?rnam t\u233? n\u233?mafnangi y\u233?na, {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 6\~}
t\u233?kaf \u225?mb sifay\u233? y\u233?na Ijif\u233?n y\u233?feyot \u225?mnjogh\u233?t tawaram merfifi mband Ijifm\u233?n. So emor k\u233?t\u233? Gosen\u233?n, efe em f\u233?nat\u233? tamb\u233?naf\u233?, tak\u233?m tane w\u233?r\u225?r wanjeng\u233?t w\u233?i."
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 7\~}
F\u233?yo Josefem t\u233?nmasrong\u233? y\u225?ref\u233? Jeikof, a yuyafoi Faraofaf a Jeikof\u233?m y\u233?frendai Farao, {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 8\~}
a Faraom t\u233?motang\u233? f\u225?, "Nj\u233?namb yunj\u233?f fene em?"
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 9\~}
Jeikof\u233?m yawangoi, "Y\u233?ndo t\u233? karandan y\u233?n\u233? mbandan k\u233?t\u225?n 130 t\u225?ik\u233?raf\u233? yunj\u233?f. W\u233?nde tane gh\u233?rs\u233? t\u233? n\u233?namnde t\u233?njfi njam tangon k\u233?t\u225?n tane t\u225?rf\u225?r \u225?kiambum." {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 10\~}
F\u233?yo Jeikof\u233?m kor y\u233?frende w\u233?i Farao soram\u233? y\u233?n\u233?rangoi y\u225?ne lim\u225?n\u233?gh \u225?mnjogh sifay\u233?. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 11\~}
F\u233?yo Josefem yanai merfifi mband Ijif\u233?n, y\u233?n\u233? yuwan Rameses, y\u225?refai a y\u225?ne m\u233?r\u233?n, y\u233?mo k\u233?t\u233? ewauyafoi y\u233?fe \u225?mnjogh\u233?t, nden\u233? f\u233?t\u233? Faraom ndern\u225?ye ewafaretai. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 12\~}
A Josefem njamke ram\u233?gh tawawafngong\u233? y\u225?refai a y\u225?ne m\u233?rnat y\u233?n\u233? f\u233?yotaroyan awaf\u233?ghan t\u233? emorm\u233?n y\u225?ne \u225?kiambum, y\u233?mafayo n\u233?mbnar ambumt\u233?rt\u233?r.
\par\pard\plain \s105\qc\fi0\lin0\rin0\sb160\sa80\b\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 Josefene lim\u225?n\u233?gh kaukau k\u233?nj\u250?n
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 13\~}
Tekofnar siogh kaukau mindefifi nd\u233?mkef\u233? a m\u233?inyotio njamke ewifoy\u233?nd a \u225?r sioghan tarsau Ijif yuwon a Kanan. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 14\~}
M\u233?nayan maniot stat\u233?rnau flaw\u233? \u225?r\u233?t, Josefem t\u250?m\u233?n mani takafetau k\u233?t\u233? Ijif\u233?n a Kanan\u233?n, a y\u233?mo t\u225?kmangai mani Faraone mani yaf\u233?n. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 15\~}
Njam Ijif a Kananm\u233?n \u225?r sot k\u225?y\u225?tongay\u233?nd manian, m\u233?inyotio Ijif \u225?r tanmorw\u233?n Josefefaf, a f\u225? kutnang\u233? y\u233?n\u233?, "T\u233?fene mani t\u233? nefongi! T\u233?nmaram t\u233?fe njamke, o y\u233?nd so k\u233?r y\u233?n\u233?m fene gh\u233?kfanyo."
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 16\~}
Josefem tawawangongi, "F\u233?fene mani k\u233?s nefongi, kwaramangi f\u233?fene manjar\u233?gh w\u233?r\u225?r. Y\u233?ndo so ewarametan njamke y\u233?n\u233? t\u233?rar\u233?gh w\u233?r\u225?ran." {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 17\~}
F\u233?yo y\u233?mofem t\u233?n\u233?rsaw\u233?t manjar\u233?gh w\u233?r\u225?r Josefefaf njamke t\u233?rargh\u233?t, a t\u233?rar\u233?gh y\u233?naye y\u233?fene ose, manjar\u233?gh w\u233?r\u225?r nden\u233? sif, gout, kau a ndonki, Josefem taw\u225?ut\u225?nau njamkeye w\u233?i \u225?mb yunj\u233?f.
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 18\~}
W\u233?nde y\u233?n\u233? yiy\u225?tong\u233?rm\u233?n, a w\u233?i \u225?mb yunj\u233?f f\u225? tanmorw\u233?n a korayangi, "Y\u233?ndfem yau so yitnota efalo fe tamb\u233?n, tane ndimbal, t\u233?fene mani t\u233? nefongi, a m\u233?inyotio t\u233?fene manjar\u233?gh w\u233?r\u225?r a kau em fene. T\u233?fene \u225?mb n\u233?m\u233? yau nafrangongi w\u233?nde t\u233?fene fifiro a t\u233?fene mband. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 19\~}
Y\u233?nd n\u233?mam\u233?n so k\u233?r y\u233?n\u233?m fene gh\u233?kfan, t\u233?nman y\u233?nd a t\u233?fene mband njamke faie. Y\u233?mofem erametam t\u233?fene mband a y\u233?ndyo s\u225?i y\u233?n\u233?m faiofnar \u225?s\u225?fogh \u225?r Farao, m\u233? t\u233?nmaram flaw\u233? m\u233?n\u225?t y\u233?nd m\u233? gh\u233?rs\u233? so y\u233?ng\u233?m a yau so k\u233?r y\u233?n\u233?m, a mband yau so k\u233?namndang\u233? sotro a safro."
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 20\~}
F\u233?yo Josefem yanai Ijif mband y\u225?yot Farao. M\u233?inyotio Ijif \u225?r\u233?m maniot tat\u233?rnaw\u233?t Josefefaf mband m\u233?nam\u233?n kaukau t\u233?morw\u233?n minde nd\u233?mkef\u233?, a tekofnar m\u233?inyotio mband namndai Faraone. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 21\~}
\u193?r y\u233?mo ey\u225?toi faiofnar \u225?s\u225?fogh \u225?r m\u233?inyotio, k\u233?tam\u233? \u225?mb Ijif mband f\u233?d k\u233?t\u225?n \u225?mb mband f\u233?d. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 22\~}
M\u233? y\u233?naro mband y\u233?mo \u225?rk\u233?m\u233?n\u233? yau yanai mband \u225?rk\u233?m\u233?n\u233? t\u233?morw\u233?n gh\u233?ng\u233?n w\u225?rogh t\u233?fn\u225?rafene. Y\u233?mofem tarsaw\u233?t m\u233?naye njamke mbark\u225?ndaye k\u233?tam\u233? Faraota, f\u233?yo yau m\u233?nde tamorw\u233?n s\u225?i maniot t\u233?t\u233?rnangay\u233?nd y\u233?fene mband.
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 23\~}
F\u233?yo Josef korayang\u233? \u225?rfefaf, "K\u233?retangi, s\u233?nonjo y\u233?ndo t\u233? yanan f\u233?fene mband Faraoi, y\u233?ndon so ewarametan mbwe so eutati ndauam\u233?. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 24\~}
A njam f\u233?mofem ef\u233?rnati, \u225?mbiro 50m\u233?n mbwe so em Faraoi. F\u233?mofem t\u233?u ewangotati 4 5m\u233?n afrangogh mbwe f\u233?fenjo ndauot a n\u233?net f\u233?fenjo, f\u233?fen m\u233?ngot a ambumt\u233?rt\u233?r."
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 25\~}
F\u225? korayangi, "F\u233?mo t\u233? t\u233?fene gh\u233?rs\u233? ewanjar! So \u225?uw\u233?ghaf\u233? nuy\u225?tote, tane ndimbal, m\u233?n\u225?t s\u225?i y\u233?nd y\u233?nmumyota s\u225?i y\u233?n\u233?m Faraone \u225?s\u225?fogh \u225?r." {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 26\~}
Josefem y\u233?ramai w\u233?i n\u225?k m\u233? t\u233?morw\u233?n waftaf\u233? Ijif mbandan nden\u233? Faraom so t\u233?rsau \u225?mbiro 5m\u233?n m\u233?inyotio mbwem\u233?n skanotaw\u233?t y\u225?njo mbandan. M\u233? y\u233?n\u233? mband st\u233?morw\u233?n gh\u233?ng\u233?n w\u225?rogh \u225?rfene yau tarametaw\u233?t y\u233?n\u233?mam\u233?n Faraoi.
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 27\~}
Tekofnar Israil \u225?r\u233?m m\u233?ngotu yafrotam\u233?nd Gosen yuwon Ijif k\u233?nj\u250?n, k\u233?t\u233? y\u233?mofem ewanay\u233?nd rokar a tamorw\u233?n mbwe k\u233?r ro, a \u225?r m\u233?r\u233?n n\u225?y\u225?toi t\u225?rf\u225?r m\u233? k\u233?nayototau w\u233?keyero. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 28\~}
Jeikof y\u233?morang\u233?rm\u233?n 17 yunj\u233?f soram\u233? nufary\u233?ng Ijif\u233?t, m\u233?inyotio y\u225?ne \u225?mnjogh y\u233?morm\u233?n 147 yunj\u233?f. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 29\~}
Njam y\u225?ne k\u233?rm\u233?n kaka k\u233?nayatotau, Jeikof\u233?m y\u233?ngwarawetam y\u225?njo ambum Josef a t\u233?mndang\u233? f\u225?, "T\u225?f m\u225?m\u233? wawafrota tane m\u233?nde, tak\u233?m fenjo ng\u225?ng\u233? tane buraber mbandmbandam\u233? a koraya nden\u233? f\u233?mo so warawe ndimbal uw\u233?ghe s\u225?i ut\u233?mnda \u225?mbirom\u233?n amyogh. Yau t\u225?f mband kwaram Ijif\u233?n, {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 30\~}
w\u233?nde njam k\u233?r w\u233?m, t\u225?f mbana tane fifi t\u233?ngutorngi y\u233?nam\u233? Ijifta a mband kwaramangi k\u233?t\u233? \u225?nde tane \u225?kif ey\u225?to."
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 F\u233?yo Josef uny\u233?ghofnar si norayai, "Y\u233?ndon so yafrotau f\u233?m ke n\u243?mnenda."
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 31\~}
Jeikof m\u233?njtaye m\u233? korayau, "Koraya nden\u233? f\u233?mo yafrote." F\u233?yo Josef sot\u233? norayai, a Jeikof n\u225?wefnoi m\u233?tare k\u233?m\u233?gh s\u233?nko tafalota.
\par\pard\plain \s52\ql\fi0\lin0\rin0\sb160\sa80\b\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs33 48
\par\pard\plain \s105\qc\fi0\lin0\rin0\sb160\sa80\b\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 Jeikof\u233?m efrengw\u233? M\u233?nase a Ifraim
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 1\~}
\u193?mbiro efogh soram\u233?, si y\u233?nmorm\u233?n Josefefaf, "Feraf\u233? nuite m\u225?m\u233?gh\u233?raye." F\u233?yo Josef y\u233?ngmorm\u233?n y\u225?ref\u233? yafogh\u233?t, a y\u233?mo engwasreyai y\u225?njo s\u243?mbio ambum, M\u233?nase a Ifraim. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 2\~}
