T\u225?rf\u225?r yunj\u233?f soram\u233?, njam Moses nanotam, f\u225? y\u233?ngmorm\u233?n yafogh\u233?t y\u225?njo \u225?rfefaf, Ibrum\u233?n, a y\u233?mo ewinjoi nder\u233? m\u233?njtaye f\u225? tawafaretaw\u233?t m\u233?n\u225?t \u225?s\u225?fogh\u233?t, t\u225?f y\u225?ne yafoghan. Y\u233?mo yinjoi \u225?mb Ijif\u233?n t\u233?smetau \u225?mb y\u225?ne Ibrum\u233?n \u225?r. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 12\~}
Matataye fronde n\u233?retam m\u233?n\u225?t \u225?rk\u233? \u225?rom yau so t\u233?fandau, Moses y\u233?smetam Ijifm\u233?n a y\u233?tnoi y\u225?ne fifi Mirian. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 13\~}
W\u233?i \u225?mb efghon, njam Moses n\u233?ngtory\u233?ng m\u233?n\u225?t siya t\u225?y\u225?fongai y\u225?ne \u225?r w\u233?ikor. Y\u233?mo tawinje s\u243?mbio Ibru \u225?r kasm\u233?gh\u233?t, "N\u233?mam\u233?n f\u233?mo yesmete fenjo f\u250?tar?" Moses\u233?m y\u233?mndai y\u233?n\u233? \u225?r emo fronde yaufaindai \u225?sm\u233?gh.
