\u193?rom yawangoi, "Emo fem n\u233?kaf siya n\u233?m t\u233?fene warsagh \u225?r a mogh \u225?r? So f\u233?mo y\u233?nd w\u233?smete nden\u233?yameyo f\u233?mo k\u233?s t\u233?ngw\u233?smete y\u233?n\u233? Ijifm\u233?n k\u225?ye?" F\u233?yo Moses f\u233?rf\u233?r t\u233?morw\u233?n, kemnau, "M\u233?inyoto \u225?r mat em n\u233?m\u233? y\u233?ndon tafrotan." {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 15\~}
Njam Farao n\u225?y\u225?toi n\u233?m\u233? t\u233? nufrotam, a y\u233?ta t\u233?rametau Moses ngiot. W\u233?nde Moses nawatembai a yiyotam s\u225?i t\u233?morang\u233?rw\u233?n Median yuwon, njam Moses nufary\u233?ng, k\u233?t\u233? Midian, f\u225? n\u225?mnjoy\u233?ng nu y\u233?kw t\u233?ndon. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 16\~}
Midianm\u233?n gh\u233?ng\u233?n \u225?roene tamorw\u233?n 7 m\u233?r\u233?s efe t\u250?m\u233?n tanmorw\u233?n m\u233?n\u225?t nu ukw\u233?gh\u233?t a tawarataw\u233?t tru y\u225?refane w\u233?r\u225?rafet. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 17\~}
W\u233?nde \u225?mb sif wanjeng\u233?gh \u225?r enmorm\u233?n a tawifnaw\u233?t w\u233?nde Moses nokayoi natnam a ewanjary\u233?ng m\u233?r\u233?s k\u233?tam\u233? sif wanjeng\u233?gh t\u233?fn\u225?rafe tamb\u233?n. F\u233?yo y\u233?mo nu tawauketau y\u233?fene w\u233?r\u225?rat. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 18\~}
Njam m\u233?r\u233?s nangotam\u233?nd k\u233?t\u225?n Reuel, y\u225?refam tamotang\u233? n\u233?mam\u233?n f\u233?m n\u233?nangongi w\u233?keye s\u233?nonjo?"
