Soram\u233? ambum y\u233?r\u225?ftam, a Moses\u233?m y\u233?tkw\u233?n yaramai Gersom, y\u233?mo taferng\u233?, "Y\u233?nd t\u233? kw\u233?nmorw\u233?n Dabi \u225?rfene yuwon."
