Yunj\u233?f nawainday\u233?nd, a warsagh \u225?r Ijifm\u233?n k\u233?r y\u233?morm\u233?n, w\u233?nde Israil \u225?r m\u233?gh awamb\u233?gh mbanmbanan tamorw\u233?n y\u233?fene k\u233?rtaye waw\u233?rsoghan. F\u225? kendaw\u233?t w\u225?ut\u225?r\u233?gh\u233?t, a y\u233?fene ye narmboi Ng\u225?nj\u225?njefaf. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 24\~}
