\u193?mb efghon njam Moses\u233?m tawanjetau y\u225?natene w\u233?r\u225?r, Jetroene, gh\u233?ng\u233?n w\u225?rogh \u225?r Midianm\u233?n. Y\u233?mo talimndau w\u233?r\u225?r nayu k\u233?t\u225?n fanfne yuwot a n\u233?nufary\u233?ng Sinay\u233?t, Ng\u225?nj\u225?nene mband tunak\u233?ffaf. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 2\~}
K\u233?t\u233? yurane njafar si r\u233?sagh \u225?r nufary\u233?ng y\u225?faf f\u233?s akrar\u233?ghnit k\u233?tam\u233? k\u233?ghat n\u233?ndk\u233?fta, Moses\u233?m yawewoi s\u233?lngw\u233?laf\u233? ndemam\u233?n f\u233?s akrar\u233?ghan t\u233?morw\u233?n, yau kakernau. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 3\~}
