Y\u233?nd w\u233?m Ng\u225?nj\u225?n fene ferafane, Ebraamene Ng\u225?nj\u225?n, Aisekene Ng\u225?nj\u225?n a Jeikofene Ng\u225?nj\u225?n." Njam Moses\u233?m n\u225?y\u225?rai y\u233?n\u233?, y\u233?mo yamoi y\u225?njo s\u225?f m\u233?nam\u233?n f\u225? f\u233?rf\u233?r t\u233?morw\u233?n s\u225?i t\u233?fandau Ng\u225?nj\u225?n. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 7\~}
