Y\u233?n\u233?mam\u233?n y\u233?nd t\u233? n\u233?newor\u233?n m\u233?n\u225?t s\u225?i tawanjar\u233?n f\u225? k\u233?t\u225?ndm\u233? Ijif \u225?rfene waftata a tautor\u233?n Ijifta k\u233?t\u225?n y\u233?fenjo d\u233?gw\u233?r a merfifi mbandfaf. Y\u233?nd mband y\u233?m \u225?nde nasune kau w\u233?kw\u233?r f\u225?m\u233?gharaf\u233?-y\u233?n\u233? mband \u225?nde Kanan \u225?r, Itait \u225?r, Amor \u225?r, Feris \u225?r, Ifi \u225?r, Jebus \u225?r. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 9\~}
K\u233?reta Israil \u225?rfene yeyam y\u233?nd t\u233? w\u233?yanja a y\u233?ndo t\u233? tafandan nder\u233? m\u225?m\u233?gh\u233?raye Ijif \u225?r\u233?m tawas\u233?rmbotat f\u225?. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 10\~}
S\u233?nonjo kuwano, y\u233?ndo n\u233?ngmafaretan f\u233?m k\u233?t\u225?n Faraofaf. F\u233?mo y\u225?f tanlim tane \u225?r Israil taneutor k\u233?tam\u233? Ijifta."
