\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 12\~}
Ng\u225?nj\u225?nam tawangong\u233?, "Y\u233?nd so y\u233?nre f\u233?maf\u233?, a Y\u233?n\u233? f\u233?y\u233?m fene matot nden\u233? y\u233?nd y\u233?n\u233? fuwom emo n\u233?nmafarete f\u233?m. Njam f\u233?mo taneufar \u225?r taneutor k\u233?tam\u233? Ijifta f\u233?mofem so y\u225?wefnotat Ng\u225?nj\u225?ne y\u233?n\u233? fifi mband tunakfan."
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 13\~}
W\u233?nde Moses m\u233? t\u233?rnotau, "Njam y\u233?nd w\u233?ng\u233?m Israil \u225?rfefaf a tamndan, f\u233?fene \u225?kiafene Ng\u225?nj\u225?nam t\u233? kw\u233?nmafarete y\u233?nd f\u233?fefaf, y\u233?mofem so kw\u233?motangi, 'Efe y\u233?m y\u225?ne y\u233?tkw\u233?n? F\u233?yo ndern\u225?ye y\u233?ndon so tamndan?"
