\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 16\~}
"S\u233?nonjo kuwano tawanmo s\u233?nko \u225?r m\u233?inyotio Israilm\u233?n \u225?mbiro faf\u233?t, Tawaufro Yur\u233?, Ng\u225?nj\u225?n f\u233?fene \u225?kifene-Ebraamene Ng\u225?nj\u225?n, Aisekene Ng\u225?nj\u225?n a Jeikofene Ng\u225?nj\u225?n-t\u233? nufar tafaf, y\u233?mo kw\u233?mndete, y\u233?ndo t\u233? tafandan kaka a k\u233?retan ndern\u225?ye Ijif \u225?r\u233?m engus\u233?rmbotat f\u233?m. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 17\~}
