Israilm\u233?n s\u233?nko \u225?r\u233?m so tanango fene si. F\u233?yo f\u233?m a s\u233?nko t\u233?fn\u225?r t\u225?f eng\u233?m k\u233?t\u225?n Ijifm\u233?n warsagh \u225?roefaf a taufrongi, 'Yur\u233?, Ibru \u225?rfene Ng\u225?nj\u225?naf\u233? y\u233?nd t\u233? naf\u225?ngong\u233?m, Y\u233?n\u233?mam\u233?n gh\u233?rgh\u233?rsis\u233? y\u233?nd so kuwanong\u233?m nambio efogh k\u233?t\u233? fanfne yuwot m\u233?n\u225?t so yawafrotam gh\u233?ng\u233?n Yurai, t\u233?fene Ng\u225?nj\u225?n.' {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 19\~}
W\u233?nde y\u233?nd mat w\u233?m nden\u233? Ijifm\u233?n warsagh \u225?rom yau so taumyong\u233? f\u233?m \u225?ligh\u233?t t\u225?fandro waftaf\u233? ng\u225?ngayam njam timndang\u233? f\u225?. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 20\~}
Y\u233?ndon so tauyon tane ng\u225?ng\u233? a esmetan Ijif \u225?r, y\u233?ngwafrotan f\u233?nat\u233? wafrogham s\u225?f y\u233?fene k\u233?nj\u250?n, f\u233?yo soram\u233? y\u233?mo so f\u233?m taumyong\u233? \u225?ligh\u233?t.
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 21\~}
