M\u233?inyotio Israilm\u233?n amaf so k\u243?mnendangi wafroghm\u233?n silf\u233? a gol a awogh s\u225?l\u225?met k\u233?t\u225?n \u225?mb yum\u233?n amafafefaf y\u233?fene m\u233?ngo. F\u233?mofem so ewamanetati f\u233?fenjo ambum a m\u233?r\u233?s y\u233?naye, omy\u233?gh t\u225?y\u225?tongi Ijif \u225?r y\u233?fene awayoghta."
