Yuram t\u233?ng\u233?mndang\u233?, "Tita mbandot." F\u233?yo Moses\u233?m yitam w\u233?tu, a y\u233?n\u233? nawengoi kambanot! Moses n\u233?ngfnam s\u233?mta. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 4\~}
F\u233?yo Yuram t\u233?mndang\u233?, "Tawatemb ng\u225?ng\u233? a tawer y\u225?ne k\u233?r." Moses\u233?m ewatembai ng\u225?ng\u233? a y\u233?rai, a w\u233?i nangoi nawengoi k\u233?t\u225?notio sif wanjeng\u233?gh \u225?roene w\u233?tu y\u225?ne ng\u225?ngayan. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 5\~}
Yafrota y\u233?n\u233? ufarogh yam, "Yuram t\u233?mndang\u233?, "F\u233?yo y\u233?mofem so efalo kwiy\u225?tongi nden\u233?nde Yuram y\u233?fene \u225?kifene Ng\u225?nj\u225?n-Ebraam Ng\u225?nj\u225?n, Aisekene Ng\u225?nj\u225?n a Jeikofene Ng\u225?nj\u225?n- efaloe t\u233? nufar fefaf."
