Yuram norayai, "S\u233?nonjo tawango fenjo ng\u225?ng\u233? k\u233?t\u225?n k\u233?nj\u250?t fenjo sodafaf. F\u233?yo Moses\u233?m t\u225?kmang\u233? y\u225?njo ng\u225?ng\u233? tawangong\u233? k\u233?nj\u250?t, a njam y\u233?mon w\u233?i esufai w\u233?ikor, nden\u233? mer k\u233?retaw\u233?t ndern\u225?ye y\u225?ne m\u233?inyotio fifi mer k\u233?retau. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 8\~}
Yuram t\u233?mndang\u233? Moses, "Njam y\u233?mofem yau efalo k\u233?ny\u225?tongi a yau tam\u233?indang\u233? frondem\u233?n yam wafrogham, f\u225? so tam\u233?indang\u233? t\u225?f s\u243?mbiom\u233?n yam wafrogham. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 9\~}
A njam y\u233?mofem yau efalo niy\u225?totat o k\u233?ny\u225?rangi f\u233?m k\u233?tam\u233? y\u233?n\u233? s\u243?mbio yam wafroghta, f\u233?yo t\u233?ngwan \u225?mb nu k\u233?tamam\u233?n Nail wanjeta a tas\u233?r k\u233?t\u225?n gh\u233?rnat mbandfaf. Njam y\u233?n\u233? yafrota, nu Nailm\u233?n so kawengong\u233? f\u233?rkot mbandan."
