W\u233?nde Moses\u233?f m\u233? k\u233?wiw\u233?t Yuraf\u233?, "O Yur\u233?, y\u233?nd yau w\u233?m merfifi m\u233?n\u225?yan sian a y\u233?nd yau w\u233?ngmorm\u233?n y\u233?nayan a so w\u233?m s\u233?nonjo, ndemam\u233?n f\u233?m koray\u233? tafaf, y\u233?nd afraye si t\u233?fn\u225?r w\u233?m, a tane kauk\u233? t\u225?f sakram tifong\u233? tekofnar."
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 11\~}
f\u233?yo Yuram t\u233?motang\u233? Moses, "Emo yafrotam \u225?roene mb\u237?rmb\u237?r? Emo yafrotam \u225?r s\u225?i noraya o yau noraya, o siya naret a yau siya nareta, s\u225?i y\u233?fana o yau y\u233?fende, y\u233?nd w\u233?t y\u233?n\u233? yau fuw\u233?n Yur\u233?? {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 12\~}
S\u233?nonjo kuwano! Y\u233?nd so w\u233?m fefaf njam noraya, a y\u233?ndon so n\u233?matametan f\u233?m n\u233?m\u233? si so noraye."
