W\u233?nde Yur\u233? namndai n\u233?kwaf\u233? Mosesefaf a korayang\u233?, "F\u233?yotaro. Ndern\u225?ye w\u233?t fene n\u233?ngnenem\u233?n, Aron Lefi \u225?rfenem\u233?n? Y\u233?nd mat w\u233?m f\u225? noraye mer k\u233?r\u225?ye a k\u233?reta f\u225? y\u233?n\u233?m \u225?lighan s\u225?i k\u233?nf\u225?ngong\u233? f\u233?m s\u233?nonjo f\u225? so y\u233?m \u225?uw\u233?ghaf\u233? mindefifi s\u225?i k\u233?minjong\u233? f\u233?m. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 15\~}
Noraya y\u225?faf, a tak\u233?m si y\u225?ne mb\u237?rmb\u237?ran, y\u233?nd so w\u233?m f\u233?fefaf f\u233?m s\u243?mbio sere siya norayet, a y\u233?ndon so ewatamewan f\u233?m s\u243?mbio n\u233?m\u233? so ewafrot. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 16\~}
Aron so y\u233?m fene si t\u233?fn\u225?r k\u233?t\u225?n \u225?rfet, f\u225? so y\u233?m f\u233?fene mb\u237?rmb\u237?r a f\u233?m so ewakai Ng\u225?nj\u225?nene sifayan y\u225?yot, yafrotati n\u233?m\u233? so norayati. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 17\~}
A tanangi f\u233?fenjo sif wanjeng\u233?gh w\u233?tu y\u233?namayo f\u233?mof\u233?; a y\u233?kmetati y\u233?n\u233? \u225?s\u225?foghan m\u233?n\u225?t so ewafrotati s\u233?lngw\u233?laf\u233? yam y\u233?ndon \u225?rk\u233? tawanyafotan."
