W\u233?nde f\u233?mo so t\u233?mnde f\u225?, nden\u233? Yur\u233? noraya, "Israil siy\u233?m tane fronde s\u233?nko ambum. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 23\~}
Y\u233?ndon n\u233?mafaretan f\u233?myo tane ambum nguwanong\u233?, y\u233?mo so ta w\u225?wefnote. W\u233?nde f\u233?m t\u233? nakena, y\u233?ndon so t\u233?smai fene fronde s\u233?nko ambum!"
