F\u233?yo Moses a Aron n\u233?ngangeyay\u233?nd k\u233?t\u225?n Ijif\u233?t a eumendangeyay\u233?nd m\u233?inyotio lim\u225?n\u233?gh \u225?r Israilm\u233?n m\u233?rne. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 30\~}
