"Yau engwarametati w\u233?ikor fakfak sim\u233?nd wafrogh\u233?t; \u225?r\u233?myo so eng\u233?rsat y\u233?mofemyo. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 8\~}
W\u233?nde m\u233? so f\u233?t\u233? ewafrotat y\u233?mofem y\u233?n\u233? f\u233?yotaro sim\u233?nd nden\u233? k\u233?s em frondem\u233?n. Yau t\u225?f tiy\u225?tongi mbarmbar. F\u225? sem sak\u233?r; y\u233?n\u233?mam\u233?n f\u225? ye n\u233?ngendat, 'So y\u233?ng\u233?m a yatetam gh\u233?ng\u233?n k\u233?t\u225?n t\u233?fene Ng\u225?nj\u225?nefaf.' {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 9\~}
Ewafrotam f\u225? t\u225?rf\u225?r \u225?s\u225?foghe, ey\u225?tota f\u225? m\u233?lm\u233?lro! Y\u233?nayam so ewatamete siya n\u225?y\u225?retat uny\u233?gh.
