F\u233?yo waw\u233?rsogh wim\u225?ng\u233?gh t\u233?fn\u225?r a m\u233?ngo ram\u233?gh \u225?r engmorm\u233?n a tawaufrongi \u225?r\u233?t; nden\u233? Farao noraya: 'Y\u233?ndo w\u233?i yau so kor engrametan sim\u233?n fak f\u233?feyot. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 11\~}
Tang\u233?m a tan\u233?rsangi f\u233?mofemyo tawinjongi \u225?nde w\u233?n, w\u233?nde f\u233?mofem t\u225?f ewafrotati t\u225?rf\u225?ryo nden\u233? yau frondem\u233?n sim\u233?nd k\u233?s em." {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 12\~}
F\u233?yo \u225?r nofarnay\u233?nd y\u233?n\u233? Ijif mbandan \u233?regh\u233?t flaw\u233? s\u233?r\u233?t mbwem\u233?n t\u233?ngan t\u233?nganot m\u233?n\u225?t wafrogh\u233?t fakot. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 13\~}
M\u233? Ijifm\u233?n waw\u233?rsogh wim\u225?ng\u233?gh \u225?r m\u233?njtaye kimndaw\u233?t taikre, f\u225? k\u243?mnendangai, "Et\u233?mndati f\u233?fenjo efoghm\u233?n mbarmbar sim\u233?nd, nden\u233? y\u233?ndfem ndern\u225?ye tawarametaw\u233?m kun t\u233?ngangt\u233?ngan." {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 14\~}
F\u233?yo y\u233?mofem f\u233?mogh tawafngongi Israilm\u233?n m\u233?ngo ram\u233?gh \u225?r y\u233?mofem \u225?rk\u233? ekmay\u233?nd \u225?s\u225?fogh \u225?r wanjeng\u233?gh\u233?t, f\u225? k\u243?mnendangi, "N\u233?mam\u233?n f\u233?mofem yau eutarngi f\u233?fenjo mbarmbar k\u225?ye a s\u233?nonjo?"
