T\u233?fe yau y\u233?nmaramangi flaw\u233? mbwe arau fakfak, w\u233?nde wawersogh \u225?rfene wim\u225?ng\u233?gh t\u233?fn\u225?r m\u233? komnendaw\u233?t, ewafrotati sim\u233?nd. Y\u233?nd t\u233? t\u233?n\u233?fmotat, w\u233?nde yau y\u233?m t\u233?fene t\u233?f\u233?n. Fene \u225?r em t\u233?f\u233?n."
