S\u233?nonjo kangongi \u225?s\u225?fogh\u233?t! Yau \u225?mb flaw\u233? t\u233?ngant\u233?ngan f\u233?t\u233? so wawaramang\u233?m, w\u233?nde f\u233?mofem m\u233? so f\u233?t\u233? ewafrotati wifoghfaf sim\u233?nd. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 19\~}
Israilm\u233?n m\u233?ngo \u225?s\u225?fogh \u225?r\u233?m yinjoy\u233?nd nden\u233? ndimbal k\u233?rtayan nokayoy\u233?nd njam f\u225? emnday\u233?ng, "F\u233?mofem yau t\u225?f y\u233?wonati sim\u233?ndene waf\u233?gh t\u250?m\u233?n efghon \u225?rk\u233? ewafrotati."
