m\u233?ngo ram\u233?gh \u225?r\u233?m tamnd\u233?nd f\u225?, so Yuram moghan a t\u233?kratan takm\u233? f\u233?m m\u233?nam\u233?n y\u233?n\u233?kmangi y\u233?nd t\u233?kratan Faraofaf a y\u225?ne ofis \u225?s\u225?fogh \u225?r, f\u233?mofem t\u233? eram\u233?nd witmaf\u233? s\u233?nt\u233? n\u225?if\u233? y\u233?fene ng\u225?ngat, a s\u233?safne t\u233?fe ngiot."
