A Ng\u225?nj\u225?n norayai Mosesfaf, "Y\u233?nd w\u233?m Yur\u233?. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 3\~}
Y\u233?nd nu fary\u233?n k\u233?t\u225?n Ebraamefaf, k\u233?t\u225?n Aisekefaf, a k\u233?t\u225?n Jeikoffaf nden\u233? El Sadai, Ng\u225?nj\u225?n ndimbalfifi w\u233?nde y\u233?ndo yau yufar\u233?n tane y\u233?tkw\u233?n, Yur\u233?, k\u233?t\u225?n y\u233?fefaf. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 4\~}
A y\u233?ndo kor yiy\u225?toy\u233?n tane \u225?rny\u233?gh y\u233?maf\u233? y\u233?n\u233? mbanmbanan y\u233?ndo uny\u233?gh si ewaramay\u233?n y\u233?fe s\u225?i tawaraman Kanan mband, \u225?nde f\u225? tamorang\u233?rw\u233?n d\u225?bi. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 5\~}
F\u233?m so mat em nden\u233? y\u233?nd t\u233? n\u225?y\u225?ran mike Israil \u225?rfene, efe em faiofnar \u225?s\u225?fogh \u225?r Ijif \u225?rfefaf, a y\u233?nd mer mat w\u233?m tane \u225?rny\u233?gh y\u233?maf\u233?. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 6\~}
Y\u233?n\u233?mam\u233?n, tamnd\u233? Israil \u225?r: Y\u233?nd w\u233?m Yur\u233?. Y\u233?ndo so yuwek t\u225?y\u225?ton fem k\u233?t\u225?ndm\u233? k\u233?rtayan stumnde a so tawanjar\u233?n f\u233?m k\u233?t\u225?ndm\u233? f\u233?fene faiofnar \u225?s\u225?foghta k\u233?t\u233? Ijif\u233?n. Y\u233?ndon so tafrendang\u233?n f\u233?m m\u233?naye waftaf\u233? ng\u225?ngaye a ndimbalfifi wafrogh\u233?t moghan. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 7\~}
Y\u233?ndon so ewatnan nden\u233? tane \u225?r a y\u233?nd so w\u233?m f\u233?fene Ng\u225?nj\u225?n. F\u233?yo f\u233?m so mat em nden\u233? y\u233?nd w\u233?m Yur\u233? f\u233?fene Ng\u225?nj\u225?n emo t\u233? yuwek ey\u225?toi f\u233?m k\u233?tam\u233? k\u233?rt\u233? yam statumndau Ijif\u233?n. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 8\~}
Y\u233?ndon so tanaufar\u233?n y\u233?n\u233? mbandot y\u233?ndon efalo t\u233? norayay\u233?n s\u225?i tawaramangay\u233?n y\u233?fe Ebraam, Aisek, a Jeikof. Y\u233?ndo so tawaraman f\u233?fe nden\u233? f\u233?fene sifay\u233? fifi. Y\u233?nd w\u233?m yur\u233?!" {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 9\~}
F\u233?yo Moses\u233?m ewaufrot Israil \u225?rfet n\u233?m\u233? Yur\u233? t\u233? norayai, w\u233?nde f\u225? w\u233?i s\u225?i kor k\u225?y\u225?retaw\u233?t. F\u225? t\u233? n\u233?namnday\u233?nd \u225?uw\u233?ghonfar m\u233?n\u225?yan nd\u233?mkef\u233? y\u233?fene faiofnar \u225?s\u225?foghan.
