W\u233?nde Yur\u233? korayang\u233? Mosesefaf a Aronefaf ewaramai wafar\u233?gh y\u233?fe Israil \u225?r, Ijifm\u233?n warsagh \u225?r. Yuram ewafaretangeyai Moses a Aron m\u233?n\u225?t s\u225?i talimeyay\u233?nd Israil \u225?r tautoreyay\u233?nd Ijifta.
