Amram nawerai y\u225?refane y\u225?m\u233?r\u233?s Jokebed, a y\u233?mo erafm\u233?ng ambum Aron a Moses. Amram y\u233?morang\u233?rm\u233?n 137 yunj\u233?f namndai. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 21\~}
