\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 1\~}
F\u233?yo Yur\u233? norayai Mosesefaf korfifi k\u225?y\u225?r y\u233?n\u233?, "Y\u233?ndon so f\u233?m k\u233?ny\u225?ton ndenanit Ng\u225?nj\u225?n y\u225?faf Faraofaf, a fene an\u233?, Aron, so y\u233?m Ng\u225?nj\u225?nene mat y\u225?togh \u225?r. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 2\~}
Yaufrotan Arone m\u233?inyotio y\u233?ndon n\u233?mat n\u233?ngmafaretang\u233?n f\u233?m, a Aron\u233?m t\u225?f tafaretang\u233? Farao m\u233?n\u225?t taumyong\u233? Israil \u225?r korongi y\u225?ne yu. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 3\~}
W\u233?nde y\u233?ndon so tiy\u225?ton Faraone tik\u233?f t\u225?ik\u233?r m\u233?n\u225?t y\u233?ndon so eminan tane s\u233?lngw\u233?laf\u233? ufarogh yam a sunsunaf\u233? yam k\u233?t\u233? Ijif mbandan. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 4\~}
Farao kakenang\u233? \u225?y\u225?rgh\u233?t f\u233?feta. Y\u233?ndon so y\u233?n\u233?rsan tane t\u233?ndo Ijif\u233?t. F\u233?yo y\u233?ndon so tawanjar\u233?n tane kw\u233?rnaraf\u233? tane \u225?r, Israil \u225?r k\u233?tam\u233? Ijif mband ta m\u233?naye ndimbal t\u233?krat yame. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 5\~}
Njam y\u233?ndon tauyon tanjo waftaf\u233? ng\u225?ng\u233? a taneutor\u233?n Israil \u225?r, Ijif \u225?r so mat kamndangi y\u233?nd w\u233?m Yur\u233?." {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 6\~}
F\u233?yo Moses a Aron ewafrom\u233?nd nden\u233? f\u233?t\u233? Yuram ndern\u225?ye tawafarew\u233?ng f\u225?. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 7\~}
Moses t\u233?morw\u233?n 80 yunj\u233?f, a Aron t\u233?morw\u233?n 83 yunj\u233?f njam y\u233?mofem y\u233?rameyay\u233?nd y\u233?fenjo m\u233?nde Faraofaf.
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 8\~}
F\u233?yo Yur\u233? norayai Mosesefaf a Aronefaf, {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 9\~}
"Farao so k\u243?mnendang\u233?, 'Kauyafongi s\u233?lngw\u233?le yam, njam y\u233?mo yafrota y\u233?n\u233?, t\u233?mnde Aron tan\u233?gh fenjo w\u233?tu a yita yuwot Faraone s\u225?fr\u233?re,' a y\u233?n\u233? so kawengong\u233? kambanot." {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 10\~}
F\u233?yo Moses a Aron nuwaneyay\u233?nd k\u233?t\u225?n Faraofaf a ewafrom\u233?nd ndern\u225?ye Ng\u225?nj\u225?nam t\u233? tawafarew\u233?ng f\u225?. Aron\u233?m t\u225?y\u225?ng\u233? y\u225?njo w\u233?tu y\u233?fe s\u225?fr\u233?re Farao a y\u225?ne ofis \u225?s\u225?fogh \u225?r nawengoi kambanot. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 11\~}
F\u233?yo Faraom tanwanmong\u233? y\u225?njoyo k\u225?fet\u233? mwighaf\u233? \u225?r a ghar t\u233?fn\u225?r, a y\u233?n\u233? f\u233?r\u233?k sufgharam nden\u233?yameyo yam yafrotam\u233?nd y\u233?fenjo ngamaye. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 12\~}
Y\u233?mofem ewitam\u233?nd y\u233?fenjoyo w\u233?tu, \u225?rk\u233?m\u233?n\u233? w\u233?i n\u233?n\u225?t\u225?toy\u233?nd kamban. W\u233?nde Aronene w\u233?tuam euloy\u233?ng y\u233?fene w\u233?tu. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 13\~}
Faraone tik\u233?f m\u233? t\u225?ik\u233?r t\u233?morw\u233?n, f\u225? yau n\u225?y\u225?rai, nden\u233? f\u233?t\u233? Yur\u233? ndern\u225?ye norayan.
\par\pard\plain \s105\qc\fi0\lin0\rin0\sb160\sa80\b\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 F\u233?r\u233?koene k\u233?rtaf\u233? yam
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 14\~}
F\u233?yo Yur\u233? korayang\u233? Mosesefaf, "Faraone tik\u233?f siy\u233?m t\u225?ik\u233?r a f\u225? m\u233? nakene m\u233?n\u225?t s\u225?i taumyong\u233? \u225?r \u225?ligh\u233?t. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 15\~}
F\u233?yo nguwano k\u233?t\u225?n Faraofaf akwan njam f\u225? nguwanong\u233? k\u233?t\u225?n wanjet, Kokai k\u233?t\u233? Nail wanje t\u233?ndon a t\u233?f\u225?ngo f\u225? k\u233?t\u233?, f\u233?t\u233? t\u225?f t\u233?ngwan w\u233?tu \u225?rk\u233?m\u233?n\u233? nawengoi lambanot. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 16\~}
F\u233?yo mat tiy\u225?to f\u225?, 'Yur\u233? Ibru \u225?rfene Ng\u225?nj\u225?nam, t\u233? w\u233?nmafareta y\u233?nd m\u233?n\u225?t s\u225?i k\u233?namndan f\u233?m, "Taumyo tane \u225?ligh\u233?t, y\u233?mofem so w\u225?wefnotat ta k\u233?t\u233? fanfne yuwon. Y\u233?nanotio s\u233?nonjo, f\u233?m t\u233? kakene \u225?y\u225?rgh\u233?t y\u225? tamb\u233?n. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 17\~}
Ndern\u225?ye Yur\u233? noraye, "Y\u233?ndon so k\u233?mauyofon fe nden\u233? y\u233?nd w\u233?m Yur\u233?, "K\u233?reta! Y\u233?ndon so t\u233?sman Nail wanje nu y\u233?n\u233? w\u233?tue tane ng\u225?ngayan siy\u233?m, a wanje so kawengong\u233? f\u233?rkot. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 18\~}
Wagif k\u233?t\u233? k\u233?s em so em k\u233?r, a wanje so nornde Ijifm\u233?n \u225?r f\u233?yotarofnar so em s\u225?i narmbnetat nu y\u233?n\u233? Nail wanjeta."
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 19\~}
F\u233?yo Yuram korayang\u233? Mosesefaf, "T\u233?mnde Aron, tan\u233? fenjo w\u233?tu a tauyo fenjo ng\u225?ng\u233? Ijif \u225?rfene nu tukm\u233?, m\u233?inyotio \u225?mb wanje, nu end, nu nd\u233?mngu a m\u233?inyotio akegh s\u250?mb ewengota m\u233?inyotio nu f\u233?rkot, m\u233?inyotio sifayam\u233? Ijif k\u233?nj\u250?n nu so nawengotat f\u233?rkot, nu t\u233?u em w\u233?n k\u233?nj\u250?n w\u233?m kwaran."
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 20\~}
Moses a Aron ewafrogh\u233?t y\u233?maf\u233?m nden\u233? f\u233?t\u233? Yuram ndern\u225?ye tawafarew\u233?ng f\u225?. Farao a y\u225?njo ofis \u225?s\u225?fogh t\u233?fandaw\u233?t, Aronm\u233?n yuyoi w\u233?tu a y\u233?smai Nail wanje nu tekofnar m\u233?inyotio wanje nawengoi tekofnar k\u233?t\u225?n f\u233?rkot. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 21\~}
Wagif wanjem\u233?n k\u233?r t\u233?ramngotau, a nu kor n\u233?namndai k\u233?rk\u233?f a Ijif \u225?r f\u233?yotarofnar tamorw\u233?n n\u233?net k\u233?t\u233? t\u233?morw\u233?n f\u233?r\u233?k m\u233?inyotio sifayam\u233? y\u233?nam\u233? Ijif mbandan.
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 22\~}
W\u233?nde w\u233?ikor Ijifm\u233?n ghar t\u233?fn\u225?ram tawafngongi y\u233?fenjo ngam\u233?, a y\u233?mofem w\u233?i nden\u225?yo tawengotaw\u233?t nu f\u233?rkot; f\u233?yo Faraone tik\u233?f m\u233? t\u233?morw\u233?n t\u225?ik\u233?r, f\u225? nakenai s\u225?i k\u225?y\u225?retau Mosesefaf a Aronefaf nden\u233? f\u233?t\u233? Yuram ndern\u225?ye korayau. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 23\~}
Farao nangoi y\u225?njo utman\u233?gh sifayat a m\u233?inyotio yam mwighata ewitam. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 24\~}
F\u233?yo m\u233?inyotio Ijifm\u233?n \u225?r\u233?m nu y\u233?kw tar\u233?gh ewafngoy\u233?nd wanje t\u233?ndom\u233? \u225?r\u225?mbn\u233?gh nuot, a yau y\u233?mofem t\u233?netaw\u233?t Nail wanjem\u233?n nu.
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 25\~}
Sefen efogh nawainday\u233?nd y\u233?n\u233? efghon njam y\u233?smai Nail wanje.
\par\pard\plain \s52\ql\fi0\lin0\rin0\sb160\sa80\b\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs33 8
\par\pard\plain \s105\qc\fi0\lin0\rin0\sb160\sa80\b\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 Ndokreyafene k\u233?rtaf\u233? yam
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 1\~}
F\u233?yo Yur\u233? norayai Mosesefaf, "Ngango Faraofaf a taufro y\u225?yot, nden\u233? Yur\u233? noraye, 'Taumyong\u233? tane \u225?r kuwangongi, y\u233?mofem so ta w\u225?wefnotat. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 2\~}
Njam f\u233?m nakena tang\u233?umyo f\u225? nguwanongi, y\u233?ndo so y\u233?ngwafaretan ndokreyafene kaukau y\u233?nam\u233? fene m\u233?inyotio yuwom\u233?. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 3\~}
Nail wanjefaf t\u233?fghan ndokre, so en\u233?m n\u233?ntonat k\u233?t\u225?ndm\u233? wanjeta a n\u233?ny\u225?wetat fene warsagh \u225?r utman\u233?gh sifayafaf, a w\u233?i fene k\u233?m\u233?gh sifayafaf a k\u233?m\u233?gh sifay\u233? tuk\u233?t! F\u225? so nufanat fene ofis \u225?s\u225?fogh \u225?rfene m\u233?ngot a fene \u225?r w\u233?i f\u225? so n\u233?ngatnat nuflitat f\u233?fene njamke f\u233?s sifayam\u233? a sinam\u233?. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 4\~}
Ndokre so n\u233?ngatnat f\u233?fefaf, fene \u225?r, a m\u233?inyotio ofis \u225?s\u225?fogh \u225?r."
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 5\~}
F\u233?yo Yuram t\u233?mndang\u233? Moses, "T\u233?mnd\u233? Aron, tuyong\u233? w\u233?tu fene ng\u225?ngata m\u233?inyotio wanjeyam\u233? nu end nu nd\u233?mngu Ijifm\u233?n tanwasrend ndokre m\u233?inyotio yum\u233?n." {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 6\~}
F\u233?yo Aron\u233?m euyoi y\u225?njo ng\u225?ng\u233? Ijif nufaf, a enwertoi ndokre a nofayoi m\u233?inyotio yu. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 7\~}
W\u233?nde ghar t\u233?fn\u225?ram w\u233?i nden\u233? yamyo tawafrotaw\u233?t em\u233?indam\u233?nd ndokre kufanaw\u233?t Ijif mbandan.
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 8\~}
F\u233?yo Faraom eng\u233?mndeyai Moses a Aron a engwamnendangeyai, "Korayangi Yuraf\u233? m\u233?n\u225?t ndokre tawot\u233?rmbongi nayu y\u233?nam\u233? ta tamb\u233?n a tane \u225?r. Y\u233?ndon so tangweumyon fene \u225?r nguwanongi so y\u233?mofem yawafrotat gh\u233?ng\u233?n y\u225? Yurai."
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 9\~}
Moses\u233?m yawangoi, "F\u233?mo t\u233?frenda efogh kw\u233?f, kwaufro njamtai f\u233?m m\u233?nde n\u233?m. Y\u233?nd s\u225?i notayan Ng\u225?nj\u225?nefaf fenem\u233?n fene ofis \u225?s\u225?fogh \u225?r a fene \u225?r. F\u233?yo f\u233?m a f\u233?fene m\u233?ngota so kit\u233?rmbongi ndokre, so em k\u233?tam\u233? m\u233? Nail wanjenro."
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 10\~}
Farao korayang\u233?, "Yafrota k\u225?ye, f\u233?yotaro."
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 Moses tawangong\u233?, "So nden\u233? f\u233?t\u233? y\u233?mo k\u233?s noraya a f\u233?m so mat n\u233?m nden\u233? y\u233?na yau \u225?mb \u225?r nden\u233? Yur\u233? t\u233?fene Ng\u225?nj\u225?n. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 11\~}
Ndokreyam so t\u233?f\u225?ngongi f\u233?m a f\u233?fene m\u233?ngo a fene ofis \u225?s\u225?fogh t\u233?fn\u225?r; f\u225? k\u233?t\u233? m\u233? so em Nail wanjen."
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 12\~}
F\u233?yo Moses a Aron y\u233?frangeyay\u233?nd Faraone lim\u225?n\u233?gh \u225?mnjogh sifay\u233?, a Moses nutnam k\u233?t\u225?n Yurafaf m\u233?nam\u233?n ndokreye y\u233?mon \u225?rk\u233? nd\u233?mke yaramai Faraoi. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 13\~}
A Yuram tawafrotau y\u233?n\u233? n\u233?m\u233? Moses t\u233? korayau ndokre m\u233?ngo k\u233?nj\u250?m\u233?, mogh sifayam\u233?, ndau sifayam\u233? m\u233?inyotio t\u233?ramngotau. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 14\~}
Ijif \u225?r\u233?m t\u233?ngumendaw\u233?t ndimbal sefri a yaufi wimam nofayoi yu. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 15\~}
W\u233?nde njam Faraom yinjoi y\u233?n\u233? freng\u233?gh t\u233? nufary\u233?ng, f\u225? n\u233?namndai tik\u233?f t\u225?ik\u233?r. F\u225? nakenai s\u225?i k\u225?y\u225?retau y\u233?fefaf Moses a Aron, nden\u233? f\u233?t\u233? Yur\u233? ndern\u225?yefifi t\u233? korayau.
\par\pard\plain \s105\qc\fi0\lin0\rin0\sb160\sa80\b\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 Yond\u233?ryond\u233?rafene k\u233?rtaf\u233? yam
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 16\~}
A Yur\u233? korayang\u233? Mosesefaf, "Taufro Arone, 'Tuyong\u233? y\u225?njo w\u233?tu a t\u233?s\u233?m mband.' Ngurm\u233?ng so kafurnangi s\u233?f yond\u233?ryond\u233?ram so kofayong\u233? Ijif mband." {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 17\~}
Moses a Aronf\u233? tawafrogh\u233?t nden\u233? f\u233?t\u233? Yuram ndern\u225?ye tawafarew\u233?ng f\u225?. Njam Aron\u233?m euyoi y\u225?njo ng\u225?ng\u233? a y\u233?smai mband m\u233?naye w\u233?tue, yond\u233?ryond\u233?ram n\u233?nofayoi m\u233?inyotio yu, ewafary\u233?ng Ijif \u225?r a y\u233?fene w\u233?r\u225?r rokar, m\u233?inyotio ngurm\u233?ng y\u233?n\u233? yuwon ng\u233?furnai yond\u233?ryond\u233?rot. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 18\~}
Faraone ghar t\u233?fn\u225?ram y\u233?ta tawafrotaw\u233?t y\u233?n\u233? yamyo kwankwane t\u233?m\u233?nde yame, w\u233?nde y\u233?n\u233? efghon f\u225? nuyay\u233?nd. A yond\u233?ryond\u233?ram ewafary\u233?ng m\u233?inyotio \u225?r a f\u233?nataf\u233?nat\u233? w\u233?r\u225?r, {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 19\~}
Ghar t\u233?fn\u225?r korayaw\u233?t Faraofaf, "Y\u233?n\u233? siy\u233?m Ng\u225?nj\u225?nene ng\u225?ng\u233?!" W\u233?nde Faraone tik\u233?f m\u233? t\u233?morw\u233?n t\u225?ik\u233?r a f\u225? yau k\u225?y\u225?retau y\u233?fenfaf nden\u233? f\u233?t\u233? Yur\u233? ndern\u225?ye t\u233? norayam.
