A Yuram tawafrotau nden\u233? f\u233?t\u233? ndern\u225?ye f\u225? norayai a s\u233?njt\u233? mbwerang s\u233?fam yafary\u233?ng Faraone lim\u225?n\u233?gh \u225?mnjogh sifay\u233? a m\u233?ngo y\u225?ne ofis \u225?s\u225?fogh \u225?rfene. M\u233?inyotio Ijif mband yitam k\u233?t\u225?n mwigh\u233? uw\u233?rsoghfaf m\u233?naye mbwerange.
