F\u233?yo Yuram korayang\u233? Moses, "Kango w\u233?ikor Faraofaf a w\u233?ikor tafrota \u243?mneng\u233?gh. Y\u233?ndon tafrotan f\u225? a y\u225?njo ofis \u225?s\u225?fogh \u225?r t\u225?ik\u233?r, m\u233?n\u225?t y\u233?ndon so ewafrotan tane s\u233?lngw\u233?laf\u233? yam y\u233?fefaf. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 2\~}
