Njam f\u233?m kakena gh\u233?kfe s\u233?nt\u233?, k\u225?ye y\u233?ndon so tanwasron ngumbainy s\u233?f fene yuwot. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 5\~}
Y\u233?mofem so kofayongi yu m\u233?n\u225?t f\u233?mo yau so y\u233?fande mband, y\u233?mofem so tawofongi n\u233?m\u233? n\u233?mbnare kafrangotat fene y\u233?gh w\u233?n njamke t\u233?f\u233?n a mb\u233?me y\u233?n\u233? soram\u233? kruf\u233?r nu saioene k\u233?rtaf\u233? yam mbormboraf\u233? y\u233?nayafayo m\u233?inyotio w\u233?n k\u233?s n\u233?nganotat ndau sifayam\u233?. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 6\~}
F\u225? so n\u233?rsat w\u233?rsaye k\u233?t\u225?n f\u233?fene utman\u233?gh sifayat a fene ofis \u225?s\u225?fogh \u225?rfene m\u233?ngot a m\u233?inyotio Ijif \u225?rfene m\u233?ngo. Yau \u225?mb nafrotam\u233?nd nden\u233?yam\u233?n Ijif\u233?n \u225?rk\u233? fene \u225?kiambumam s\u225?i y\u233?fandat nden\u233? y\u233?n\u233? siy\u233?m,' a y\u233?nandm\u233? Moses nawengoi a y\u233?frangoi Farao.
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 7\~}
