A ngumbainyam nafor m\u233?inyotio yu Ijif\u233?n t\u233?rnaw\u233?n s\u233?f k\u233?t\u225?notio \u225?mb kw\u233?ndkw\u233?nd k\u233?t\u225?n \u225?mb kw\u233?ndkw\u233?nd y\u233?n\u233? yuwon. Y\u233?n\u233? tamorw\u233?n mindefifi k\u233?rt\u233? yam wafrogh ngumbainy Ijifoene matot soramatau \u225?r fandagh\u233?t a k\u233?t\u233? yau \u225?mb y\u233?morm\u233?n nden\u233? y\u233?n\u233? nufrotam. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 15\~}
