Faraom w\u233?keye tamnd\u233? Moses a Aron, a kwawafenau, "Y\u233?ndon t\u233? yaufi tafrotan Yurafaf f\u233?fene Ng\u225?nj\u225?n a f\u233?fefaf. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 17\~}
