F\u233?yo korayang\u233? Mosesefaf, "Y\u233?ndon so t\u233?sman Farao a Ijif m\u233?naye \u225?mbirotaro wan\u233?fgh\u233?t. Y\u233?n\u233? soram\u233?, Faraom so taumyong\u233? f\u233?m t\u233?frangongi y\u233?n\u233? yu. Mbark\u225?nde f\u225? so m\u233? karamang\u233? f\u233?fe wit\u233?rmbogh\u233?t nden\u233? y\u233?mo so ewafrote f\u233?m m\u233?inyotio kuwanongi. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 2\~}
Tamnde m\u233?inyotio Israil \u225?r ghak\u233?r a amaf m\u233?n\u225?t s\u225?i enmotat y\u233?fene Ijifm\u233?n y\u233?fe f\u250?tar\u233?f m\u233?n\u225?t wafroghm\u233?n silfat a golot." {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 3\~}
S\u233?nonjo Yuram t\u233? em\u233?inda Ijif \u225?r m\u233?ndef\u233? ewinjongi Israil \u225?r. A moses t\u233?fandaw\u233?t nden\u233? ndimbal \u225?r Ijif mbandan, tut\u233?mndaw\u233?t Faraone ofis \u225?s\u225?fogh \u225?r a Ijifm\u233?n f\u233?nataf\u233?nat\u233? \u225?r\u233?m.
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 4\~}
Moses\u233?m mat tiy\u225?totau Farao, "Nden\u233? Yur\u233? n\u233?noraye: 'S\u233?mb\u225?r n\u233?ndk\u233?fan s\u233?nonjo, y\u233?nd so nawaindan Ijif \u225?rfene tikfam\u233?. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 5\~}
M\u233?inyotio fronde s\u233?nko ambum so em k\u233?r m\u233?inyotio m\u233?r\u233?nta Ijif k\u233?nj\u250?n, k\u233?tam\u233? fronde s\u233?nko ambum Faraone, efe y\u233?mor y\u225?njo lim\u225?n\u233?gh \u225?mnjogh sifayan, k\u233?t\u225?n fronde s\u233?nko ambum yuwon \u225?s\u225?fogh m\u233?rsoene emo ewafene flaw\u233?, w\u233?i fronde \u225?r\u225?f\u233?ghm\u233?n manjar\u233?gh w\u233?r\u225?rfene m\u233?inyotio so em k\u233?r. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 6\~}
F\u233?yo marataye yeyam so kofayong\u233? y\u233?nam\u233? m\u233?inyotio Ijif mbandam\u233?, a ye so nawerametat nden\u233? emo \u225?mb yau n\u225?y\u225?retam fronde a yau so w\u233?ikor n\u233?ng\u225?y\u225?retat. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 7\~}
Israil \u225?rfefafm\u233? so y\u233?m merro yau \u225?mb \u225?gh\u233? so nawanamnde, f\u233?yo f\u233?m mat so n\u233?m nden\u233? Yuram yafrote falogh y\u233?fefaf Ijif \u225?r Israil \u225?r. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 8\~}
M\u233?inyotio ofis \u225?s\u225?fogh t\u233?fn\u225?r so n\u233?n\u233?rsat y\u233?nan tafaf a n\u233?nuitat mbandot tar\u233?re, "Gh\u233?rgh\u233?rsis\u233? kuwanongi! Y\u233?mofem so w\u233?mndetat, w\u233?keye! A tangwasrogh m\u233?inyotio fene waitogh \u225?r f\u233?mo y\u233?mayanyo y\u233?nd t\u225?f so kuwanong!" F\u233?yo n\u233?kwaf\u233? Moses\u233?m t\u233?frangong\u233? Farao.
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 9\~}
Yuram t\u233? y\u233?mndai Moses fronde, "Faraom yau so niy\u225?rete f\u233?m, w\u233?nde y\u233?ndon m\u233? so ewafrotan ndimbal s\u233?lngw\u233?laf\u233? yam Ijif mbandan." {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 10\~}
Moses a Aron y\u233?mofem tawafrogh\u233?t y\u233?n\u233? s\u233?lngw\u233?laf\u233? Faraoner\u233?re, w\u233?nde Yuram t\u233? Faraone tik\u233?f t\u225?ik\u233?r yiy\u225?to a y\u233?mo yau m\u233? so taumyongai Israil \u225?r korongay\u233?nd yu.
