\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 1\~}
Njam Israil \u225?r m\u233? tamorw\u233?n Ijif yuwon, Yuram ewaramai waitogh\u233?t si y\u225?fafm\u233? Moses a Aron. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 2\~}
"S\u233?nonjo y\u233?nandm\u233?, y\u233?n\u233? gh\u233?rare so fiy\u233?m fronde gh\u233?rare y\u233?n\u233? yunj\u233?fm\u233?n f\u233?feyot. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 3\~}
Mat t\u225?y\u225?to m\u233?inyotio Israil \u225?r 10 efogh njam kawerang\u233? y\u233?n\u233? gh\u233?rareyan f\u233?natayero m\u233?rnam t\u225?f tawatnangi tos\u233? kau o tos\u233? gout m\u233?n\u225?t gh\u233?ng\u233?n ramgh\u233?t, \u225?mbiro w\u233?r\u225?r \u225?mbiro m\u233?ngot. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 4\~}
Njam y\u233?n\u233? m\u233?r\u233?n em n\u233?mbnarfifi m\u233?n\u225?t s\u225?i y\u233?netat m\u233?inyotio y\u233?n\u233? w\u233?r\u225?r so y\u233?mofem tawaftangi y\u233?maf\u233? \u225?mb m\u233?rnaf\u233? kaka f\u250?tarf\u233?. Y\u233?falotat kor w\u233?r m\u233?r\u233?n f\u233?yotaroam\u233? a nder\u233?m\u233?n\u233? so enetat. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 5\~}
W\u233?r\u225?r siya tawaf\u233?rngi f\u233?mofem t\u225?f aem \u225?mbiro yunj\u233?fm\u233?n ghak\u233?r w\u233?r\u225?r t\u233?u y\u233?m sif o gout \u225?sogh\u225?soghofnar. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 6\~}
Kor a ewarawenati y\u233?n\u233? f\u233?nataye kaf\u233?ghm\u233?n w\u233?r\u225?r k\u233?t\u225?notio 14m\u233?n efogh kawerang\u233? s\u233?ite y\u233?n\u233? fronde gh\u233?rare. F\u233?yo m\u233?inyotio Israil t\u225?f tasmangi y\u233?fenjo tot\u233?r kau o tot\u233?r gout efghon krufr\u225?tan. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 7\~}
