Y\u233?n\u233? s\u233?mb\u225?ranyo y\u233?mofem t\u225?f b\u233?laie en\u233?ghat fenjenfenjen a enetat kabesaf\u233? a Minaghofnaye flawaf\u233?. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 9\~}
Yau t\u225?f enetati fenjen gh\u233?rs\u233?gh\u233?rs\u233? o en\u233?ghati nu f\u233?se m\u233?inyotio w\u233?r\u225?r s\u233?nko ghafayo, ng\u225?ng\u233? a k\u233?nj\u250? rokar, t\u225?f a belaie erametati f\u233?s\u233?n. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 10\~}
Yau t\u225?f n\u233?m\u233? korongi akwtau ewak\u233?rnati \u225?rk\u233?m\u233?n\u233? yau n\u233?nefnar em yau t\u225?f em akwot. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 11\~}
Y\u233?n\u233? fem f\u233?feyot yam waitogh\u233?t y\u233?n\u233? n\u233?net m\u233?inyotio numanetati s\u225?l\u225?meye, nawotati f\u233?fenjo sandol, ersati f\u233?fenjo \u225?lighm\u233?n w\u233?tu f\u233?fenjo ng\u225?ngaye enetati fenjen mataf\u233?, m\u233?nam\u233?n y\u233?n\u233? siy\u233?m Yurane Waing\u233?gh t\u233?m\u233?nd.
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 12\~}
Y\u233?n\u233? s\u233?mb\u225?ran y\u233?nd so nawaindan Ijif mbandan a eng\u233?smetan m\u233?inyotio fronde s\u233?nko ambum a fronde s\u233?nko \u225?r\u225?f\u233?gh w\u233?r\u225?rm\u233?n Ijif mband k\u233?nj\u250?n. Y\u233?ndon so yafrotan mogh y\u233?fefaf Ijifm\u233?n ng\u225?nj\u225?n t\u233?rt\u233?r, m\u233?nam\u233?n y\u233?nd w\u233?m Yur\u233?. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 13\~}
W\u233?nde f\u233?r\u233?k f\u233?fene m\u233?ngo s\u233?safne s\u233?ras\u233?ran so em matot, euyafota m\u233?ngo fem \u225?nde emor. Njam y\u233?ndon tawinjon f\u233?r\u233?k, y\u233?ndon m\u233? so tukm\u233? tangwaindang\u233?n f\u233?m. Y\u233?n\u233? k\u233?raf\u233? k\u233?rt\u233? yamam yau so eyanje f\u233?m njam y\u233?ndon t\u233?smang\u233?n Ijif mband. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 14\~}
Y\u233?n\u233? efogh fiy\u233?m awafarogh\u233?t, yunjfero, k\u233?tam\u233? \u225?mb \u225?r sat\u233? k\u233?t\u225?n \u225?mb \u225?r sat\u233?, f\u233?mofem t\u225?f wafrotati y\u233?n\u233? nden\u233? f\u233?t\u233? f\u233?nataye t\u233?m\u233?nd k\u233?t\u225?n Yurai. Y\u233?n\u233? siy\u233?m n\u225?k k\u233?t\u225?notio. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 15\~}
7 efogh s\u225?i enetati flaw\u233? yistofnar t\u225?f ewafrotati, fronde efghon t\u233?mndan ewitormbotati m\u233?inyotio minagh f\u233?moghf\u233?mogh f\u233?fene m\u233?ngotu \u225?rk\u233? \u225?rom njam y\u233?neta flaw\u233? yist wanjm\u233?ghkaf y\u233?n\u233? 7 efoghf\u233?nef\u233?ne k\u233?nj\u250?n so tanfang\u233?m k\u233?tam\u233? Israil \u225?r tam. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 16\~}
Fronde efogh t\u233?mndan a w\u233?i 7 efghon, m\u233?inyotio \u225?r\u233?m t\u225?f yut\u233?mndat ofis \u225?s\u225?fogh efogh nj\u250?nnj\u250?nofnar \u225?umeng\u233?gh\u233?t. N\u233?m\u233? \u225?s\u225?fogh \u225?mb yau so ewafrotati y\u233?n\u233? efghon m\u233? k\u233?t\u225?ndro \u225?nde njamke efrendati. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 17\~}
Yafrotati y\u233?n\u233? minaghofnarm\u233?n flaw\u233? t\u233?m\u233?nd, y\u233?n\u233? yam so mwighayan nemnati f\u233?m nden\u233? y\u233?ndon en\u233?rsam\u233?n f\u233?fene waw\u233?rsogh waft\u233? eneutory\u233?n k\u233?tam\u233? Ijif mbandta y\u233?n\u233?fifi s\u233?nonjo efghon y\u233?n\u233? t\u233?m\u233?nd so y\u233?m ambino n\u225?k f\u233?feyot, y\u233?ngwafrotati y\u233?n\u233? efogh k\u233?tam\u233? f\u233?fene \u225?r sat\u233? k\u233?t\u225?n \u225?mb \u225?r sat\u233?. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 18\~}
Flaw\u233? f\u233?mofem s\u225?i enetati t\u225?f ewafrotati minaghofnar 14m\u233?n efghon s\u233?ite fronde gh\u233?rareyan k\u233?t\u225?notio kawerang\u233? 21 efogh y\u233?n\u233? gh\u233?rareyo. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 19\~}
Y\u233?n\u233? 7 efogh k\u233?s em yau n\u233?m\u233? minagh mbarmbar t\u225?f em f\u233?fene m\u233?ngom\u233? \u225?rk\u233? \u225?rom njam y\u233?neta minagh wanjm\u233?ghkaf y\u233?n\u233? efghon so tanfangi k\u233?tam\u233? Israil \u225?rf\u233? tamb\u233?n, Y\u233?n\u233? n\u225?kn\u225?k m\u233?inyotio em y\u233?feyot wan t\u233?fn\u225?r efe em f\u233?fene k\u233?nj\u250?n a Israilm\u233?nyo \u225?r\u225?f\u233?gh t\u233?fn\u225?r. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 20\~}
Y\u233?n\u233? efogh k\u233?s em f\u233?mofem yau t\u225?f enetat \u225?rk\u233?m\u233?n\u233? njam minagh wanjmeng\u233?ghkaf em. \u193?nde f\u233?m ekam, enetati m\u233? flawaro minaghofnar.
