F\u233?yo Moses tawanmong\u233? m\u233?inyotio s\u233?nko \u225?r Israilm\u233?n \u225?mbirofaf\u233?t a tamndang\u233? f\u225?, "Tang\u233?m tanwerangi tot\u233?r kau a tot\u233?r gout f\u233?fene m\u233?r\u233?n f\u233?yotaroan a tasmangi aWaing\u233?gh t\u233?m\u233?nd w\u233?r\u225?r. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 22\~}
F\u233?r\u233?k ewararotati k\u233?t\u225?n Disfaf tawanangi isof kafekafe a tauwarngi k\u233?t\u225?n f\u233?r\u233?kfaf y\u233?s\u233?nati isof\u233? y\u233?nam\u233? tukta a t\u233?ndo s\u233?safneta f\u233?fene m\u233?ngota. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 23\~}
Yur\u233? so nawainde y\u233?n\u233? yuwom\u233? m\u233?n\u225?t s\u225?i esmeta Ijifm\u233?n \u225?r. W\u233?nde y\u233?mo njam efanda f\u233?r\u233?k tuk\u233?n a t\u233?ndon s\u233?safne man\u233?ghfaf. Yuram so engwande f\u233?fene m\u233?ngo. Y\u233?mo yau so eumyote y\u225?njo k\u233?r si r\u233?sagh \u225?r k\u233?nyawangi f\u233?fene m\u233?ngot a esmetat f\u233?m. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 24\~}
Nawafarotati y\u233?n\u233? waufarogh siy\u233?m ambino n\u225?k f\u233?myo a f\u233?fene \u225?kiambum a ewafrotati tuot. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 25\~}
Njam f\u233?m kufarngi y\u233?n\u233? yu Yuram \u225?rk\u233?m\u233?n\u225?t uny\u233?ghofnar si t\u233? emndai f\u233?m. F\u233?mofem m\u233? so y\u233?ngwafrotati y\u233?n\u233? t\u233?m\u233?nd. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 26\~}
F\u233?yo f\u233?fene ambum so namotat, 'Y\u233?n\u233? t\u233?m\u233?nd ndern\u225?yefifi y\u233?m?' {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 27\~}
A f\u233?m so n\u233?wangotati, y\u233?n\u233? siy\u233?m w\u225?ng\u233?gh t\u233?m\u233?nd gh\u233?ng\u233?n ram\u233?gh y\u225? Yurai. Y\u233?mo tawindau m\u233?ngo Israil \u225?rfene Ijif\u233?n a w\u233?i t\u225?smetau Ijif \u225?r, y\u233?mo tawarawenau t\u233?fene m\u233?r\u233?n." Njam Mosesene si nefoi, m\u233?inyotio \u225?r niyay\u233?nd mbandot y\u225?wefnoy\u233?nd. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 28\~}
F\u233?yo Israil \u225?r\u233?m tawafrotaw\u233?t nden\u233? f\u233?t\u233? Yuram ndern\u225?ye tawafaretau Moses a Aronfene k\u233?nj\u250?m\u233?.
