A y\u233?n\u233? s\u233?mb\u225?r n\u233?ndk\u233?f fifiyan, Yuram t\u225?smetau m\u233?inyotio fronde s\u233?nko ambum Ijif mbandan, k\u233?tam\u233? fronde s\u233?nko ambum Faraone, efe t\u233?morang\u233?rw\u233?n y\u225?njo lim\u225?n\u233?gh \u225?mnjogh sifayan, k\u233?t\u225?n fronde s\u233?nko ambum kw\u233?fkw\u233?f m\u233?ngo n\u225?uw\u233?gh \u225?roene. W\u233?i manjar\u233?gh w\u233?r\u225?rafene fronde s\u233?nko \u225?r\u225?f\u233?ghm\u233?n t\u225?smetau. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 30\~}
