Moses\u233?m taufrotau yanate m\u233?inyotio Yuram n\u233?m\u233? tafrotau Faraofaf a Ijif Israil \u225?rfene t\u233?fnan. Y\u233?mo w\u233?i taufarotau m\u233?inyotio t\u225?ik\u233?r yamm\u233?n y\u233?mofem \u225?rk\u233? t\u233? mat k\u225?y\u225?totaw\u233?t \u225?lighan a ndern\u225?ye Yuram t\u233? ewanjary\u233?ng y\u225?njo \u225?r k\u233?tam\u233? y\u233?fene m\u233?inyotio k\u233?rt\u233?yamta. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 9\~}
Jetro t\u233?morw\u233?n \u225?uw\u233?ghan njam f\u225? n\u225?y\u225?rai m\u233?nam\u233?n m\u233?inyotio meryamm\u233?n Ng\u225?nj\u225?nam \u225?rk\u233? tawafrotau Israil \u225?r\u233?t nden\u233? f\u233?t\u233? y\u233?mo ewanjary\u233?ng k\u233?tam\u233? Ijif mbandta.
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 10\~}
Jetro norayai, "Yuwetam Yur\u233?, y\u233?mo t\u233? ewanjary\u233?ng Ijif \u225?rfeta a Faraota. N\u233?m\u233?w\u233?t, y\u233?mo t\u233? ewanjary\u233?ng Israil \u225?r k\u233?tam\u233? Ijif \u225?rfene waft\u233? ng\u225?ngata! {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 11\~}
Y\u233?nd mat w\u233?m s\u233?nonjo nden\u233? Ng\u225?nj\u225?n siy\u233?m ndimbalfifi \u225?mb ng\u225?nj\u225?nta, m\u233?nam\u233?n y\u233?mo ewanjary\u233?ng y\u225?njo \u225?r k\u233?tam\u233? tuktuk yam s\u233?nan\u233?ghta Ijif \u225?rfene."
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 12\~}
F\u233?yo Jetro, Mosesene yanat\u233?m y\u233?n\u233?rsam w\u225?roghm\u233?n gh\u233?ng\u233?n ram\u233?gh a yaramay\u233?nd Ng\u225?nj\u225?ne. Aron a m\u233?inyotio s\u233?nko \u225?r Israilm\u233?n n\u233?ntory\u233?nd enmorm\u233?n nufnyay\u233?nd y\u225?faf gh\u233?ng\u233?n ram\u233?gh njamke k\u233?nj\u250?n Ng\u225?nj\u225?nene s\u225?fan.
\par\pard\plain \s105\qc\fi0\lin0\rin0\sb160\sa80\b\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 Jetroene k\u225?fet\u233? wawanjagh mwigh\u233?
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 13\~}
\u193?mb efghon, Moses yanai \u225?mnjogh sifay\u233? m\u233?n\u225?t s\u225?i k\u225?y\u225?retau \u225?rfene as\u233?nan\u233?gh y\u233?fenjo k\u233?nj\u250?n. F\u225? tamorw\u233?n y\u233?maf\u233? k\u233?tam\u233? akw k\u233?t\u225?n s\u233?ite.
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 14\~}
Njam Mosese yanat\u233?m yinjoi y\u233?n\u233? m\u233?inyotio Moses\u233?m n\u233?m tawafrotau \u225?r\u233?t, f\u225? kamotang\u233?, "N\u233?m\u233? f\u233?mo fifi y\u233?na ewafrote? N\u233?mam\u233?n f\u233?mo y\u233?n\u233? ewafrote m\u233?inyotio t\u225?f njam m\u233?inyotio \u225?r ewakai n\u233?marendangi f\u233?m k\u233?tam\u233? akw k\u233?t\u225?n s\u233?ite?"
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 15\~}
Moses\u233?m yawangoi, "M\u233?nam\u233?n \u225?r en\u233?m tafaf m\u233?n\u225?t s\u225?i eng\u233?rsat lim\u225?n\u233?gh k\u233?tam\u233? Ng\u225?nj\u225?neta. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 16\~}
Njam amror\u233?gh nanota, f\u225? en\u233?m tafaf, y\u233?nd y\u233?n\u233? f\u233?gh\u233?m emo efrende k\u233?rt\u233? amror\u233?gh m\u233?rnafene, y\u233?ndo mat ey\u225?totan \u225?r Ng\u225?nj\u225?nene n\u225?k a ewarametan y\u225?ne waitogh\u233?t si."
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 17\~}
Moses yanat\u233?m korayang\u233?, "Y\u233?n\u233? yau mer y\u233?m!" {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 18\~}
F\u233?m so yongnai n\u225?y\u225?tote f\u233?myo-a \u225?r, w\u233?i y\u233?n\u233? \u225?s\u225?fogh siy\u233?m minde k\u233?t\u233? a k\u233?rtaye y\u233?m feyot s\u225?i y\u233?frenda f\u233?mbia. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 19\~}
S\u233?nonjo k\u225?y\u225?r tafaf, a kwumyo y\u233?nd k\u233?maraman wawanjagh si, a so y\u233?m Ng\u225?nj\u225?n fefaf. F\u233?m m\u233? so n\u233?ng\u233?m s\u225?i n\u233?m \u225?rfene t\u233?fnan Ng\u225?nj\u225?nener\u233?re, en\u233?rsa y\u233?fene amror\u233?gh y\u225?faf.
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 20\~}
Ewatamete Ng\u225?nj\u225?nene n\u225?k, a ewarametat y\u225?ne waitogh si, ewarameta ndern\u225?ye so elimndat y\u233?fenjo gh\u233?rs\u233?. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 21\~}
W\u233?nde ekafeta m\u233?inyotio \u225?rta \u225?mb s\u233?nt\u233? mwighaf\u233? afalogh \u225?r emofem f\u233?rf\u233?raf\u233? y\u233?fandat Ng\u225?nj\u225?n a m\u233?ndm\u233?ndat efandat wafogh yam, ekafeta f\u225? lim\u225?n\u233?gh\u233?t 1,000, 100, a 10 \u225?r m\u233?rnat. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 22\~}
F\u225? so t\u250?m\u233?n f\u233?yotaro em \u225?rfene marataye amror\u233?gh freng\u233?gh\u233?t, w\u233?nde y\u233?mofem a en\u233?rsat ndimbal k\u233?rt\u233? y\u233?n\u233?m fefaf. Y\u233?fe lim\u225?n\u233?gh \u225?r\u233?m n\u233?mbnar k\u233?t\u233? so efandat y\u233?mofemro. Y\u233?mofem so ew\u225?ut\u225?nat k\u233?t\u233? r\u233?sagh\u233?t, s\u225?i yiy\u225?totat \u225?s\u225?fogh \u225?fr\u225?te feyot. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 23\~}
Njam f\u233?mo ewaitota y\u233?n\u233? wawanjagh, a njam Ng\u225?nj\u225?nam n\u233?mafareta f\u225? s\u225?i yafrota, f\u233?yo f\u233?mo so t\u225?f yamarote y\u233?n\u233? muy\u233?, a m\u233?inyotio y\u233?n\u233? \u225?r so eng\u233?m m\u233?ngotuot \u225?uw\u233?ghaf\u233?."
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 24\~}
Moses k\u225?y\u225?retau y\u225?natene wawanjagh a tawaitotau y\u225?ne si. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 25\~}
Y\u233?n\u233? \u225?r t\u250?m\u233?n t\u233?morw\u233?n s\u225?i tawafrendau marataye amror\u233?ghm\u233?n. Y\u233?mofem tan\u233?rsaw\u233?t ndimbal k\u233?rt\u233? Mosesefaf, w\u233?nde f\u225? kawarawenaw\u233?t n\u233?mbnar k\u233?tayan f\u225?yo. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 26\~}
Tekofnar y\u233?n\u233? soram\u233? Moses\u233?m otemb\u233?ghm\u233?n mer si yaramai y\u225?njo yanate, efe n\u233?ngangotam k\u233?t\u225?n y\u225?njo mbandot. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 27\~}

