S\u243?mbio gh\u233?rare fifiyan y\u233?n\u233? soram\u233? Israil \u225?r\u233?m noroy\u233?nd Ijif, f\u225? nufary\u233?nd Sainai fanfne yuwot. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 2\~}
M\u233?ngotu wiror\u233?gh soram\u233? k\u233?t\u233? Refidim, f\u225? enmorm\u233?n k\u233?t\u225?n fanfne yuwot Sainay\u233?n a m\u233?ngot y\u233?frendam\u233?nd k\u233?t\u225?n Sainai mband tunak\u233?f t\u233?fnan.
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 3\~}
F\u233?yo Moses narmbotam mband tunak\u233?f Ng\u225?nj\u225?nr\u233?re ufargh\u233?t. Yuram y\u233?nmotai f\u225? k\u233?tam\u233? mband tunak\u233?fta a k\u233?norayang\u233?, "Tawaram si wafrogh\u233?t y\u233?fe Jeikofene m\u233?rnat; mat engy\u225?tota Israilm\u233?n \u225?kiambum: {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 4\~}
'F\u233?mo t\u233? tafande y\u233?ndon n\u233?m\u233? tawafrotan Ijif \u225?rfefaf f\u233?m mat n\u233?m y\u233?ndon ndern\u225?ye tarsan ndik\u225?k\u233? njambe a tan\u233?rsan tafaftio. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 5\~}
S\u233?nonjo njam f\u233?mofem wiy\u225?totati y\u233?nd a yeretati tane \u225?rny\u233?gh f\u233?maf\u233?, f\u233?m so em tane f\u233?nataye tuk\u233?n \u225?r k\u233?tam\u233? m\u233?inyotio \u225?mb \u225?rta mbandan; m\u233?nam\u233?n m\u233?inyotio mband y\u233?m tane. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 6\~}
A f\u233?m so em tane Ng\u225?nj\u225?n lim\u225?n\u233?gh gh\u233?ng\u233?n w\u225?rogh \u225?r, tane ndimbal yu.' Y\u233?n\u233? fiy\u233?m si f\u233?mo t\u225?f tawaram y\u233?fe Israil \u225?r\u233?t."
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 7\~}
F\u233?yo Moses n\u233?nangotam k\u233?tam\u233? mband tunak\u233?fta a tawanmong\u233? \u225?rfene s\u233?nko \u225?r a tawaufrotau m\u233?inyotiom\u233?n Yuram ndern\u225?ye tafaretau f\u225?. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 8\~}
A m\u233?inyotio \u225?r namyotay\u233?nd m\u233?rne, "Y\u233?ndfem so ewafrotam m\u233?inyotio Yuram k\u233?s y\u233?nmafarete." F\u233?yo Moses\u233?m y\u233?nmangotam \u225?rfene wangogh si k\u233?t\u225?n Yurafaf.
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 9\~}
F\u233?yo Yur\u233? korayang\u233? Mosesefaf, "Y\u233?nd so w\u233?n\u233?m f\u233?fefaf nu kw\u233?f k\u233?nj\u250?m\u233?, Moses, m\u233?n\u225?t \u225?r\u233?m y\u233?mofemyo so wiy\u225?totat njam y\u233?nd noraiw\u233?n f\u233?maf\u233?. F\u233?yo y\u233?mofem so efalo niy\u225?totat."
