 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 10\~}
F\u233?yo Yuram t\u233?mndang\u233? Moses, "Ngewor a efenda \u225?r tane ufar\u233?ghm\u233?n. Ewatetari f\u225? s\u233?nonjo a k\u225?ye, a eumbenat y\u233?fenjo s\u225?l\u225?me. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 11\~}
F\u225? so em freng\u233?ghkaf nambio efghon, y\u233?n\u233? efghon Yur\u233? so k\u233?neworng\u233? k\u233?t\u233? Sainai mband tunakfan s\u225?i m\u233?inyotio \u225?r\u233?m y\u233?fandat. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 12\~}
Ekmetati fu m\u233?inyotio y\u233?namam\u233? mband tunak\u233?fm\u233?. Mat ey\u225?totati \u225?r, 'K\u233?r aem! Yau ta eng\u233?m narmbotati mband tunak\u233?f, o eyanjati y\u233?nayoene fu, \u225?rk\u233? \u225?rom njam tiy\u225?njang\u233? mband tunak\u233?f so f\u233?yotaro t\u233?kmangi krot. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 13\~}
Yau \u225?mb ng\u225?ngayam so eyanje \u225?r o w\u233?r\u225?r \u225?rk\u233?m\u233?n\u233? n\u233?f\u233?rmetat fu, w\u233?nde ewafyafotati w\u237?me, o ewafyafotati fimbe. F\u225? t\u225?f ekmetati krot.' W\u233?nde t\u225?f goutoene t\u225?rt\u225?ram njam yatembeta tom ke, a m\u233?inyotio \u225?r f\u233?rf\u233?r em."
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 14\~}
F\u233?yo Moses ngeworng\u233? k\u233?t\u225?n \u225?rfefaf. Y\u233?mo tauwatetau f\u225? m\u233?n\u225?t w\u225?wefnogh\u233?t a y\u233?mofem taumbnaw\u233?t y\u233?fenjo s\u225?l\u225?me. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 15\~}
Y\u233?mo tamndang\u233?, "Nafrendati nambiom\u233?n efghot, a k\u233?t\u225?notio nawarawenati walta."
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 16\~}
Nambiom\u233?n efogh akwan, aruruke kutnaw\u233?t a toy\u233? k\u225?smetaw\u233?t, a s\u233?njt\u233? nu kw\u233?f n\u233?newory\u233?nd mband tunak\u233?ffaf. K\u233?t\u233? t\u233?morw\u233?n tomb\u233? ndimbal ke k\u233?tam\u233? goutoene t\u225?rt\u225?rta, a m\u233?inyotio \u225?r tamorw\u233?n ngernger. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 17\~}
Moses\u233?m elimay\u233?ng eutory\u233?ng m\u233?ngo \u225?nde narametam\u233?nd m\u233?n\u225?t s\u225?i kaf\u225?ngongay\u233?nd Ng\u225?nj\u225?naf\u233?, a f\u225? nokayoy\u233?nd mband tunakfoene kafkafta. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 18\~}
M\u233?inyotio mband tunak\u233?f yafary\u233?ng kwamam m\u233?nam\u233?n Yur\u233? t\u233? n\u233?newory\u233?ng k\u233?t\u225?n f\u233?snit. Kwam kuyotau njafarot ndenanit kwam y\u233?nau y\u233?m s\u233?mend wafroghm\u233?n njamke f\u233?sm\u233?n, a m\u233?inyotio mband tunak\u233?f k\u225?s\u225?mbnetau mam\u233?ghraye. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 19\~}
Njam ke kanamndau goutm\u233?n t\u225?rt\u225?rta minde tuk\u233?n, Mosese norayai, a Ng\u225?nj\u225?nam toyaye yawangoi. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 20\~}
Yur\u233? n\u233?newory\u233?ng tukfifi Sainai mband tunak\u233?ffaf a y\u233?nmotati Moses k\u233?t\u225?n mband tunak\u233?f.
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 21\~}
F\u233?yo Yuram t\u233?mndang\u233? Moses, "Ngango ngewor a mat ey\u225?tota \u225?r yau t\u225?f n\u233?f\u233?rmetat fu m\u233?n\u225?t s\u225?i y\u233?fandat Yur\u233?, o k\u233?r so em. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 22\~}
