Njam \u225?r nuita y\u233?n\u233? nambio yaman, \u225?mb so y\u233?mor nden\u233? f\u233?t\u233? yuwek amaf mani faiofnar.
\par\pard\plain \s105\qc\fi0\lin0\rin0\sb160\sa80\b\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 K\u233?rt\u233? f\u233?natayero t\u233?kr\u225?tm\u233?n
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 12\~}
"\u193?rk\u233? \u225?rom t\u233?krat y\u233?fande a yesmete \u225?mb \u225?r so t\u233?kmangi krot. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 13\~}
W\u233?nde njam m\u233? y\u233?morm\u233?n nekambe t\u233?krat Ng\u225?nj\u225?nene umyoghan, y\u233?ndon so tuyafon sifay\u233? atnogh\u233?t \u225?ndan ngi t\u233?fn\u225?r so n\u233?rse awanjargh\u233?t. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 14\~}
Ndern\u225?ye njam, \u225?mb \u225?rom t\u233?smang\u233? \u225?mb \u225?r, t\u225?f ngi t\u233?fn\u225?r y\u233?roghati y\u233?nam\u233? tane gh\u233?ng\u233?n kitar\u233? tambne a t\u233?kmangi krot.
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 15\~}
"\u193?rk\u233? \u225?rom emo t\u225?sm\u233? af\u233? o am\u233? so t\u233?kmangi krot. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 16\~}
T\u233?nogh \u225?r so t\u225?kmangi krot, t\u233?u tawerangi k\u233?rtayan wafrogh sifayan o t\u233? \u233?ternay\u233?nd f\u225? manie nden\u233? f\u233?t\u233? faiofnar \u225?s\u225?fogh \u225?r.
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 17\~}
"\u193?rk\u233? \u225?rom emo yau eutumanuw\u233? af\u233? o am\u233? so t\u233?mangi krot.
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 18\~}
"S\u233?nonjo njam s\u243?mbio \u225?r namror\u233?t, \u225?mb \u225?rom t\u233?smang\u233? \u225?mb m\u233?naye w\u237?me o faise, a mboraf\u233? yau s\u225?i k\u233?r y\u233?m w\u233?nde y\u233?fely\u233?felan y\u233?k\u233?m. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 19\~}
Njam f\u225? soram\u233? f\u233?yotaro y\u233?m s\u225?i y\u233?yota t\u233?ndota w\u233?ikor m\u233?n\u225?yaf\u233? w\u233?tuaf\u233?, ngi t\u233?fn\u225?r yau so t\u233?kmangi t\u233?kratan w\u233?nde fai so nufrote y\u225?ne ngi uy\u233?gh sifay\u233? a so yaramete w\u225?ut\u225?r\u233?gh y\u225?ne m\u233?inyotio freng\u233?gh\u233?t.
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 20\~}
"Njam \u225?rom yesmeta y\u225?njo ghak\u233?r \u225?r o \u225?mb \u225?s\u225?fogh m\u233?r\u233?s w\u233?n ngie a faiofnar \u225?s\u225?fogh \u225?r k\u233?r y\u233?m y\u233?nayan, yur\u233? so t\u233?kratan t\u233?kmangi. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 21\~}
W\u233?nde njam faiofnar \u225?s\u225?fogh \u225?r mer k\u225?y\u225?tong\u233? \u225?mbiro efghon o s\u243?mbio, f\u233?yo yur\u233? yau so t\u233?kratan t\u233?kmangi, m\u233?nam\u233?n faiofnar \u225?s\u225?fogh \u225?r siy\u233?m Y\u225?ne.
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 22\~}
"S\u233?nonjo njam s\u243?mbio \u225?r n\u225?sm\u233?t, a y\u233?n\u233? \u225?sm\u233?ghan t\u233?smend \u225?mbam suaf\u233? amaf a f\u225? n\u225?r\u225?fta m\u233? ufer\u233?ghofnar yau njam kor y\u225?ne ngi mbor, \u225?r emo y\u233?smai amaf y\u225?njarene m\u233?ndeyan fai so yafrote a mogh t\u233?fn\u225?rafene efalo y\u225?togh. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 23\~}
W\u233?nde njam y\u233?m mindefifi mbor y\u233?n\u233? makan so y\u233?m t\u233?kratan: gh\u233?rs\u233? gh\u233?rsat. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 24\~}
gh\u233?k\u233?f gh\u233?kfot, s\u233?n s\u233?not, ng\u225?ng\u233? ng\u225?ngat, kafkaf kafkafot, {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 25\~}
f\u233?sm\u233?n f\u233?se w\u225?rogh f\u233?se w\u225?rogh\u233?t, a mbor mborot, tirar\u233?gh tirargh\u233?t.
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 26\~}
"Njam \u225?rom t\u233?smang\u233? y\u225?njo m\u233?nd faiofnar \u225?s\u225?fogh \u225?r ghak\u233?r o m\u233?r\u233?s gh\u233?kfan a gh\u233?k\u233?f t\u233? kumb\u233?rtote y\u233?mo so taumeye m\u233?nd faiofnar \u225?s\u225?fogh \u225?r yuwek gh\u233?k\u233?fm\u233?n faiot. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 27\~}
A \u225?rom njam s\u233?n y\u225?njo m\u233?nd \u225?s\u225?fogh ghakroene a m\u233?rsoene tafarmang\u233?, y\u233?mo so taumiye so engre yuweke s\u233?nm\u233?n faiot.
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 28\~}
Njam kauam y\u233?tumnda \u225?r ghak\u233?r a m\u233?r\u233?s krot, kau so w\u237?me yafyatotat, a y\u225?ne fifi yau so y\u233?netat, y\u233?n\u233? k\u233?rt\u233? k\u233?nj\u250?n ndern\u225?ye t\u233?u yur\u233? yau so y\u233?fandat uny\u233?gh \u225?r. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 29\~}
W\u233?nde kau njam y\u233?m y\u233?n\u233? yaman tum\u225?ng\u233?ghm\u233?n, a yur\u233? t\u233? mat yiy\u225?toy\u233?nd w\u233?nde yau tarawenau, njam kauam t\u225?f krot t\u233?smang\u233? \u225?mb \u225?r, so yafyatotat w\u237?me, a yur\u233? w\u233?i ndernayo so t\u233?kmangi krot. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 30\~}
Ndern\u225?ye t\u233?u, k\u233?r \u225?roene f\u250?tarfem t\u233?u tumyongi fai y\u225?ne gh\u233?rs\u233? taran\u233?ghm\u233?n, kau yuram so t\u233?frendang\u233? y\u225?njo gh\u233?rs\u233? y\u233?n\u233? faie \u225?rk\u233?m\u233?n\u225?t nomnendangi.
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 31\~}
Nden\u233?yameyo n\u225?kn\u225?k y\u233?m kauye njam y\u233?timnde ghak\u233?r ambum o m\u233?r\u233?s. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 32\~}
W\u233?nde kauam njam y\u233?tumnda faiofnar \u225?s\u225?fogh \u225?r, ghak\u233?r o m\u233?r\u233?s, w\u233?r\u225?r yuram so fai ewafrote faiofnar \u225?s\u225?fogh \u225?rfene yur\u233? 30 mani mbwe, a kau t\u225?f w\u237?me y\u233?namndat.
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 33\~}
T\u225?f \u225?mb \u225?rom njam y\u233?tana y\u233?kw a yau yafna, a kau o ndonki k\u233?nyawend k\u233?t\u233?. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 34\~}
Y\u233?kw yuram so m\u233?inyotio f\u225? nufrote w\u233?r\u225?r yurafaf w\u233?nde y\u233?mo tanang\u233? m\u233?n\u225?t so yamnde k\u233?r w\u233?r\u225?r.
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 35\~}
Njam \u225?mb \u225?roene kauam kal yafrota y\u225?f\u250?tarene kau a kal kau k\u233?r y\u233?m, f\u233?yo s\u243?mbio yurafem t\u225?f maniot tat\u233?rnang\u233?nd gh\u233?rs\u233? kau a efalot f\u225? y\u233?mofem f\u233?yotaroe. Y\u233?mofem w\u233?i t\u225?f efalot k\u233?t\u233? w\u233?r\u225?r. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 36\~}
W\u233?nde njam kau y\u233?m f\u233?r\u233?k erghan, w\u233?nde y\u233?nayoene yuram yau yamarota, f\u225? t\u225?f fai nufrota f\u233?yotaro-a gh\u233?rs\u233? kau k\u233?r kaufaf-w\u233?nde y\u233?mo so yamnde k\u233?r kau.
\par\pard\plain \s52\ql\fi0\lin0\rin0\sb160\sa80\b\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs33 22
\par\pard\plain \s105\qc\fi0\lin0\rin0\sb160\sa80\b\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 Wamb\u233?gh f\u233?fenjo rokar
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 1\~}
Njam \u225?mb \u225?rom oroe tanang\u233? kau o sif a t\u233?mang\u233? o maniot t\u233?t\u233?nang\u233?, oro t\u233?fn\u225?ram t\u225?f fai nufrota 5 kauye oro kaum\u233?n a 4 silf\u233? m\u233?nam\u233?n sif orom\u233?n.
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 2\~}
Njam oro t\u233?fn\u225?r terangi m\u233?ngo \u233?naughan a t\u233?smangi y\u233?n\u233? yaman krot, y\u233?n\u233? \u225?r emo oro t\u233?fn\u225?r y\u233?s\u233?m krotio yau y\u233?m k\u233?rtayan ngim\u233?n. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 3\~}
W\u233?nde y\u233?n\u233? njam nufrota efghon, f\u225? em krot y\u233?sem oro t\u233?fn\u225?r y\u233?m k\u233?rtayan ngim\u233?n.
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 "Oro t\u233?fn\u225?r efe terangi t\u225?f fai nufrota m\u233?inyotio rokarm\u233?n y\u233?mo oroe starse. Njam f\u225? yau fai nufrota, f\u225? t\u225?f t\u233?ngt\u233?rnangi faiofnar \u225?s\u225?fogh\u233?t m\u233?n\u225?t fai so nufrote y\u225?njo orom\u233?n. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 4\~}
Njam \u225?mb \u225?rom oroe tanang\u233? kau o ndonki o sif a y\u233?n\u233? tinjongi oro t\u233?fn\u225?rane sifayan, f\u233?yo oro t\u233?fn\u225?r t\u225?f fai nufrota f\u233?rghe oro w\u233?r\u225?rm\u233?n.
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 5\~}
"Njam w\u233?r\u225?ram enetat yus y\u233?fenjo sifayan o g\u233?reif mbwe m\u233?nj ndawan a yuram t\u233?ng\u233?frangonga k\u233?t\u225?n \u225?mb \u225?rfene w\u233?r\u225?r sifayafaf yus n\u233?net, f\u233?yo w\u233?r\u225?r yus t\u225?f mani fai nufrota k\u233?tam\u233? y\u225?njoyo merfifi raista o g\u233?reif mbwe m\u233?nj mbweta.
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 6\~}
"Njam f\u233?mo yuwarota w\u233?tw\u233?tro k\u233?ghat a f\u233?s k\u233?mboghofnar k\u225?y\u225?ronga a k\u233?f\u233?rnang\u233? \u225?mb \u225?roene ndau sifay\u233?, y\u233?ngwas\u233?rmbota kun o n\u233?f\u233?ghofnar rais o m\u233?inyotio njamke t\u233?f\u233?n, y\u233?n\u233? \u225?rom emo yafrota f\u233?s t\u225?f fai nufrota oling\u233?gh njamke t\u233?f\u233?nm\u233?n.
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 7\~}
T\u225?f \u225?mb \u225?rom njam t\u225?frangonga mani o njamke y\u225? f\u250?tarefaf waman\u233?gh\u233?t, a oroe tawanangi y\u225?f\u250?t\u225?rene m\u233?ngon, njam oro t\u233?fn\u225?r terangi f\u225? sem farufaru y\u233?n\u233? tuk\u233?n n\u233?m\u233? t\u233? oroe ewanai. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 8\~}
W\u233?nde oro t\u233?fn\u225?r yau njam terangi, y\u225? f\u250?tar so yakai Ng\u225?nj\u225?nener\u233?re, emo so yaf\u233?nmete njam y\u233?mo t\u233? oroe tawarse y\u233?fene rokar.
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 9\~}
T\u225?f njam \u225?snay\u233?gh eware s\u243?mbio \u225?rfene efe nafayo \u225?mb kaufaf, ndonki, sif, \u225?uw\u233?ghm\u233?n rokar, o \u225?mb oling\u233?gh rokar, s\u243?mbio \u225?r t\u225?f enre Ng\u225?nj\u225?nener\u233?re, a y\u233?n\u233? \u225?r efe Ng\u225?nj\u225?nam tinjonga k\u233?raf\u233? so f\u233?rghe fai yafrote \u225?mb \u225?r.
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 10\~}
"T\u225?f \u225?mb \u225?rom njam tafrangong\u233? ndonki, kau, sif, o \u225?mb w\u233?r\u225?r y\u225? f\u250?tarefaf wanjargh\u233?t, w\u233?nde k\u233?r y\u233?m, o kal nufrota o kengong\u233?, a \u225?rk\u233? \u225?rom yau yinjo n\u233?m\u233? nufrote. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 11\~}
Y\u225?f\u250?tarem so tanang\u233? sotot yuraner\u233?re. Njam yuram efalo tiy\u225?tong\u233? nden\u233? y\u225? f\u250?tar yau oro kufrote y\u225?ne rokarfaf, yuram t\u225?f tumyong\u233? moghm\u233?n y\u225?togh, a yau fai so y\u233?m. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 12\~}
W\u233?nde njam w\u233?r\u225?r t\u233? oroe yanangi, y\u233?n\u233? k\u233?rt\u233? wafrogh \u225?rom so fai nufrote k\u233?t\u225?n yurafaf. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 13\~}
Njam t\u233? t\u233?ft\u233?rnat k\u233?ghat w\u233?r\u225?ram, mbarmbar w\u233?r\u225?rfifi so tuyafongi matot, a yau fai \u225?mb so y\u233?m.
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 14\~}
"Njam \u225?mb \u225?rom watma tanang\u233? w\u233?r\u225?r yau f\u250?tarene a kal nufrota o k\u233?r y\u233?m njam yur\u233? yuk\u233?r y\u233?m, y\u233?n\u233? \u225?r emo watma y\u225?ne t\u225?f m\u233?inyotio f\u225? nufrota. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 15\~}
W\u233?nde njam yur\u233? m\u233? t\u233?morw\u233?n, n\u233?m\u233? fai yau so t\u233?morw\u233?n, a n\u233?m\u233? fai yau y\u233?m t\u225?fandro njam w\u233?r\u225?r maniot t\u233?ramangay\u233?nd, y\u233?n\u233? m\u225?m\u225?fifaf so tamong\u233? mani fayam.
\par\pard\plain \s105\qc\fi0\lin0\rin0\sb160\sa80\b\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 F\u250?tar yam
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 16\~}
"Njam \u225?r ghakrom yar\u233?mna m\u233?r\u233?s efe yau ereinm\u233?nd \u225?mb \u225?rf\u233? a yafrot wal y\u233?maf\u233?, y\u233?mo t\u225?f fai nufrota t\u233?fenjo yame a kawerang\u233?. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 17\~}
W\u233?nde y\u225?ref\u233? njam nakena m\u233?n\u225?t s\u225?i kawerang\u233? m\u233?r\u233?s, \u225?rom m\u233? so fai nufrote y\u225?refefaf y\u233?n\u233? awer\u233?gh fayan y\u233?n\u233? m\u233?rsoefaf.
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 18\~}
"F\u233?mofem yau t\u225?f eumyotati f\u233?r\u233?k suf\u233?gh \u225?r \u225?ligh\u233?t.
