a \u225?mb s\u233?n f\u233?tf\u233?tta k\u233?t\u225?n r\u233?rm\u233?ghfaf, ewafeindati y\u233?n\u233? k\u233?t\u225?n fader rokarfaf m\u233?nam\u233?n Efodm\u233?n k\u233?tam\u233? tik\u233?fta. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 26\~}
Ewafrot s\u243?mbio golm\u233?n ring a tafghend y\u233?n\u233? k\u233?t\u225?n \u225?mb s\u243?mbio w\u233?fm\u233?n rokar kw\u233?ndkw\u233?ndfaf k\u233?t\u225?n k\u233?nj\u250?ta sarifaf y\u233?namayo efodfaf. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 27\~}
Ewafrot w\u233?ikor s\u243?mbio golm\u233?n ring a tafghend y\u233?nd k\u233?t\u225?n fader rokar kw\u233?mbanfaf efod tik\u233?fta, kaka lainfaf w\u233?f umb\u233?ghm\u233?n tuk\u233?n efodm\u233?n. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 28\~}
W\u233?f rokar t\u225?f tambangi k\u233?t\u225?n kwasaumb\u233?ghfaf, m\u233?n\u225?t w\u233?fm\u233?n rokar yau so nafnende k\u233?tam\u233? efodta.
