"Njam nden\u233?m\u233?nayan Aron n\u233?nyaweta nj\u250?nnj\u250?nofnar sifay\u233?, y\u225?faf so em Israil ambumafene y\u233?tkw\u233?n y\u225?ne tikfan k\u233?t\u233? w\u233?fm\u233?n rokar mwigh\u233? wafrogh\u233?t s\u225?i m\u233? y\u233?ng\u233?m awafarogh\u233?t Yurafaf. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 30\~}
W\u233?i takm\u233?nd Urim a Tumim w\u233?fm\u233?n rokarfaf, so f\u225? ere Aronene tik\u233?f tukta njam t\u233? f\u225? n\u233?nyaweta Yurane waftafaf, t\u225?f Aron so nufande mwigh\u233? wafrogh\u233?t fifi Israil \u225?rfenem\u233?n an\u233? tikfan Yurafaf.
