\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 31\~}
Ewafrotati tomb\u233? s\u225?l\u225?me efodm\u233?n njafar ngarot s\u225?l\u225?meta, {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 32\~}
m\u233?n\u225?yaf\u233? saur\u233?ghkaf s\u233?nkoyot y\u233?fenjoyo n\u233?ndk\u233?fan k\u233?t\u233? so y\u233?m wafroghm\u233?n sar ndenanit kolayam yarende y\u233?n\u233? saur\u233?gh, m\u233?n\u225?t yau so karirarng\u233?. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 33\~}
Ewafrotati fomegrenait m\u233?nam\u233?n njafar ngarotm\u233?n, nd\u233?nd\u225?k ngarotm\u233?n a f\u233?rkat y\u233?kwy\u233?kwaf\u233? golm\u233?n b\u233?lesaf\u233? y\u233?fene n\u233?ndk\u233?fan. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 34\~}
Golm\u233?n bel a fomefrenait so r\u233?rke yafrotat wareng\u233?ghkaf s\u225?l\u225?me fedfedam\u233?. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 35\~}
Aron so yawo y\u233?n\u233? s\u225?l\u225?me njam f\u225? n\u225?s\u225?fota Yurane r\u233?re k\u233?nj\u250?n nj\u250?nnj\u250?nofnar sifayan. Njam f\u225? yawo y\u233?n\u233?, yau so k\u233?r y\u233?m.
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 36\~}
Y\u233?namayo ewafrotati m\u233?nden f\u233?w\u233?nf\u233?w\u233?nofnar golm\u233?n, a f\u233?r\u233?nf\u233?r\u233?n yafrotati ndenanit man\u233?ghkaf y\u233?n\u233? sifay\u233?: Nj\u250?nnj\u250?nofnar y\u233?m Yurafaf. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 37\~}
T\u233?fghangi m\u233?nden y\u233?nayaf\u233? njafar ngarot kodaf\u233? Aronene tik\u233?fta, \u225?nde f\u225? m\u233? k\u233?t\u233? so y\u233?m. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 38\~}
Aron t\u225?f yawo y\u225?njo s\u225?f sotan y\u233?mo so y\u233?monyo eng\u233?rse Israil \u225?rfene k\u233?rt\u233? njam y\u233?mofem ewatetat f\u233?nataf\u233?nat\u233? ram\u233?gh. F\u225? t\u225?f t\u250?m\u233?n yawo y\u225?njo s\u225?f sotan so Yuram t\u225?f eumyote \u225?r. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 39\~}
Yawafrotati \u193?roene s\u225?fs\u225?faf\u233? w\u233?f s\u225?l\u225?me k\u233?tam\u233? mer s\u225?l\u225?mem\u233?n, s\u225?f tengongi t\u233?ban y\u233?n\u233? s\u225?l\u225?meta mere. A w\u233?i ewafrotati sas, a f\u233?r\u233?n ewafrotati f\u233?r\u233?nf\u233?r\u233?naf\u233?. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 40\~}
Aronene ambumat, ewafrotati w\u233?f awogh s\u225?l\u225?me, sas a f\u233?natayero s\u233?nko wafar\u233?ghm\u233?n \u225?rk\u233? em kwayagharo. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 41\~}
Yawotati f\u233?fene an\u233? Aron a y\u225?ne ambum y\u233?n\u233? a sariaf\u233? s\u225?l\u225?meye a efrendati a ewatetati f\u225?, t\u225?y\u225?tongi \u225?s\u225?fogh\u233?t f\u225? m\u233?n\u225?t gh\u233?ng\u233?n w\u225?rogh \u225?s\u225?fogh so yafrotat.
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 42\~}
W\u233?i ewawafrotati k\u233?nj\u250? awogh s\u225?l\u225?me y\u233?feyot, s\u225?i ewawogh y\u233?namayo fifiyan, k\u233?tam\u233? mbork\u233?fta k\u233?t\u225?n y\u233?fene burab\u233?rfaf. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 43\~}
Y\u233?n\u233? t\u225?f ewawo njam Aron a y\u225?njo ambum n\u233?nyawetat w\u225?wefnogh m\u233?ngo o s\u225?i y\u233?ngwanetat gh\u233?ng\u233?n kitar\u233? nj\u250?nnj\u250?nofnar sifay\u233? k\u233?nj\u250?n m\u233?n\u225?t s\u225?i y\u233?fenjo gh\u233?ng\u233?n w\u225?rogh \u225?s\u225?fogh yafrotat. W\u233?nde yau y\u233?mofem so yafrotat m\u233?ndefnar k\u233?rt\u233? a k\u233?r em. Y\u233?n\u233? sem f\u233?yotio n\u225?k y\u233?feyot Aron a m\u233?inyotio y\u225?ne \u225?ki ambum y\u225? soram\u233?.
