Y\u233?n\u233? f\u233?m t\u233?m\u233?ndm\u233?n yam f\u233?mofem s\u225?i ewaitotati njam yatetati Aron a y\u225?njo ambum k\u233?s em m\u233?n\u225?t so n\u225?s\u225?fotat tayot nden\u233? f\u233?t\u233? gh\u233?ng\u233?n w\u225?rogh \u225?r: Tanangi kau tos\u233? a s\u243?mbio sif mborofnar. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 2\~}
F\u233?yo wit flawaye yistafnar ewafrotati f\u233?skaf flaw\u233? sut, fafat keik wanjm\u233?ghkaf olif oilf\u233?, bisket oil y\u225?toghkaf. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 3\~}
Ekmetati \u225?mbiro y\u225?fan m\u233?inyotio, a t\u225?kmangi k\u233?t\u233? w\u225?wefnogh m\u233?ngo enyaghaghkaf, y\u233?nayaf\u233? m\u233?rne kau tos\u233? a s\u243?mbio sif. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 4\~}
Tauyafongi Aron a y\u225?njo ambum k\u233?t\u233? enyaghaghfaf, a eumbnati nue. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 5\~}
Yawotati Aron y\u225?njo gh\u233?ng\u233?n w\u225?rogh s\u225?l\u225?meye, w\u233?f s\u225?l\u225?me tomb\u233? kar\u233?fkar\u233?f s\u225?l\u225?me m\u233?n\u225?yaf\u233? efodaf\u233?, efod a w\u233?fm\u233?n rokar, f\u233?yo y\u233?finati wamanegh sas Efodm\u233?n yarendati y\u225?njo fifiyan. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 6\~}
Tafayongi t\u233?ban y\u225?ne s\u233?nkoyan, a tafarend utman\u233?gh m\u233?ndef\u233? k\u233?t\u225?n t\u233?banfaf. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 7\~}
F\u233?yo t\u233?faghangi f\u225? m\u233?naye yasunati faghar\u233?gh oile s\u233?nko tuk\u233?n. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 8\~}
Y\u233?namayo tauyafongi y\u225?ne ambum a ewawotati y\u233?fenjo w\u233?f s\u225?l\u225?me. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 9\~}
Efinati sas karatam\u233? ewarenati Aronefaf a y\u225?ne ambumafefaf, a tawafayongi f\u233?nataf\u233?nat\u233? s\u233?nko wafar\u233?ghm\u233?n y\u233?fefaf. F\u233?yo mbark\u225?nd gh\u233?ng\u233?n w\u225?roghfaf so y\u233?m y\u233?fene m\u233?n\u225?yan n\u225?kan.
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 "Y\u233?n\u233? ende, f\u233?mo so t\u233?teta Aron a y\u225?ne ambum k\u233?s em.
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 10\~}
"T\u233?nmanangi tot\u233?r kau k\u233?t\u225?n w\u225?wefnogh s\u233?safnefaf, \u225?nde Aron a y\u225?njo ambumam so efayotat ng\u225?ng\u233? y\u233?fenjo s\u233?nkoyam\u233?. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 11\~}
F\u233?yo t\u233?smangi kau Yurane s\u225?fan k\u233?t\u233? w\u225?wefnogh m\u233?ngo s\u233?safnefaf. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 12\~}
Takmangi \u225?mb y\u233?n\u233?mam\u233?n f\u233?r\u233?k gh\u233?ng\u233?n w\u225?rogh kitar\u233? tartarfaf f\u233?fenjo ng\u225?ng\u233? mine, a tasurngi \u225?mb n\u233?ndk\u233?fan gh\u233?ng\u233?n w\u225?rogh kitarayan. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 13\~}
Tawanangi m\u233?inyotio nj\u233?mar k\u233?nj\u250? rokarm\u233?n, a gh\u233?ng\u233?n tomb\u233? t\u233?f\u233?n a s\u243?mbio y\u233?sey\u233?se a nj\u233?mar y\u233?nam\u233?, a ewakernati m\u233?inyotio gh\u233?ng\u233?n w\u225?rogh kitarayan. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 14\~}
F\u233?yo m\u233?inyotio kau fifi, y\u233?nayaf\u233? y\u225?ne ngar, fenjen, nj\u233?nnj\u233?n, a tawarongi m\u233?ngotu a lim\u225?n\u233?gh t\u233?ndota nden\u233? f\u233?t\u233? yaufiyam gh\u233?ng\u233?n ram\u233?gh. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 15\~}
Yanamayo Aron a y\u225?ne ambumam t\u225?f tafayongi y\u233?fenjo ng\u225?ng\u233? \u225?mb sifoene s\u233?nkoyan. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 16\~}
F\u233?yo t\u233?mangi sif, a y\u233?ngkayotati y\u225?ne f\u233?r\u233?k gh\u233?ng\u233?n w\u225?rogh kitar\u233? t\u233?ndom\u233?. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 17\~}
Y\u233?nfetati sif fenjen a eumnati k\u233?nj\u250? rokar a ghamb\u233?r a t\u225?kmangi nayue s\u233?nkota a \u225?mb fifi fenjen. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 18\~}
F\u233?yo yak\u233?rnati m\u233?inyotio w\u233?r\u225?r gh\u233?ng\u233?n w\u225?rogh kitarayan. Y\u233?n\u233? fiy\u233?m w\u225?rogh gh\u233?ng\u233?n ram\u233?gh y\u225?yot Yurai.
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 19\~}
"S\u233?nonjo tanangi \u225?mb sif, a so Aron a y\u225?njo ambumaf\u233? tafayongi y\u233?fenjo ng\u225?ng\u233? y\u233?n\u233? s\u233?nkoyan. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 20\~}
F\u233?yo t\u233?smangi y\u233?n\u233?, a y\u233?n\u233? f\u233?rke tawayatongi tamb\u233?nta Aronene t\u233?ngan t\u233?f\u233?n a y\u225?ne ambumafene. W\u233?i tawakayongi tamb\u233?n ng\u225?ng\u233? s\u233?nko ndamban a tamb\u233?n ghamb\u233?rta ndimbal s\u233?nko ndamban, y\u233?kyotati f\u233?r\u233?k gh\u233?ng\u233?n w\u225?rogh kitar\u233? t\u233?ndom\u233?. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 21\~}
F\u233?yo tawanangi \u225?mb f\u233?r\u233?k k\u233?tam\u233? gh\u233?ng\u233?n w\u225?rogh kitarata a \u225?mb f\u233?ghm\u233?n oil a ey\u225?totati Aron\u233?f y\u225?njo ambumafayo a y\u233?fene s\u225?l\u225?me. Y\u233?n\u233? ende, f\u225?yo a y\u233?fene s\u225?l\u225?me so em f\u233?nataye nj\u250?nnj\u250?nofnar.
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 22\~}
Nden\u233? f\u233?t\u233? y\u233?n\u233? siy\u233?m efalofifi sif m\u233?n\u225?t Aron a y\u225?njo ambum f\u225?ghargh\u233?t, tawanangi sif n\u233?mar, y\u233?nayafayo wasamngogh ker nj\u233?maraf\u233?, nj\u233?mar k\u233?nj\u250? rokaram\u233?, enj\u233?m m\u233?njam\u233? a s\u243?mbio y\u233?sey\u233?seyam\u233? a nj\u233?mar y\u233?n\u233? yam\u233? warengaghare. Y\u233?nayaf tamb\u233?n burab\u233?raf\u233?. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 23\~}
F\u233?yo tanangi ambinotaro f\u233?skaf flaw\u233? sut, \u225?mbiro fafat keik olif oil wanjmeng\u233?ghkaf a \u225?mbiro weifa k\u233?tam\u233? flaw\u233? yafta yistofnar \u225?rk\u233?m\u233?n\u233? y\u233?kmay\u233?nd Yurane s\u225?fan. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 24\~}
Takmangi y\u233?n\u233? m\u233?inyotio Aron a y\u225?ne ambumafene ng\u225?ngayan m\u233?n\u225?t so euyotat tuk\u233?t nden\u233? f\u233?t\u233? f\u233?nataye ram\u233?gh k\u233?t\u225?n Yurai. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 25\~}
Soram\u233? t\u225?f tawanangi y\u233?n\u233? flaw\u233? k\u233?tam\u233? y\u233?fene ng\u225?ngata, a ewarotati gh\u233?ng\u233?n kitarayan m\u233?rne m\u233?n\u225?yaf\u233? gh\u233?ng\u233?n ram\u233?gh w\u225?roghaf\u233?, y\u233?n\u233? siy\u233?m m\u233?ndef\u233? wimaf\u233? k\u233?t\u225?n Yurai, a f\u233?nat\u233? ram\u233?gh y\u225?yot. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 26\~}
F\u233?yo tanangi nono Aronene wateghm\u233?n sif, a tuyongi tuk\u233?t Yurane r\u233?re nden\u233? f\u233?t\u233? f\u233?nataye ram\u233?gh k\u233?t\u225?n y\u225?yot. F\u233?yo yamndati nden\u233? f\u233?t\u233? f\u233?fenjo awafgh\u233?t.
