Tafrendangi f\u233?nataye awaf\u233?gh\u233?t wateghkaf sif \u225?rk\u233?m\u233?n\u233? em Aronene a y\u225?ne ambumafene. Y\u233?nayafayo nono a burab\u233?r \u225?rk\u233?m\u233?n\u233? t\u233? euyoy\u233?nd Yurane r\u233?re nden\u233? f\u233?t\u233? f\u233?nataye ram\u233?gh yam. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 28\~}
Soram\u233? yuwon njam \u225?nde Israil \u225?r\u233?m yuyotat n\u233?mbnar kar\u233?fkar\u233?f ram\u233?gh, a awaf\u233?ghm\u233?n y\u233?namam\u233?n so t\u233?kmangi f\u233?nataye y\u225?yot Arone a y\u225?ne \u225?kiambum. Y\u233?n\u233? siy\u233?m y\u233?fene mbark\u225?nd, a y\u233?n\u233? siy\u233?m utman\u233?gh ram\u233?gh k\u233?tam\u233? Israil \u225?rta k\u233?t\u225?n Yurafaf.
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 29\~}
"\u193?roene utman\u233?gh s\u225?l\u225?me t\u225?f a em wam\u225?ng\u233?gh\u233?t y\u233?feyot y\u225?ne y\u225?kiyafet emofem efalo yiy\u225?toy\u233?nd, a f\u225? so nawotat t\u225?f f\u225? njam etetat a wafetat. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 30\~}
\u193?kiambum emo efalo tiy\u225?tong\u233? f\u225? nden\u233? f\u233?t\u233? gh\u233?ng\u233?n w\u225?rogh \u225?r so y\u233?wo y\u233?n\u233? s\u225?l\u225?me k\u233?t\u225?n 7 efogh njam f\u225? n\u225?s\u225?fota w\u225?wefnogh m\u233?ngo k\u233?nj\u250?n a nj\u250?nnj\u250?nofnar sifayan.
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 31\~}
"T\u233?ngwanangi sif \u225?rk\u233?m\u233?n\u233? tafrotat wategh t\u233?mndan, a nu f\u233?se eneghati y\u225?ne fenjen utman\u233?gh sifayan. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 32\~}
F\u233?yo Aron a y\u225?njo ambumaf\u233? so enetat y\u233?n\u233? fenjen, y\u233?nayaf\u233? yaf\u233?n flaw\u233? k\u233?s fenjen a flaw\u233? \u225?rk\u233?m\u233?n\u233? nawafrotam\u233?nd y\u233?fene wanyay\u233?gh\u233?t k\u233?t\u233? wategh tam\u233?ndfaf. Yau \u225?rk\u233? \u225?rom so enetat, y\u233?n\u233? rokar efrendam\u233?nd f\u233?nataye a nj\u250?nnj\u250?nofnar. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 33\~}
Y\u233?mofemro so enetat fenjen a flaw\u233? \u225?rk\u233?m\u233?n\u233? nawafrotam\u233?nd y\u233?fene w\u225?ny\u225?ny\u233?gh\u233?t k\u233?t\u233? wategh t\u233?m\u233?ndfaf. Yau \u225?rk\u233? \u225?rom so enetat, y\u233?n\u233? rokar efrendam\u233?n f\u233?nataye a nj\u250?nnj\u250?nofnar. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 34\~}
Njam \u225?mb wateghm\u233?n fenjen o flaw\u233? k\u225?l\u225?itangi k\u233?t\u225?n akwot, ta ewak\u233?rnati. Yau t\u225?f enetati y\u233?n\u233? em nj\u250?nnj\u250?nofnar.
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 35\~}
"Siy\u233?m y\u233?n\u233? ndern\u225?ye so yatetati Aron a y\u225?ne \u225?mb m\u233?r\u233?n k\u233?t\u225?n y\u233?fene ofis \u225?s\u225?fogh \u225?rfefaf, nden\u233? f\u233?t\u233? y\u233?ndon ndern\u225?ye ewafaretay\u233?n f\u233?m. Wategh t\u233?m\u233?nd so n\u233?ngarse k\u233?t\u225?n 7 efghot. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 36\~}
\u193?mbiro efghe f\u233?mo t\u225?f gh\u233?ng\u233?n yafrota tot\u233?r kau nden\u233? f\u233?t\u233? kau nden\u233? f\u233?t\u233? yaufiyam ram\u233?gh m\u233?n\u225?t yaufiyamta w\u225?ny\u225?ny\u233?gh y\u233?fe, eyatota mbark\u225?nd Yuraf\u233?. Soram\u233? y\u233?sambnati wafngogh m\u233?ngo m\u233?naye w\u225?ny\u225?ny\u233?gh y\u233?n\u233?. Yafrotati y\u233?n\u233? nj\u250?nnj\u250?nofnar m\u233?n\u225?yan y\u233?tetati m\u233?naye oile. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 37\~}
Yainati gh\u233?ng\u233?n kitar\u233? a y\u225?tetati t\u250?m\u233?n efogh k\u233?t\u225?n 7 efghot. Y\u233?n\u233? soram\u233?, gh\u233?ng\u233?n kitar\u233? mbark\u225?ndaye so y\u233?m nj\u250?nnj\u250?nofnar, a m\u233?n\u225?yam njam tiy\u225?njang\u233? so k\u233?namndang\u233? nj\u250?nnj\u250?nofnar.
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 38\~}
Sem y\u233?n\u233? gh\u233?ng\u233?n f\u233?mofem s\u225?i ewatetati t\u250?m\u233?n gh\u233?ng\u233?n kitarayan. T\u250?m\u233?n efogh taramend s\u243?mbio kau tos\u233? \u225?rk\u233?m\u233?n\u233? em \u225?mbiro yunj\u233?fm\u233?n. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 39\~}
\u193?mb akwan a \u225?mb s\u233?ite. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 40\~}
\u193?mbot siya y\u233?m t\u233?ramangi s\u243?mbio kar\u233?f m\u233?ndef\u233? flaw\u233? wanjmeng\u233?ghkaf \u225?mbiro kar\u233?f oilaf\u233? k\u233?tam\u233? tum\u225?ng\u233?gh olifta, t\u233?ramangi \u225?mbiro kar\u233?f w\u233?ri num\u233?n nden\u233? f\u233?t\u233? w\u233?kw\u233?r ram\u233?gh. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 41\~}
T\u233?ramangi \u225?mb sif s\u233?iteyan, y\u233?nayafayo f\u233?skaf flaw\u233? a w\u233?ri nu ram\u233?gh k\u233?s tam akwan, y\u233?n\u233? so y\u233?m m\u233?ndef\u233? wim a f\u233?nataye ram\u233?gh y\u225?yot k\u233?t\u225?n Yurai.
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 42\~}
"Y\u233?n\u233? w\u225?rogh ram\u233?gh t\u225?f ewafrotati t\u250?m\u233?n efogh k\u233?tam\u233? \u225?mb \u225?r sat\u233? k\u233?t\u225?n \u225?mb \u225?r sat\u233?. Erametati k\u233?t\u225?n Yurane r\u233?re k\u233?t\u233? w\u225?wefnogh m\u233?ngo s\u233?safnefaf. K\u233?t\u233? y\u233?ndon so taf\u225?ngon a norayam f\u233?mof\u233?. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 43\~}
Y\u233?ndon so taf\u225?ngon Israil \u225?r k\u233?t\u233?, y\u233?n\u233? sifayan nufrotam nj\u250?nnj\u250?nofnar n\u233?nayan tane ndimbal kwayagh\u233? freng\u233?gham.
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 44\~}
"N\u233?m\u233?w\u233?t, y\u233?ndon so yatetan w\u225?wefnogh m\u233?ngo a gh\u233?ng\u233?n kitar\u233?, a y\u233?ndon so yatetan Aron a y\u225?njo ambum k\u233?s em m\u233?n\u225?t so n\u225?s\u225?fotat nden\u233? f\u233?t\u233? gh\u233?ng\u233?n w\u225?rogh \u225?r. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 45\~}
F\u233?yo y\u233?nd so w\u233?mor Israil \u225?rfefafm\u233? a so w\u233?m y\u233?fene Ng\u225?nj\u225?n. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 46\~}
A f\u225? so mat em nden\u233? y\u233?nd w\u233?m Yur\u233? y\u233?fene Ng\u225?nj\u225?n. Y\u233?nd Y\u233?n\u233? f\u233?y\u233?m emo en\u233?utory\u233?ng k\u233?tam\u233? Ijif mbandta m\u233?n\u225?t y\u233?nd so kw\u233?morang\u233?rw\u233?n y\u233?fefaf, Y\u233?nd w\u233?m Yur\u233? y\u233?fene Ng\u225?nj\u225?n.
