F\u233?yo yafrotati \u225?mb gh\u233?ng\u233?n kitar\u233? mbiyar w\u233?nm\u233?n m\u233?n\u225?t gh\u233?ng\u233?n w\u225?rogh\u233?t. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 2\~}
Yafrotati 46 sentimit\u233? marate a 91 sentimit\u233? tuk\u233?t m\u233?n\u225?yaf\u233? tartaraf\u233? m\u233?n\u225?ta kw\u233?ndkw\u233?ndta yafrotati y\u233?nayayo w\u233?n kar\u233?fkar\u233?fe nden\u233?yameyo gh\u233?ng\u233?n kotar\u233? f\u225?yo. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 3\~}
Ewafnati tuk\u233?n t\u233?ndom\u233? a gh\u233?ng\u233?n kitar\u233? tartar m\u233?naye m\u233? golero a y\u233?rsati gole wafroghe yarendati m\u233?inyotio gh\u233?ng\u233?n kitar\u233?. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 4\~}
Ewafrot s\u243?mbio gol ring a tawafnend k\u233?t\u225?n gh\u233?ng\u233?n kitar\u233? s\u233?mtamb\u233?n yuwon gol wafroghm\u233?n m\u233?n\u225?t so y\u233?rete r\u233?saghm\u233?n s\u233?ras\u233?r. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 5\~}
Ewafrotati s\u233?ras\u233?r mbiyar w\u233?nm\u233?n a ewafnati m\u233?naye gole. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 6\~}
Takmangi mer wimaf\u233? gh\u233?ng\u233?n ram\u233?gh kitar\u233? k\u233?nj\u250? k\u233?t\u225?n t\u233?ndota \u225?rk\u233?m\u233?nayam t\u233?mnang\u233? \u225?rny\u233?gh boks, boks wafar\u233?gh frondeta sifayan \u225?rk\u233?m\u233?n\u225?yan ewafne n\u225?k ekai freng\u233?gh gh\u233?ng\u233?nm\u233?n m\u233?nam\u233?n freng\u233?gh t\u233?m\u233?ndm\u233?n, y\u233?ndf\u233? k\u233?t\u233? sif naf\u225?ngotam.
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 7\~}
T\u250?m\u233?n akwan Aron\u233?m njam ewafeinda tot\u233?r sif y\u233?mo t\u225?f ewarota mer wimaf\u233? gh\u233?ng\u233?n, gh\u233?ng\u233?n kitarayan. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 8\~}
A y\u233?n\u233? s\u233?iteyam\u233? njam y\u233?mo ewarota lambef\u233?, y\u233?mo t\u225?f w\u233?ikor ewarota gh\u233?ng\u233?n Yurane s\u225?fan. Y\u233?n\u233? t\u225?f ewafrotati k\u233?tam\u233? \u225?mb \u225?r sat\u233? k\u233?t\u225?n \u225?mb \u225?r sat\u233?. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 9\~}
Yau t\u225?f ewatetati nj\u250?nnj\u250?naf\u233? gh\u233?ng\u233?ngh\u233?ng\u233?n y\u233?n\u233? gh\u233?ng\u233?n kitarayan. O \u225?mb w\u225?rogh ram\u233?gh, rais mbwe ram\u233?gh a w\u233?kw\u233?r ram\u233?gh. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 10\~}
\u193?mbiro yunjfan Aron\u233?m t\u225?f f\u233?w\u233?nf\u233?w\u233?nofnar yiy\u225?tota gh\u233?ng\u233?n kitar\u233? m\u233?naye s\u225?i engy\u225?tota tartar f\u233?rke k\u233?tam\u233? gh\u233?ng\u233?n ram\u233?gh wafroghm\u233?n m\u233?n\u225?t \u225?r so tay\u225?tong\u233? f\u233?w\u233?nf\u233?w\u233?nofnar k\u233?tam\u233? y\u233?fene yaufita. Y\u233?n\u233? so fiy\u233?m t\u250?m\u233?n, yunjfe yam k\u233?tam\u233? \u225?mb \u225?r sat\u233? k\u233?t\u225?n \u225?mb \u225?r sat\u233?, m\u233?nam\u233?n y\u233?n\u233? siy\u233?m Yurane mindefifi nj\u250?nnj\u250?nofnar gh\u233?ng\u233?n kitar\u233?.
