M\u233?inyotio \u225?r efe s\u225?i ewafta t\u225?f ewarameta n\u233?mbnar kar\u233?fkar\u233?f silfam\u233?n nden\u233? f\u233?t\u233? utman\u233?ghaf\u233? ram\u233?gh Yurai. (Y\u233?n\u233? fai siy\u233?m mbarmbar mani t\u233?f\u233?n m\u233?n\u225?yan yunjfe mani, \u225?rk\u233? y\u233?m k\u233?t\u225?n 11.4 grams) {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 14\~}
M\u233?inyotio emofem t\u233? yeray\u233?nd y\u233?fenjo araf\u233?gh kw\u233?f 11.4 gramfaf erametat y\u233?n\u233? utman\u233?ghaf\u233? ram\u233?gh k\u233?t\u225?n Yurai. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 15\~}
