"Yafrota bronjm\u233?n umbar\u233?ghm\u233?n dis m\u233?n\u225?yaf\u233? bronjm\u233?n wakayoghm\u233?n, t\u233?kmangi y\u233?n\u233? w\u225?wefnogh m\u233?ngo a gh\u233?ng\u233?n kitar\u233? n\u233?ndk\u233?fan, a tafongi nue. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 19\~}
