Njam Moses k\u233?ngtorngai k\u233?t\u225?n farai m\u233?ngot \u225?umeng\u233?gh sifayat, m\u233?inyotio so kanotaw\u233?t a kokayotaw\u233?t y\u233?fenjo farai m\u233?ngo end s\u233?safnefaf. Y\u233?mofem so m\u233?inyotioyam t\u233?fandaw\u233?t Moses k\u233?t\u225?notio kolindangi k\u233?nj\u250?n. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 9\~}
Njam k\u233?nawangai farai m\u233?ngon nu kw\u233?f so k\u233?new\u233?rngay\u233?nd y\u233?n\u233? enyagh endfaf njam Yuraf koraiw\u233?t Mosesf\u233?. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 10\~}
Njam \u225?r\u233?m tinjongay\u233?nd nu kw\u233?f takayong\u233?rw\u233?n k\u233?t\u233? s\u233?safne \u233?nyaghfaf farai m\u233?ngon. F\u225? so kokayongay\u233?nd k\u225?wefnongay\u233?nd y\u233?fenjo farai m\u233?ngo s\u233?safneta. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 11\~}
Yuraf so korayaw\u233?t Mosesf\u233? s\u225?fero, nden\u233? f\u233?t\u233? \u225?r y\u233?nau norayet y\u225?f\u250?tar\u233?faf. Y\u233?n\u233? soram\u233? Moses so kangotau k\u233?t\u225?n m\u233?ngo aram\u233?gh sifayat, w\u233?nde tot ambum emo t\u225?ut\u225?nau, Josua Nunene ambum so m\u233? t\u233?morang\u233?rw\u233?n t\u233?ndon k\u233?t\u233? farai m\u233?ngo sifayan.
\par\pard\plain \s105\qc\fi0\lin0\rin0\sb160\sa80\b\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 Moses\u233?m t\u233?fandau Yurane ndimbal kwayagh\u233?.
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 12\~}
\u193?mb efghon Moses norayai Yurafaf, "F\u233?mo y\u233?nd t\u233? kw\u233?mndetau, 'Tang\u233?mnja y\u233?n\u233? \u225?r k\u233?t\u225?n uyafogh mbandfaf.' W\u233?nde f\u233?mo yau wafrogh emaf\u233? y\u233?ndf\u233? so y\u233?mafarew\u233?. F\u233?mo y\u233?nd t\u233? w\u233?mnde, 'Y\u233?nd mat namnday\u233?n fenem\u233?n m\u233?n\u225?yan y\u233?tkw\u233?nan, a y\u233?ndon m\u233?ndef\u233? n\u233?fandan f\u233?m.' {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 13\~}
Njam y\u233?n\u233? efalo y\u233?m nden\u233? f\u233?mon y\u233?nd m\u233?nde w\u233?fande, kw\u233?myo y\u233?nd mat s\u225?i w\u233?m fene end so mat kamndan fenem\u233?n m\u233?inyotio a m\u233?njtaye so yayamnetat fene m\u233?nde. A nawafarotan nden\u233? y\u233?n\u233? ndimbal yuwon sem fene \u225?r fifi em."
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 14\~}
Yuram yawangoi, "Y\u233?nd so f\u233?mafaro y\u233?nyow\u233?, Moses, a y\u233?ndon so k\u233?maram enagh m\u233?inyotio yam so y\u233?m merro fe."
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 15\~}
F\u233?yo Moses norayai, "Njam yau f\u233?maf\u233? y\u233?ndf\u233? y\u233?nyota, yau t\u233?ny\u225?to s\u225?i korong\u233?m y\u233?n\u233? sifay\u233?. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 16\~}
Ndern\u225?ye so \u225?mb \u225?r mat em nden\u233? f\u233?mon y\u233?nd m\u233?ndef\u233? w\u233?fande-y\u233?nd a fene \u225?r njam f\u233?maf\u233? yau y\u233?nyota? M\u233?nam\u233?n fene s\u225?fam t\u233?fefaf ekmete fene \u225?r a y\u233?nd f\u233?nataye k\u233?tam\u233? \u225?mb \u225?rta y\u233?n\u233? mbandan?"
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 17\~}
Yuram yawangoi Mosese, "Y\u233?ndon so y\u233?n\u233? yafrotan n\u233?mat f\u233?m t\u233? n\u243?mnenda, m\u233?nam\u233?n y\u233?nd m\u233?nde n\u233?retan fefaf, a y\u233?nd mat w\u233?m f\u233?m enayan y\u233?tkw\u233?nan."
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 18\~}
Moses namyoi, "F\u233?yo kwauyafo fene ndimbal kwayagh\u233?."
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 19\~}
Yuram yawangoi, "Y\u233?ndon so ewafrotan tane mer yam nawaindat fene r\u233?re, a y\u233?ndon so k\u233?maufron tane y\u233?tkw\u233?n, nden\u233? y\u233?nd sw\u233?m Yur\u233?. M\u233?nam\u233?n y\u233?ndon so yuyafotan gh\u233?rgh\u233?rsis\u233? k\u233?t\u225?n \u225?rk\u233? \u225?roefaf t\u233?u efe y\u233?ndon t\u233?kafan, a y\u233?ndo yuyafotan ng\u225?r\u225?mng\u225?r\u225?m k\u233?t\u225?n \u225?rk\u233? \u225?roe t\u233?u efe y\u233?ndon t\u233?kafan. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 20\~}
W\u233?nde f\u233?mo yau so y\u233?fande tane s\u225?f m\u233?nam\u233?n \u225?rk\u233? \u225?rom njam kwinjong\u233? yau so gh\u233?rs\u233? y\u233?m."
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 21\~}
F\u233?yo Yur\u233? noraye, "K\u233?reta! Y\u233?na y\u233?m sifay\u233? ta kaka \u225?nde f\u233?m so kokai w\u237?m tuk\u233?n. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 22\~}
Njam tane ndimbal kwayagh\u233? kawaindang\u233? fefafm\u233?, y\u233?ndon so k\u233?ntnon f\u233?m w\u237?m f\u233?neyan. Y\u233?ndo so tafar\u233?n fene s\u225?f tane ng\u225?ngaye k\u233?t\u225?notio y\u233?nd kawaindang\u233?n fefafm\u233?. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 23\~}
F\u233?yo y\u233?ndo so tawit\u233?rmbon tane ng\u225?ng\u233? a f\u233?mo so tinjo s\u233?m. W\u233?nde \u225?rk\u233? \u225?rom yau so tinjong\u233? tane s\u225?f."
\par\pard\plain \s52\ql\fi0\lin0\rin0\sb160\sa80\b\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs33 34
\par\pard\plain \s105\qc\fi0\lin0\rin0\sb160\sa80\b\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 Tot\u233?r wafarnjagh m\u233?nam\u233?n \u225?rny\u233?ghm\u233?n
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 1\~}
F\u233?yo Yuram y\u233?mndai Moses, tawerte s\u243?mbio w\u237?m kar\u233?f nden\u233? frondem\u233?n k\u233?s tam. Y\u233?ndon so efarotan nden\u233?yameyo y\u233?nayan \u225?rk\u233? tamorw\u233?n k\u233?t\u233? f\u233?mon setyareyai. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 2\~}
An\u233?m afreng\u233?ghkaf akwan s\u225?i narmbota Sainai mband tunak\u233?f a kauyafo f\u233?myo tafaf k\u233?t\u225?n fifi mband tunakfan. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 3\~}
\u193?mb \u225?rof\u233? yau so enre f\u233?maf\u233? mbark\u225?nde, \u225?rk\u233? \u225?r yau so kufarng\u233? \u225?nde k\u233?t\u233? mband tunakfan yau t\u225?f eumyota sif m\u233?r\u233?n o kau m\u233?r\u233?n yus y\u233?ngnetat mband tunak\u233?f t\u233?ndon."
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 4\~}
F\u233?yo Moses\u233?m ew\u233?rteyai s\u243?mbio w\u237?m kar\u233?f nden\u233? frondem\u233?n tarw\u233?n, T\u225?nd\u225?i akwan f\u225? karmbotau Sainai mband tunak\u233?f ndern\u225?ye Yuram t\u233? yafaretai f\u225? a y\u233?mo tarsew\u233?ng s\u243?mbio w\u237?m kar\u233?f y\u225?njo ng\u225?ngaye. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 5\~}
F\u233?yo Yur\u233? n\u233?new\u233?ry\u233?ng nu kw\u233?faf\u233? a nokayeyay\u233?nd y\u233?maf\u233?, a y\u233?mo y\u233?mndai y\u225?ne y\u233?tkw\u233?n, yaw\u233?. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 6\~}
Yur\u233? nawaindai Mosese tik\u233?f r\u233?re, k\u233?ngutnau, "Yaw\u233?! Yur\u233? Ng\u225?ramng\u225?r\u225?m a gh\u233?rgh\u233?rsisaye Ng\u225?nj\u225?n! Y\u233?nd teke w\u233?m n\u233?kwot a afoghkaf uw\u233?ghan a ndimbal mwighayan, {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 7\~}
y\u233?ndo yuwetan uw\u233?gh y\u233?fefaf 1,000 \u225?r sat\u233?. Y\u233?ndon engwawitan yaufi, \u225?y\u225?r\u233?ghofnar, a yaufiyam, w\u233?nde y\u233?ndon yau yumyotan k\u233?rt\u233?. Y\u233?ndon efayotan afaf a amaf y\u233?fene yaufiyam y\u233?fene ambumafefaf a \u225?ki ambumafefaf a m\u233?inyotio m\u233?r\u233?n y\u233?n\u233? yam y\u233?rse w\u233?i efe ambumt\u233?rt\u233?r em nambiom\u233?n m\u233?r\u233?n \u225?r sat\u233? a 4 m\u233?n m\u233?r\u233?n \u225?r sat\u233?."
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 8\~}
Moses tekofnar f\u225?yo nuyai mbandot a y\u225?wefnoi. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 9\~}
A f\u225? norayai, "O Yur\u233?, njam y\u233?n\u233? efalo nden\u233? y\u233?ndon t\u233? yinjon m\u233?ndefefaf, f\u233?yo gh\u233?rgh\u233?rsis\u233? so yinjota f\u233?maf\u233?, n\u233?m\u233?w\u233?t, y\u233?n\u233? sem t\u225?ik\u233?r tik\u233?ffaf a \u225?y\u225?r\u233?ghofnar \u225?r, w\u233?nde gh\u233?rgh\u233?rsis\u233? t\u233?nmawai t\u233?fene yaufi a t\u233?fene yaufiyam. T\u233?ny\u225?to y\u233?nd nden\u233? f\u233?t\u233? fendio f\u233?nat\u233? sifay\u233?."
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 10\~}
Yuram yawangoi, "K\u225?y\u225?rangi, y\u233?nd yafrotan \u225?rny\u233?gh f\u233?maf\u233? fene \u225?rfene s\u225?fan. Y\u233?ndon so ewafrotan s\u233?lngw\u233?laf\u233? yam \u225?rk\u233?m\u233?n\u233? yau kufrotat \u225?nde m\u233?inyotio mbandan o \u225?mb ndimbal yuwon. A m\u233?inyotio fene wereng\u233?gh \u225?r\u233?m so y\u233?fandat Yurane waft\u233? matot waft\u233? y\u233?nd so nambnan f\u233?feyot. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 11\~}
W\u233?nde kor n\u225?y\u225?retati merk\u233?r\u225?ye m\u233?inyotio y\u233?ndon sewafaretan s\u233?nonjo. F\u233?yo y\u233?nd so w\u233?ng\u233?m frondeyo a engwifnam Amor \u225?r, Kanan \u225?r, Feris \u225?r, Ifai \u225?r, Jebus \u225?r. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 12\~}
Kor aem yau t\u225?f nawarendati y\u233?n\u233? \u225?rf\u233? efe emor y\u233?n\u233? mbandan \u225?ndan f\u233?m eyota njam f\u225? nufrotati nden\u233?, f\u233?mofem so waitogh tawafngongi y\u233?fene m\u225?m\u225?fi yam a t\u225?rnangi. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 13\~}
W\u233?nde f\u233?mofem t\u225?f engwironati y\u233?fene uny\u233?gh gh\u233?ng\u233?n kitar\u233?, eng\u233?tyanati y\u233?fene utman\u233?gh s\u233?ras\u233?r a ewanefetati y\u233?fene asera s\u233?ras\u233?r. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 14\~}
F\u233?mofem yau t\u225?f ew\u225?wefnotati \u225?mb ng\u225?nj\u225?nafet, y\u225?yot Yurai, endene y\u233?tkw\u233?n fifi y\u233?m waramnjagh \u225?r, y\u233?m y\u233?n\u233? Ng\u225?nj\u225?n efe y\u233?m waramnjagh \u225?r m\u233?nam\u233?n y\u225?ne f\u250?tar yamm\u233?n f\u233?maf\u233?.
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 15\~}
F\u233?m yau t\u225?f nawarendati tafar yame y\u233?n\u233? \u225?rf\u233? efe emor y\u233?n\u233?. Y\u233?mofem tik\u233?ffaf efandat y\u233?fenjo ng\u225?nj\u225?n, gh\u233?ng\u233?n erametat y\u233?fefaf. Y\u233?mofem so enmiyotat fe m\u233?n\u225?t so nuf\u233?indati gh\u233?ng\u233?n njamkefaf a f\u233?m so eng\u233?m y\u233?maf\u233?. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 16\~}
F\u233?yo f\u233?mofem so eumyotati y\u233?fene m\u233?r\u233?s, emofem gh\u233?ng\u233?n erametat k\u233?t\u225?n \u225?mb ng\u225?nj\u225?nafefaf, nden\u233? f\u233?t\u233? amafot f\u233?fene ambumot, a y\u233?mofem so em\u233?indat f\u233?fene ambum amafanyo awan\u233?gh\u233?t \u225?snan\u233?gh\u233?t tafaf m\u233?naye w\u225?wefnogh \u225?mb ng\u225?nj\u225?nat.
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 17\~}
"F\u233?mofem yau t\u225?f ewafrotati \u225?mb ng\u225?nj\u225?n tot t\u233?f\u233?nm\u233?n f\u233?fendio."
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 18\~}
"F\u233?mofem t\u225?f n\u233?us\u233?nati Minaghofnar flaw\u233? t\u233?m\u233?nd, k\u233?t\u225?n 7 efogh f\u233?skaf flaw\u233? f\u233?mofem s\u225?i enetati t\u225?f ewafrotati yitafnar, nden\u233? f\u233?t\u233? y\u233?ndon k\u233?s ewafaretay\u233?nd f\u233?m. N\u233?usenati y\u233?n\u233? t\u233?m\u233?nd yunjfero k\u233?t\u233? kaf\u233?ghm\u233?n efghon tot\u233?r k\u233?fran, a Bib gh\u233?rare k\u233?nj\u250?n, Y\u233?n\u233? f\u233?y\u233?m awafarogh kw\u233?f f\u233?fene f\u233?ramngoghm\u233?n Ijifta.
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 19\~}
"Fronde r\u225?f\u233?ghm\u233?n m\u233?inyotio w\u233?r\u225?ran em tane w\u233?i y\u233?nayafayo kau m\u233?r\u233?nta a f\u233?fene sifta a goutta. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 20\~}
Fronde r\u225?f\u233?ghm\u233?n ndonki so manie kwanangi k\u233?nawangongi k\u233?tam\u233? Yurata m\u233?naye s\u225?i t\u233?ngramang\u233?m tos\u233? sif o tot\u233?r gout y\u233?n\u233? sifayat. W\u233?nde njam f\u233?mofem yau manie tanangi y\u233?n\u233? t\u233?nmangongi, f\u233?mofem t\u225?f k\u233?m t\u233?rafangi y\u233?n\u233?, nden\u225?ye f\u233?mofem t\u225?f manie gh\u233?rsati ewangotati m\u233?inyotio fronde s\u233?nko ambum.
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 "Efe \u225?r yau so kufarng\u233? tane r\u233?re gh\u233?ng\u233?nofnar.
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 21\~}
"F\u233?fene em 6 efogh f\u233?fene m\u233?ndeye arangogh\u233?t, w\u233?nde k\u233?t\u233? 7 efogh f\u233?m t\u225?f k\u233?kmangi \u225?s\u225?fogh, w\u233?i t\u225?f y\u233?n\u233? w\u233?rw\u233?ran njam mband yengota a tar\u233?ghan.
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 22\~}
